\id GEN
\h Amezwaru 
\toc1 Amezwaru 
\toc2 Amezwaru 
\toc3 Amz. 
\mt1 Amezwaru  
\c 1
\s1 Taxeřqit n ijenwan d temmurt  
\m
\v 1 Deg umezwaru ixřeq-dd AREBBI ijenwan d temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Ayub 38:4; Izhd. 33:6; 89:12; 136:5; Řex. 14:15; 17:24; Ɛbr. 11:3; \x*   
\m
\v 2 Tuɣa tammurt texřa, am mammec war tt ittḥidi ḥed u x wudem n \add waman\add* ihewřen taǧest, u Arruḥ n AREBBI tuɣa ittraḥ ittas-dd x wudem n waman.   
\m
\v 3 Uca inna AREBBI: “Ad tiři tfawt”, uca tusa-dd tfawt! \f ◼ \fr 1:3 \ft \+fk tafawt\ft  - aqa din ijj n řfarq jar tfawt ɣar ijj n uɣezdis u tfuct d itran ɣar ijj n uɣezdis nneɣni. Tafuct d yetran aqa-ten arebbun tafawt, maca war ggin ca tafawt s yixef nsen. Tira iqeddsen qqarent aqa Arebbi d Tafawt, war dayes bu taǧest (xzar 1 Yḥ. 1:5). S uyenni teḍhar-dd tfawt deg wass d amezwaru n txeřqit, maca war tᵉttwaxřeq zi Arebbi minzi Netta s Yixef nnes d Tafawt.\f*  
\v 4 Iẓra AREBBI belli tafawt teṣbeḥ uca ibḍa AREBBI jar tfawt d taǧest.  
\v 5 Iřaɣa AREBBI tafawt ‘aziř’ u ‘taǧest’ iřaɣa as ‘ǧiřet’. Tedweř d tameddit u idweř d ṣṣbeḥ: \bd d ass amezwaru\bd*.   
\m
\v 6 Uca inna AREBBI: “Ad tiři ict n řqubbet di řwesṭ n waman, ad tebḍa aman x waman!” \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt Izhd. 33:6; 104:2; 136:5; Awřn. 8:28; Ica. 42:5; Irm. 10:12; 51:15\x*  
\v 7 AREBBI igga řqubbet \add n ujenna\add* uca ibḍa aman i iǧan swadday i řqubbet x waman i iǧan sennej i řqubbet. Uca ammu i temsar. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Izhd. 33:7; 136:6; Awřn. 8:24; Izhd. 148:4. \x*  
\v 8 Iřaɣa AREBBI i řqubbet ‘ajenna’. Uca tedweř d tameddit u idweř d ṣṣbeḥ: \bd d ass wiss tnayen\bd*.   
\m
\v 9 Uca inna AREBBI: “Ad munen waman i iǧan swadday i ujenna ɣar ijj n wemcan maḥend ad dd-iban řbarr!” Uca ammu i temsar. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Ayub 26:10; 38:8; Izhd. 24:2; 136:6. \x*  
\v 10 Iřaɣa AREBBI i řbarr ‘tammurt’ u amuni n waman iřaɣa as ‘řebḥur’. Uca iẓra AREBBI \add belli\add* man aya iṣbeḥ. \f ◼ \fr 1:10 \ft \+fk řebḥur\ft  - niɣ ‘il’ d ‘ilawen’.\f*   
\m
\v 11 Uca inna AREBBI: “Ad dd-tesseɣmi temmurt aɣemmuy aziza: afsu \add aziza\add* i izarrɛen zzariɛet d tcejjura s fruta i dd itticen frutat ɛlaḥsab marka nsent s zzariɛet nsent dayes x wudem n temmurt!” Uca ammu i temsar.  
\v 12 Tesseɣmi-dd temmurt aɣemmuy aziza: afsu \add aziza\add* i izarrɛen zzariɛet ɛlaḥsab marka nnes d tcejjura i dd itticen řɣiǧet ɛlaḥsab marka nsent s zzariɛet nsent dayes. Uca iẓra AREBBI \add belli\add* man aya iṣbeḥ.  
\v 13 Uca tedweř d tameddit u idweř d ṣṣbeḥ: \bd d ass wiss třata\bd*.   
\m
\v 14 Uca inna AREBBI: “Ad \add din\add* iřint tfawin di řqubbet \add n ujenna\add* ḥima ad bḍant jar wass d ǧiřet, ad iřint d řimarat, d wussan ittwaggen, d wussan, d iseggʷusa \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Izhd. 136:7. \x*  
\v 15 uca ad iřint d tifawin di řqubbet \add n ujenna\add* ḥima ad wcent tafawt x temmurt!” Uca ammu i temsar. \x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt Aɛwd. 4:19; Irm. 31:35\x*  
\v 16 Igga AREBBI tnayen n tifawin mɣarent, tafawt tameqqrant, ḥima ad teḥkem x uziř, u tafawt tameẓyant ḥima ad teḥkem x ǧiřet, uca uřa d itran.  
\v 17 Issars i-tent AREBBI di řqubbet \add n ujenna\add* ḥima ad wcent tafawt x temmurt  
\v 18 u ḥima ad ḥekment x wass d ǧiřet u ḥima ad bḍant jar tfawt d taǧest. Uca iẓra AREBBI \add belli\add* man aya iṣbeḥ.  
\v 19 Uca tedweř d tameddit u idweř d ṣṣbeḥ: \bd d ass wiss arebɛa\bd*.   
\m
\v 20 Uca inna AREBBI: “Ad dd-ssefyen waman s waṭṭas n \add marra min di iǧa\add* buḥbeř iddaren uca ad ḍwen ijḍaḍ sennej i temmurt ɣar mani \add teǧa\add* řqubbet n ujenna!” \f ◼ \fr 1:20 \ft \+fk ɣar mani teǧa řqubbet n ujenna\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘x wudmawen n řqubbet n ujenna’.\f*  
\v 21 Ixřeq-dd AREBBI imuddaren imeqqranen di řebḥar u marra buḥbeř iddaren ittenhezzan, inni zi dd-ssefyen waman, ɛlaḥsab marka nsen uca marra ijḍaḍ s wafriwen ɛlaḥsab marka nsen. Uca iẓra AREBBI \add belli\add* man aya iṣbeḥ.   
\m
\v 22 Ibark i-ten AREBBI, inna: “Jjem-dd řɣiǧet, ktarem, ɛemmarem aman n řebḥur, uca ad ktaren ijḍaḍ di temmurt.” \x ◘ \xo 1:22 \xt Amz. 8:17.\x*   
\m
\v 23 Uca tedweř d tameddit u idweř d ṣṣbeḥ: \bd d ass wiss xemsa\bd*.   
\m
\v 24 Uca inna AREBBI: “Ejj temmurt ad tessuffeɣ \add marra min ɣares\add* buḥbeř iddaren ɛlaḥsab marka nnes: řebhayem d \add imuddaren\add* nni ittbuɛen d řmař n řexřa ɛlaḥsab marka nsen!” Uca ammu i temsar. \f ◼ \fr 1:24 \ft \+fk imuddaren\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘iwdan’ d ‘lḥayawanat’ d marra min iddaren nni izemmar ad yuyur.\f*  
\v 25 Igga AREBBI řmař \add n řexřa\add* n temmurt ɛlaḥsab marka nsen, u řebhayem ɛlaḥsab marka nsent u marra \add imuddaren\add* nni ittbuɛen x wudem n temmurt ɛlaḥsab marka nsen. Uca iẓra AREBBI \add belli\add* man aya iṣbeḥ.   
\m
\v 26 Uca inna AREBBI: “Ejj aneɣ ad negg Adam, \add bnadem\add* di ṣṣifet nneɣ, deg warwas nneɣ, uca ad ɣares yiři jjehd x iseřman n řebḥar u x ijḍaḍ n ujenna u x řebhayem u x marra tammurt u x marra imuddaren nni ittbuɛen x temmurt!” \f ◼ \fr 1:26 \ft \+fk ad ɣares yiři\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad ɣarsen yiři’, min ixs ad yini ‘ad yiři ɣar iwdan ...’.\f*  
\v 27 Ixřeq-dd AREBBI Adam di ṣṣifet nnes. Ixřeq i-t-i-dd di ṣṣifet n AREBBI, ixřeq i-ten-dd awtem d tewtemt. \x ◘ \xo 1:27 \xt Amz. 5:1; 9:6; 1 Kur. 11:7; Afa. 4:24; Kul. 3:10. \x*   
\m
\v 28 Ibark i-ten AREBBI uca inna asen AREBBI: “Jjem-dd řɣiǧet, ktarem, ɛemmarem tammurt uca arrem tt sadu ufus nwem, ḥekmem x iseřman n řebḥar u x ijḍaḍ n ujenna u x marra imuddaren nni ittbuɛen x temmurt!” \x ◘ \xo 1:28 \xt Amz. 8:17; 9:1, 2, 7. \x*   
\m
\v 29 Inna AREBBI: “Xzarem, ad awem wceɣ marra afsu \add aziza\add* i izarrɛen zzariɛet x marra wudem n temmurt, uřa d marra ticejjura s řɣiǧet nni izarrɛen zzariɛet. Man aya ad awem yiři d macca. \f ◼ \fr 1:29 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘aseklu’ (‘isekla’) niɣ ‘taddagt’ (‘tiddagin’). \+bd afessar\+bd* - bnadem tuɣa ittett aysum di řweqt nni. Awarni i ṭṭufan ibda bnadem ad yecc aysum (xzar Amz. 9:2-4).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:29 \xt Amz. 9:3; Izhd. 104:14, 15. \x*  
\v 30 U i marra řmař \add n řexřa\add* n temmurt, u i marra ijḍaḍ n ujenna u i marra min ittbuɛen x temmurt i di iǧa buḥbeř iddaren, ad asen yiři marra afsu \add aziza\add* d macca i nitni.” Uca ammu i temsar. \x ◘ \xo 1:30 \xt Izhd. 104:14. \x*  
\v 31 Uca iẓra AREBBI marra min igga, u xzar, tuɣa iṣbeḥ aṭṭas. Tedweř d tameddit u idweř d ṣṣbeḥ: \bd d ass wiss setta\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 1:31 \xt Aɛwd. 32:4; Mk. 7:37. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\m
\v 1 Ammu i ttwakemmřen ijenwan d temmurt d qaɛ řɛeskar nsen. \f ◼ \fr 2:1 \ft \+fk qaɛ řɛeskar nsen\ft  - niɣ ‘marra řɛeskar nsen’.\f*  
\v 2 Deg wass wiss sebɛa ikemmeř AREBBI řxedmet nnes i igga uca yareyyeḥ deg wass wiss sebɛa zi marra řxedmet nnes i igga. \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Uf. 20:11; 31:17; Aɛwd. 5:14; Ɛbr. 4:4. \x*  
\v 3 Ibarek AREBBI ass wiss sebɛa uca issqeddes i-t, minzi dayes i yareyyeḥ zi marra řxedmet nnes, \add řxedmet\add* i dd-ixřeq AREBBI maḥend ad tt igg \add amenni\add*.  
\m \bd Ina d imezruyen n wexřaq n ujenna d temmurt řami dd-ttwaxeřqen.\bd*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Taxeřqit n Adam d temɣart nnes  
\m
\v 4 Deg wass i igga SIDI AREBBI tammurt d ijenwan  
\v 5 - qbeř tuɣi din marra cbarq di temmurt u qbeř dd-iɣmi wefsu n yeyyar, minzi SIDI AREBBI war ijji anẓar ad iwwet \add ɛad\add* x temmurt - uca war tuɣi din Adam \add ɛad\add* ḥima ad ixdem tammurt,  
\v 6 tgeɛɛed-dd tayyut zi temmurt, tessu marra udem n temmurt.   
\m
\v 7 Uca ikewwen SIDI AREBBI Adam zi tɛejjajt n ucař uca isuḍ řeɛwin n tudart deg wenzaren nnes. Ammu i idweř Adam d ijj n nnefs iddar. \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt 1 Kur. 15:45, 47.\x*   
\m
\v 8 Xenni iẓẓu SIDI AREBBI jjennet di Ɛadn, jjihet n ccarq, uca issars din Adam i igga. \f ◼ \fr 2:8 \ft \+fk Ɛadn\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘meẓri’. S uyenni tuɣa jjennet Ɛadn d ijj n wemcan mani izemmar bnadem ad yarr meẓri ɛlaḥsab min ixs Arebbi, war iǧi ɛlaḥsab min ixs bnadem.\f*  
\v 9 Uca isseɣmi-dd SIDI AREBBI zi temmurt kuř tacejjart, tecna i řxeẓrat u tmiẓidt i macca, uca \add isseɣmi-dd řa d\add* tacejjart n tudart di řwesṭ n jjennet uřa d tacejjart n tussna n řxar d řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 2:9 \xt Asa. 2:7. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Iffeɣ-dd ijj n iɣzar zi Ɛadn, ḥima ad issuw jjennet u ssenni immsebḍa x arebɛa n izeǧifen i iggin tiseǧyawin.  
\v 11 Isem n \add yeɣzar\add* amezwaru d Ficun. Netta i innḍen i marra tammurt n Ḥawila mani iǧa wureɣ.  
\v 12 Ureɣ n temmurt nni iṣbeḥ. Aqa din \add aserɣaɣ acemřař qqaren as\add* ‘bᵉdula’, d weẓru n ‘uniks’.  
\v 13 Isem n iɣzar wiss tnayen d Jiḥun i tuɣa innḍen i marra tammurt n Kuc.  
\v 14 Isem n iɣzar wiss třata d Ḥiddaqil. Netta ittazzeř ɣar ccarq n Accur. U iɣzar wiss arebɛa d Lfuraṭ.   
\m
\v 15 Iksi SIDI AREBBI Adam uca issars i-t di jjennet n Ɛadn, ḥima ad tt ixdem u ad tt iḥḍa.  
\v 16 SIDI AREBBI iweṣṣa Adam, inna: “Zi marra ticejjura n jjennet ad tecced macca,  
\v 17 maca zi tcejjart n tussna n řxar d řɣar war ttᵉtted ca zzayes, minzi deg wass i zzayes ɣa tecced, řmewt i ɣa temmted!”   
\m
\v 18 Inna SIDI AREBBI: “War iɛeddeř ad yiři Adam weḥḥdes. Ad as ggeɣ wi t ɣa iɛawnen, am netta qibač nnes.”   
\m
\v 19 Tuɣa SIDI AREBBI igga zeg ucař marra řmař n řexřa u marra ijḍaḍ n ujenna, uca indeh i-ten ɣar Adam, ḥima ad iẓar mammec i ten ɣa isemma. Mammec i ɣa isemma Adam kuř nnefs iddaren d wa d isem nnes.  
\v 20 Igga Adam ismawen i marra řebhayem d yejḍaḍ n ujenna u i marra řmař n řexřa, \add maca\add* i Adam war yufi wi t ɣa iɛawnen d wi ɣa yiřin am netta qibač nnes.   
\m
\v 21 Issehwa-dd SIDI AREBBI ijj n yiḍeṣ yuǧeɣ x Adam uca iṭṭeṣ. \add Xenni\add* iksi icten zi tɣezdisin nnes uca iqqen \add amcan yarezmen\add* nni s weysum.  
\v 22 Yarra SIDI AREBBI taɣezdist tenni i iksi zi Adam d tamɣart uca yiwyi tt-i-dd ɣar Adam. \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt 1 Kur. 11:8. \x*  
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* inna Adam: “Twařa-ya tanita aqa-tt d iɣes zeg iɣsan inu d aysum zeg weysum inu. Tanita ad tᵉttwasemma ‘taryazt’, \add ixs ad yini ‘tamɣart’\add*, minzi nettat tᵉttwaksi-dd zeg weryaz.” \x ◘ \xo 2:23 \xt Mal. 2:14; Afa. 5:30, 31. \x*  
\v 24 X uya ad ismeḥ weryaz di babas d yemmas, ad iqqen ɣar temɣart nnes uca ad iřin d ict n ddat. \f ◼ \fr 2:24 \ft \+fk ict n ddat\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ijj n weysum’. Awařen xsen ad inin belli aryaz d temɣart nnes aqa-ten d ijj n bnadem. Man aya d ttidet s minzi Ḥawwa teffeɣ zeg arrimet n Adam s ufus n Arebbi.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:24 \xt Mt. 19:5, 6; Mk. 10:8; Afa. 5:31; 1 Kur. 6:16. \x*  
\v 25 Tuɣa-ten s tnayen idsen d iɛaryanen, Adam d temɣart nnes, \add maca\add* tuɣa war din ca n řeḥya jar asen. \x ◘ \xo 2:25 \xt Amz. 3:7. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Ddenb amezwaru  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa afiɣar d aḥraymi x marra řmař n řexřa i igga SIDI AREBBI. Inna i temɣart: “Ma d tidett inna AREBBI: ‘Ɣarwem war ttᵉttem ca zi marra ticejjura n jjennet’?”  
\v 2 Tenna temɣart i ufiɣar: “Zi řɣiǧet n tcejjura n jjennet nzemmar ad necc,  
\v 3 maca zi řɣiǧet n tcejjart di řwesṭ n jjennet, inna AREBBI: ‘War zzayes ttᵉttem, war tt ttḥadam, ḥima war tᵉttmettim.’”  
\v 4 Inna ufiɣar i temɣart: “Kenniw war tᵉttmettim ca s řmewt qaɛ, \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt 2 Kur. 11:3. \x*  
\v 5 \add maca\add* AREBBI issen belli ass nni di zzayes i ɣa teccem, ad arzment tiṭṭawin nwem uca ad tiřim am AREBBI, ad tessnem řxar zi řɣar.” \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Yḥ. 8:44. \x*   
\m
\v 6 Teẓra temɣart belli tacejjart teṣbeḥ i macca uca teɛjeb asent i tiṭṭawin, aqa tacejjart tegga dayes meẓri maḥend ad zzayes tedweř d tamiɣist. Xenni teksi zi řɣiǧet nnes, tecca uca tewca ɛawed i weryaz nnes i tuɣa akides, uca netta icca. \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Rum. 5:12, 14-21; 1 Tim. 2:14. \x*  
\v 7 Nnarzment tiṭṭawin nsen uca ufin ixef nsen d iɛaryanen. Xenni xeyyḍen tifray n wartu, uca ggin \add zzaysent\add* tibantiwin i yixef nsen.  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* sřin nitni tmijja n SIDI AREBBI iggur di jjennet ɣar uweṭṭu n tmeddit, uca iffar Adam d temɣart nnes zeg wudem n SIDI AREBBI jar tcejjura n jjennet.   
\m
\v 9 Uca iřaɣa SIDI AREBBI Adam, inna as: “Mani teǧid?”  
\v 10 Netta inna: “Sřiɣ i tmijja nnec di jjennet uca ggʷedeɣ minzi necc d aɛaryan, xenni ffareɣ.” \f ◼ \fr 3:10 \ft \+fk aɛaryan\ft  - niɣ ‘azeɛbud’.\f*  
\v 11 Inna \add as Netta\add*: “Wi d ac innan belli cek d aɛaryan? Ma teccid zi tcejjart nni x cek weṣṣiɣ ‘Aqa ad zzayes tecced?”  
\v 12 Inna Adam: “Tamɣart nni d ayi tewcid, nettat tewca ayi zi tcejjart uca cciɣ.”  
\v 13 Inna as SIDI AREBBI i temɣart: “Manawya i teggid?” Tenna \add as\add* temɣart: “Iɣarra ayi ufiɣar uca cciɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Asa. 12:13. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 Inna SIDI AREBBI \bd i ufiɣar\bd*:  
\m \qt “Řami teggid aya,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa ac d amenɛuř jar marra řebhayem\qt*  
\m \qt u jar marra řmař n řexřa.\qt*  
\m \qt X uɛeddis nnec ad tmurded,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad tecced ucař\qt*  
\m \qt marra ussan n tudart nnec.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 3:14 \ft \+fk řmař n řexřa\ft  - marra řewḥuc i iǧan di řexřa, di demnet, di řɣabet (niɣ di tagant), deg wezɣar u di ṣṣeḥra.\f*   
\m
\v 15 \qt Ad ggeɣ řeɛdawat jar ac d temɣart,\qt*  
\m \qt jar zzariɛet nnec d zzariɛet nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt D tenni \+tl nnes\+tl* ad teřbez azeǧif nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt u cek ad as třebzed anirz \+tl nnes\+tl*.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt Amz. 24:60; Mt. 4:1; Kul. 2:15. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Inna \bd i temɣart\bd*:  
\m \qt “Aṭṭas i ɣa arniɣ řeḥriq d řewjeɛ n tarwa nnem.\qt*  
\m \qt S řeḥriq ad dd-tarwed iḥenjiren,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ɣar weryaz nnem ad temmeẓred,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maca\+tl* netta ad xam iḥkem.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Kur. 14:34; 1 Tim. 2:11, 12; Tit. 2:5; 1 Bṭ. 3:6. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 17 Uca inna \bd i Adam:\bd*  
\m \qt “Minzi tesřid ɣar tmijja n temɣart nnec\qt*  
\m \qt u teccid zi tcejjart tenni x cek weṣṣiɣ:\qt*  
\m \qt ‘Aqa ad zzayes tecced!’,\qt*  
\m \qt ad tiři temmurt d nneɛřet x ssibbet nnec.\qt*  
\m \qt S tamara ad zzayes tecced,\qt*  
\m \qt marra ussan n tudart nnec.\qt*   
\m
\v 18 \qt Isennanen d tzeggʷart i d ac dd ɣa tesseɣmi,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad tecced afsu n yeyyar\qt*.   
\m
\v 19 \qt S tidi n uɣembub nnec ad tecced aɣrum\qt*  
\m \qt ař dd ɣa tdewřed ɣar temmurt i zi temmeksid,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi cek d \+tl a\+tl*cař uca ɣar ucař i ɣa dd-tdewřed.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Iřaɣa Adam isem n temɣart nnes \bd Ḥawwa\bd* minzi nettat d yemmas n marra inni iddaren. \f ◼ \fr 3:20 \ft \+fk Ḥawwa\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘tenni iddaren’ niɣ ‘tenni itticen tudart’.\f*  
\v 21 Igga SIDI AREBBI i Adam d temɣart nnes arruḍ s yiřem uca yarḍ asen t. \x ◘ \xo 3:21 \xt 2 Kur. 5:1-5\x*  
\v 22 Inna SIDI AREBBI: “Xzar, Adam wa, aqa idweř am yijjen zzayneɣ, issen řxar d řɣar. Řexxu, ejj i-t war isswaẓẓaḍ afus nnes maḥend ad iksi zi Tcejjart n Tudart ɛawed, ad yecc u \add xenni\add* ad iddar i řebda.”  
\v 23 Uca issuffuɣ i-t SIDI AREBBI zi jjennet n Ɛadn ḥima ad ixdem tammurt i zi tuɣa immeksi.  
\v 24 Yuẓẓeř x Adam uca igga ikiruben ccarq i jjennet n Ɛadn d yijj n ssif itteḥduduq, ittecḍiḍiḥ ssa d ssa i uɛessi x webrid n tcejjart n tudart. \f ◼ \fr 3:24 \ft \+fk ikiruben\ft  - ict n lmarka n lmalakat iqeddsen. Aqa-ten d imeqqranen di tzemmar d ṣṣulṭa, ttbeddan řebda zzat i Arebbi (‹xzar Ḥiz. 1 d Aweḥḥi 4, 5›)\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Qayin d Habil  
\m
\v 1 Issen Adam Ḥawwa, tamɣart nnes, uca teysi s ddeyset uca turuw-dd \bd Qayin\bd*, tenna “Jjiɣ-dd aryaz, d SIDI!” \f ◼ \fr 4:1 \ft \+fk Qayin\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘agřa’ niɣ ‘min ittwakessben’.\f*  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* ɛawed turuw-dd umas \bd Habil\bd*. Tuɣa Habil d ameksaw n wuǧi u Qayin iruḥ ixeddem tammurt. \f ◼ \fr 4:2 \ft \+fk Habil\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘tayyut’ niɣ ‘amedlu’ niɣ ‘řefwar’ niɣ ‘min iɛeddun’ niɣ ‘min ifennan’. S uyenni idweř isem nnes d aceyyar ɣar min d as i ɣa imsaren umi i d as inɣa umas. Ad tefna tudart nnes deɣya am ict n tayyut tɛeddu. \fk ameksaw\ft  - niɣ ‘aniči’.\f*   
\m
\v 3 Uca awarni ussan imsar belli Qayin iqeddem ict n tewhibt zi řɣiǧet n wudem n temmurt i SIDI.  
\v 4 Iqeddem Habil ɛawed \add ict n tewhibt\add* zeg imenza n wuǧi nnes, zeg inni ɣar iǧa tadunt aṭṭas. Ixzar SIDI ɣar Habil d tewhibt nnes, \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt Ɛbr. 11:4. \x*  
\v 5 \add maca\add* ɣar Qayin d tewhibt nnes war d as yarri ca taynit. Uca ixeyyeq Qayin aṭṭas, inneqřeb as uɣembub.  
\v 6 Inna SIDI i Qayin: “Mayemmi txeyyqed? Mayemmi d ac inneqřeb uɣembub?  
\v 7 Mařa teggid mliḥ, ma war \add din\add* ittiři usgeɛɛed, u mařa war teggid mliḥ, ddenb aqa-t izzeř ɣar tewwart? Meẓri nnes ɣarek, \add maca\add* ittxeṣṣa cek ad xas tseǧḍed.”  
\v 8 Issiweř Qayin ak-d Habil umas. Uca imsar am ǧan nitni deg iyyar, belli Qayin ikkar ɣar umas Habil uca inɣa i-t. \x ◘ \xo 4:8 \xt Mt. 23:35; 1 Yḥ. 3:12; Yah. 11. \x*   
\m
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Qayin: “Mani iǧa umac Habil?” Inna: “War ssineɣ. Ma necc d ameḥḍay x uma?”  
\v 10 Uca inna Netta: “Min teggid? Aqa tmijja n idammen n umac sɣuyyun-dd ɣari zi temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 4:10 \xt Ɛbr. 12:24. \x*  
\v 11 Řexxu, aqa cek d menɛuř zi temmurt, tenni yarezmen aqemmum nnes, ḥima ad teqbeř idammen n umac zeg ifassen nnec.  
\v 12 Xmi ɣa txedmed x temmurt, war ttᵉdikkʷiř ad ac tewc marra jjehd nnes uca cek ad tiřid d amennejru d ametluɛ di temmurt.” \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Awřn. 28:17. \x*  
\v 13 Xenni inna Qayin i SIDI: “Lɛiqab inu imɣar aṭṭas x tzemmar inu.  
\v 14 Aqa Cek ass\add -a\add* tuẓẓřed xafi zeg uɣembub n temmurt\add -a\add* uca zeg uɣembub nnec ad ttwaffare. Ad iřiɣ d amennejru d ametluɛ di temmurt uca ad yiři marra wenni d ayi ɣa yafen ad ayi ineɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt Ayub 15:20, 21. \x*  
\v 15 Xenni inna as SIDI: “S uya marra wenni i ɣa inɣen Qayin, ad zzayes xeřfen sebɛa n twařawin.” Uca igga SIDI řeɛřamet i Qayin belli marra wenni t ɣa yafen war t ineqq.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tarwa n Qayen  
\m
\v 16 Xenni iffeɣ-dd Qayin zeg wudem n SIDI uca iruḥ izeddeɣ di temmurt n Nud, ccarq n Ɛadn. \f ◼ \fr 4:16 \ft \+fk Nud\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘atlaɛ’ niɣ ‘aweddar’ niɣ ‘tarewřa’ (xzar Izhd. 56:9).\f*  
\v 17 Issen Qayin tamɣart nnes uca teysi s ddeyset uca turuw as-dd Ḥanux. Tuɣa \add Qayen\add* ibna ict n tendint uca iřaɣa as i tendint am yisem n mmis Ḥanux. \f ◼ \fr 4:17 \ft \+fk Ḥanux\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni ittceṭṭaren’ niɣ ‘wenni ikemmřen’. Tuɣa Ḥanux d ijj n bnadem s wuř ikemmřen ɣar Arebbi.\f*  
\v 18 Ḥanux ijja-dd Ɛirad, u Ɛirad ijja-dd Miḥuya’il u Miḥuya’il ijja-dd Matuca’il u Matuca’il ijja-dd Lamak. \f ◼ \fr 4:18 \ft \+fk Ɛirad\ft  - isem wanita ittqennan ak-d ‘Ɛarad’ (xzar Řxř. 21:1). Ad taɣ ad yiři řmeɛna nnes ‘ɛzeř’ niɣ ‘arweř’. Inneɣni qqaren aqa dayes řmeɛna ‘amezduɣ n tendint’. \fk Miḥuya’il\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni ittwawten zi Arebbi’. \fk Matuca’il\ft  - ad taɣ ad yiři řmeɛna n yisem wanita ‘aryaz n Arebbi’ niɣ ‘min iɛna Arebbi?’ Inneɣni qqaren aqa-t d ‘aryaz n taẓaǧit’. \fk Lamak\ft  - ad taɣ ad yiři řmeɛna n yisem-a ‘wenni ijehden’.\f*  
\v 19 Imřec Lamak tnayen n temɣarin. Icten qqaren as Ɛada, tenneɣni qqaren as Ṣilla. \f ◼ \fr 4:19 \ft \+fk Ɛada\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘tunger’ niɣ ‘aẓri’. Uřa d tamɣart n Ɛisu řaɣan as s yisem-a (xzar Amz. 36:2, 4 u Amz. 26:34, 35). \fk Ṣilla\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘tiři’.\f*  
\v 20 Turuw-dd Ɛada Yabal. Netta idweř d babatsen i imezdaɣ n iqiḍan u i imeksawen n řebhayem. \f ◼ \fr 4:20 \ft \+fk Yabal\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘iɣzar’ niɣ ‘aman ittazzřen’. \fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  
\v 21 Isem n umas tuɣa d Yubal wenni tuɣa d babatsen i marra inni ittiraren řgambri d temja. \f ◼ \fr 4:21 \ft \+fk Yubal\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘yeɣzar’ niɣ ‘tammurt yuffen’.\f*  
\v 22 Ṣilla turuw-dd ɛawed Tubal-Qayin, amziř n imziřen n marra inni ixeddmen s nnḥas d wuzzař. Učmas n Tubal-Qayin \add tuɣa\add* d Naɛma. \f ◼ \fr 4:22 \ft \+fk Tubal-Qayin\ft  - ad taɣ isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘amziř, maca řmeɛna war iǧi itwassnen nican. \fk Naɛma\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘iɛizzen’ niɣ ‘yarḍan’.\f*   
\m
\v 23 Inna Lamak i temɣarin nnes, Ɛada d Ṣilla: “Sřent i tmijja inu, \add a\add* timɣarin n Lamak! Sřent ɣar min ɣa iniɣ. Aqa nɣiɣ aryaz i uyezzim inu d uḥenjir i uyeddim inu!  
\v 24 Aqa ad xeřfen zi Qayin sebɛa n twařawin, maca zi Lamak sebɛa u-sebɛin n twařawin.” \x ◘ \xo 4:24 \xt Amz. 4:15. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Axřaq n Cit  
\m
\v 25 Yudef Adam ɛawed x tamɣart nnes uca turuw-dd nettat aḥenjir. Třaɣa as \bd Cit\bd*, minzi \add tenna:\add* “AREBBI iwca ayi zzariɛet nneɣni deg wemcan n Habil, minzi Qayin inɣa i-t.” \f ◼ \fr 4:25 \ft \+fk Cit\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni ikessin amcan n wenneɣni’ niɣ ‘wenni ittwaggen deg wemcan n wenneɣni’. Man aya ixs ad yini aqa Arebbi iwca i Ḥawwa ijj n mmis deg wemcan n Habil.\f*  
\v 26 Uřa i Cit ittwaxřeq-dd useymi, uca igga as \bd Anuc\bd*. Řexdenni ibda bnadem s uřaɣi x Yisem n SIDI.  
\m \bd Wa d adlis ittwanḍen n imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi Adam.\bd* \f ◼ \fr 4:26 \ft \+fk Anuc\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘bnadem’ niɣ ‘aryaz’.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Tarwa n Adam  
\m
\v 1 Ass min di igga AREBBI Adam, igga i-t di ṣṣifet n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt [1 Imz. 1:1-27] — Amz. 1:26; 9:6; 1 Kur. 11:7. \x*  
\v 2 Awtem d tewtemt ixřeq i-ten-dd. Ibark i-ten uca iřaɣa asen s yisem ‘Adam’, \add bnadem\add*, deg wass i di ten dd-ixřeq. \f ◼ \fr 5:2 \ft \+fk deg wass i di ten ixřeq\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘deg wass i di dd-ttwaxeřqen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 5:2 \xt Amz. 1:26; Mt. 19:4; Mk. 10:6. \x*   
\m
\v 3 Awarni řami iddar \bd Adam\bd* mya u-třatin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd \add aḥenjir\add* deg warwas nnes u di ṣṣifet nnes uca iřaɣa as Cit.  
\v 4 Awarni řami dd-ijja Cit, iddar Adam \add ɛad\add* temn-mya n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin. \x ◘ \xo 5:4 \xt 1 Im. 1:1. \x*  
\v 5 Ammu i iddar Adam tesɛa-mya u-třatin n iseggʷusa uca immut.   
\m
\v 6 Awarni řami iddar \bd Cit\bd* mya u-xemsa n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd Anuc. \x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt Amz. 4:26. \x*  
\v 7 Awarni řami dd-ijja Anuc, iddar Cit \add ɛad\add* temn-mya u-sebɛa n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.  
\v 8 Ammu i iddar Cit tesɛa-mya u-tenɛac n iseggʷusa uca immut.   
\m
\v 9 Awarni řami iddar \bd Anuc\bd* tesɛin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd Qinan. \f ◼ \fr 5:9 \ft \+fk Qinan\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘agřa’ niɣ ‘lmulk’ niɣ ‘řɛucc’ niɣ ‘tazeddiɣt’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 5:9 \xt 1 Im. 1:2. \x*  
\v 10 Awarni řami dd-ijja Qinan, iddar Anuc \add ɛad\add* temn-mya u-xemmesṭac n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.  
\v 11 Ammu i iddar Anuc tesɛa-mya u-xemsa n iseggʷusa uca immut.   
\m
\v 12 Awarni řami iddar \bd Qinan\bd* sebɛin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd Mahalal-Il. \f ◼ \fr 5:12 \ft \+fk Mahalal-Il\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘asemɣar zi Arebbi’.\f*  
\v 13 Awarni řami dd-ijja Mahalal-Il, iddar Qinan \add ɛad\add* temn-mya u-rebɛin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.  
\v 14 Ammu i iddar Qinan tesɛa-mya u-ɛecra n iseggʷusa uca immut.   
\m
\v 15 Awarni řami iddar \bd Mahalal-Il\bd* xemsa u-settin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd Yarad. \f ◼ \fr 5:15 \ft \+fk Yarad\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yinni ‘ijjen wenni i dd-iqarrsen zi’.\f*  
\v 16 Awarni řami dd-ijja Yarad, iddar Mahalal-Il \add ɛad\add* temn-mya u-třatin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.  
\v 17 Ammu i iddar Mahalal-Il temn-mya u-xemsa u-tesɛin n iseggʷusa uca immut.   
\m
\v 18 Awarni řami iddar \bd Yarad\bd* mya u-tnayen u-settin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd Ḥanux. \f ◼ \fr 5:18 \ft \+fk Ḥanux\ft  - xzar Amz. 4:17.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt 1 Im. 1:3. \x*  
\v 19 Awarni řami dd-ijja Ḥanux, iddar Yarad \add ɛad\add* temn-mya n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.  
\v 20 Ammu i iddar Yarad tesɛa-mya u-tnayen u-settin n iseggʷusa uca immut.   
\m
\v 21 Awarni řami iddar \bd Ḥanux\bd* xemsa u-settin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd Matucalaḥ. \f ◼ \fr 5:21 \ft \+fk Matucalaḥ\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘aryaz s fřitca’ niɣ ‘wenni dd-ittwassekken’ niɣ ‘aryaz wenni ɣar iǧa ict n ureqqas niɣ ict n tabrat’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 5:21 \xt Yah. 14.\x*  
\v 22 Awarni řami dd-ijja Matucalaḥ, yuyur Ḥanux ak-d AREBBI teřt-mya n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin. \x ◘ \xo 5:22 \xt Ɛbr. 11:5. \x*  
\v 23 Ammu i iddar Ḥanux teřt-mya u-xemsa u-settin n iseggʷusa.  
\v 24 Yuyur Ḥanux ak-d AREBBI uca war ittwif ɛad minzi AREBBI iksi i-t. \x ◘ \xo 5:24 \xt Ɛbr. 11:5. \x*   
\m
\v 25 Awarni řami iddar \bd Matucalaḥ\bd* mya u-sebɛa u-tmanyin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd Lamak. \f ◼ \fr 5:25 \ft \+fk Lamak\ft  - ad taɣ ixs ad yini isem-a ‘wenni ijehden’ niɣ ‘amwaḍeɛ’.\f*  
\v 26 Awarni řami dd-ijja Lamak, iddar Matucalaḥ \add ɛad\add* sebɛa-mya u-tnayen u-tmanyin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.  
\v 27 Ammu i iddar Matucalaḥ tesɛa-mya u-tesɛa u-settin n iseggʷusa uca immut.   
\m
\v 28 Awarni řami iddar \bd Lamak\bd* mya u-tnayen u-tmanyin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd ijj n uḥenjir.  
\v 29 Iřaɣa isem nnes Nuḥ, inna: “Wa ad aneɣ issfewwej x řxedmet nneɣ d tamara n ifassen nneɣ, minzi SIDI aqa inɛeř tammurt!” \f ◼ \fr 5:29 \ft \+fk Nuḥ\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘afewwej’.\f*  
\v 30 Awarni řami dd-ijja Nuḥ, iddar Lamak \add ɛad\add* xemsa-mya u-xemsa u-tesɛin n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.  
\v 31 Ammu i iddar Lamak sebɛa-mya u-sebɛa u-sebɛin n iseggʷusa uca immut.   
\m
\v 32 Awarni řami iddar \bd Nuḥ\bd* xemsa-mya n iseggʷusa, Nuḥ ijja-dd Cam d Ḥam d Yafat.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Tuɛeffna n iwdan  
\m
\v 1 Řami bdan iwdan ad ktaren di temmurt uca urwent asen-dd yessitsen, \f ◼ \fr 6:1 \ft \+fk iwdan\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘bnadem’, uřa di ayet wiss 2.\f*  
\v 2 aqa ẓrin arrawen n AREBBI belli yessis n bnadem cnant, uca ksin timɣarin i yixef nsen zi marra tinni ixḍaren nitni. \f ◼ \fr 6:2 \ft \+fk arrawen n Arebbi\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini ‘lmalakat’. Xzar Ayub 1:6; 2:1, 38:7. Maca lmalakat war zemmarent ad adfent x yessis n bnadem, maca ad taɣ s tseḥḥart nsent u umi bdant ad zedɣen deg iryazen d temɣarin (am jjnun) ggin zzaysen arrawen nni iggin axmi ‘jjwaheř’. Jjwaheř nni ssfesden jjiř n bnadem uřa d zzariɛet n temɣart i zi iwaɛd SIDI AREBBI Amsenjem nnes, Lmasiḥ (xzar Amz. 3:15). S uyenni tuɣa ittxeṣṣa i SIDI AREBBI ḥima ad iḥkem x ddunect marra, ařami igga ṭṭufan ad dd-yas x temmurt. Mɣir Nuḥ i iqqimen iddar ak-d twacunt nnes. SIDI AREBBI iḥebbes uřa d lmalakat nni iggin aya (xzar 1 Bṭ. 3:19, 20, 2 Bṭ. 2:4 u Yah. 6, 7).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:2 \xt 2 Bṭ. 2:4; Judas 1:6, 7\x*  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI: “War ittɣimi Arruḥ inu řebda di bnadem, aqa-t d ddat zi ssibbet n uweddar nnes. Ad iřin wussan \add n tudart\add* nnes mya u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa.” \f ◼ \fr 6:3 \ft \+fk nnes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘nsen’.\f*   
\m
\v 4 Deg wussan nni tuɣa ‘inifilim’, \add ixs ad yini ‘inni iwḍan’\add*, di temmurt uca awarni man aya ɛawed, umi dd-udfen arraw n AREBBI ɣar yessis n iwdan uca urwent asen-dd. Nitni d ‘jjwaheř’ n zzman nni, d iryazen s yisem. \f ◼ \fr 6:4 \ft \+fk inifilim\ft  - s Tɛibranit ina d ‘inni iwḍan’. Nessen aqa-ten d iwdan imɣaren aṭṭas maɣar nufa awař-a uřa deg Wedlis Iqeddsen di řectab ‘Di řexřa’ 13:33. S uyenni nessen aqa isem wanita iceyyar ɣar ‘jjwaheř’.\f*  
\v 5 Iẓra SIDI belli řɣar n bnadem d aṭṭas x temmurt uca marra řemwayař n uxarreṣ n wuř nnes d aɛeffan kuř ass. \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Amz. 8:21; Ayub 15:16; Awřn. 6:14; Irm. 17:9; Mt. 15:19; Rum. 3:10, 11, 12; 8:6. \x*  
\v 6 Uca indem SIDI umi igga bnadem di temmurt uca iqqes as wuř nnes.  
\v 7 Inna SIDI: “Ad mḥiɣ x wudem n temmurt bnadem i dd-xeřqeɣ, bnadem ak-d řebhayem d \add imuddaren\add* ittbuɛen uřa d ijḍaḍ n ujenna, minzi nedmeɣ umi ten ggiɣ.”  
\v 8 \add Maca\add* Nuḥ yufa arḍa di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.  
\m \bd Ina d imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi Nuḥ.\bd*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Nuḥ d ṭṭufan  
\m
\v 9 Tuɣa Nuḥ d aryaz d amsegged ikmeř jar marra jjiřat nni iddaren akides. Yuyur Nuḥ ak-d AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 6:9 \xt Amz. 5:22. \x*  
\v 10 Uca ijja-dd Nuḥ třata n iḥenjiren: Cam d Ḥam d Yafat. \f ◼ \fr 6:10 \ft \+fk Cam\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘isem’. \fk Ḥam\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘igwa’ niɣ ‘iḥma’. \fk Yafat\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni ittwazeǧeɛ aṭṭas’ niɣ ‘innurezmen’.\f*  
\v 11 Tuɣa tammurt d ict n řxarbet di tiṭṭawin n AREBBI u tuɣa tammurt teccur s lɛunf.  
\v 12 Ixzar AREBBI ɣar temmurt, u xzar, aqa-tt d řxarbet, maɣar marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum tuɣa xarrben abrid nsen x temmurt.   
\m
\v 13 Inna AREBBI i Nuḥ: “Aneggar n marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum aqa-t zzat i wudem inu, minzi tammurt teccur s lɛunf zzaysen. Aqa ad ten teḥḥiɣ ak-d temmurt.  
\v 14 Egg i yixef nnec ijj n uɣarrabu s ukeccuḍ n umerzi uca egg ixxamen \add i marra řmař\add* deg uɣarrabu. Ɣeǧef aɣarrabu zi daxeř u zi barra s tizeft. \f ◼ \fr 6:14 \ft \+fk tizeft\ft  - awař ‘tizeft’ di Tɛibranit dayes řemɛani. Izemmar ad yini ‘afeddi’ niɣ ‘ttaman n ufeddi’. Xẓar Uf. 21:30 u Řxř. 35:32. S uyenni mařa ittwafdi ijj bnadem aqa man aya ixs ad yini belli uřa d ddnub nnes ad iřin ttwaɣemsen.\f*  
\v 15 Ammu ittxeṣṣa ad t tegged: tuzzeggart n uɣarrabu \add ad tiři\add* teřt-mya n iɣaǧen u tiru n uɣarrabu \add ad tiři\add* xemsin n iɣaǧen u řuɛřa nnes \add ad yiři\add* třatin n iɣaǧen. \f ◼ \fr 6:15 \ft \+fk iɣaǧen\ft  - ijj n uɣiř ɛřayen 50 cm niɣ azyen n mitru.\f*  
\v 16 Ittxeṣṣa ad tegged ict n tburjet i tfawt deg uɣarrabu uca ad tt tkemmřed anect n ijj n uɣiř zi sennej. Ad tegged tawwart n uɣarrabu deg uɣezdis nnes. Ad tegged ṭṭebqet n wadday d ṭṭebqet wiss tnayen \add di řwesṭ\add* d ṭṭebqet wiss třata \add sennej\add*.  
\v 17 Aqa Necc ad ssekkeɣ sseḥřet n waman x temmurt, ḥima ad teḥḥiɣ sadu ujenna marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum i di iǧa arruḥ n tudart. Marra min iǧan di temmurt ad iḍřeq i buḥbeř.  
\v 18 \add Maca\add* ad ssbeddeɣ Řɛahd inu akidek uca cek ad tadfed ɣar uɣarrabu, cek d iḥenjiren nnec d temɣart nnec d temɣarin n iḥenjiren nnec akidek. \x ◘ \xo 6:18 \xt 1 Bṭ. 3:20; 2 Bṭ. 2:5. \x*  
\v 19 Uca zi marra min iddaren, zi marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum ad tessidfed tyuya ɣar uɣarrabu ḥima ad ddaren akidek: ittxeṣṣa ad yiři d awtem d tewtemt.  
\v 20 Ad ɣarek dd-tas tyuya zi marra, ḥima ad teḥḍid tudart nsen: zeg ijḍaḍ ɛlaḥsab markat nsen, zi řebhayem ɛlaḥsab markat nsent u zi marra \add imuddaren\add* nni ittbuɛen x temmurt ɛlaḥsab markat nsen.  
\v 21 Uca cek, ksi i yixef nnec zi marra macca i ittwaccan uca smun i-tt ɣarek, ḥima ad ac yiři d macca uca uřa i nitni.”  
\v 22 Uca igga Nuḥ am mammec marra i xef t iweṣṣa AREBBI, ammu i \add t\add* igga. \x ◘ \xo 6:22 \xt Amz. 7:5; Ɛbr. 11:7. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\m
\v 1 Inna SIDI i Nuḥ: “Adef cek d marra \add řaǧ n\add* taddart nnec ɣar uɣarrabu, minzi ẓriɣ cek d amsegged zzat i wudem inu di jjiř-a. \x ◘ \xo 7:1 \xt Amz. 6:9; 2 Bṭ. 2:5. \x*  
\v 2 Zi marra řebhayem n řeḥřař ad ɣarek teksid sebɛa, sebɛa, awtem d tewtemt nnes, u zi řebhayem n řeḥram tyuya, awtem d tewtemt nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:2 \xt Lawi 11. \x*  
\v 3 Uřa zeg ijḍaḍ n ujenna ittxeṣṣa ad teksid sebɛa n tiyuyawin, awtem d tewtemt, ḥima ad teḥḍid zzariɛet \add nsen\add* i tudart di marra tammurt,  
\v 4 minzi xmi ɣa ɛdun ɛad sebɛa n wussan Necc ad jjeɣ anẓar ad iwwet x temmurt arebɛin n wussan d arebɛin n ǧyaři, uca ad teḥḥiɣ zeg wudem n temmurt marra min iǧan, d min ggiɣ Necc.”  
\v 5 Uca igga Nuḥ am mammec kuřci i xef t iweṣṣa SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 7:5 \xt Amz. 6:22. \x*   
\m
\v 6 Tuɣa Nuḥ d mmis n setta-mya n iseggʷusa řami dd-tusa sseḥřet n waman x temmurt.  
\v 7 Uca yudef Nuḥ ɣar uɣarrabu di ssibbet n waman n sseḥřet, \add netta d\add* iḥenjiren nnes d temɣart nnes d temɣarin n iḥenjiren nnes akides. \x ◘ \xo 7:7 \xt Mt. 24:38; Lk. 17:27; 1 Bṭ. 3:20. \x*  
\v 8 Zi řebhayem n řeḥřař u zi řebhayem n řeḥram u zeg ijḍaḍ u zi marra min ittbuɛen x \add wudem n\add* temmurt  
\v 9 tudef tyuya s tyuya ɣar Nuḥ ɣar uɣarrabu, awtem d tewtemt am mammec iweṣṣa AREBBI i Nuḥ.   
\m
\v 10 Awarni sebɛa n wussan imsar belli aman n sseḥřet usin-dd x temmurt.  
\v 11 Deg useggʷas wiss setta-mya zi tudart n Nuḥ, deg uyur wiss tnayen, deg wass wiss sbeɛṭac n uyur \add nni\add*, deg wass-a nnit, tuɣa ssefyen-dd marra řɛunṣarat n \add waman\add* ihewřen uca ttwarezment tburjatin n ujenna.  
\v 12 Tuɣa anẓar iqqim iccat s jjehd x temmurt arebɛin n wussan d arebɛin n ǧyaři.   
\m
\v 13 Deg wass nni \add nnit\add* tuɣa Nuḥ yudef ɣar uɣarrabu ak-d Cam d Ḥam d Yafat, ayt n Nuḥ, uřa ak-d tamɣart n Nuḥ u ak-d třata n temɣarin n iḥenjiren nnes akidsen,  
\v 14 nitni d marra markat n řmař \add n řexřa\add* d marra markat n řebhayem d marra markat n \add imuddaren\add* nni ittbuɛen x temmurt d marra markat n ijḍaḍ, marra ajḍiḍ, d marra \add min ɣar iǧa\add* afriwen.  
\v 15 Zi marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum i di iǧa arruḥ n tudart, tusa-dd tyuya s tyuya ɣar Nuḥ ɣar uɣarrabu.  
\v 16 U zi marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum i dd-yusin, yudef ijj n wewtem d ict n tewtemt am mammec \add t\add* yumur AREBBI, uca iqqen SIDI \add tawwart\add* awarni as.  
\v 17 Tuɣa sseḥřet x temmurt arebɛin n wussan uca geɛɛden waman uca ssgeɛɛden aɣarrabu ařami igeɛɛed sennej i \add wudem n\add* temmurt.  
\v 18 Geɛɛden waman uca mmarenyen-dd aṭṭas sennej i temmurt uca yuyur uɣarrabu x wudem n waman.  
\v 19 Geɛɛden aman aṭṭas s waṭṭas, ařami marra idurar yuɛřan i din iǧan sadu marra ajenna, dewřen dřin.  
\v 20 Uřyen waman xemmesṭac n iɣaǧen sennej i idurar uca dřin idurar.  
\v 21 Marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum i ittenhezzan x temmurt iḍřeq i buḥbeř nnes, ijḍaḍ d řebhayem, řmař \add n řexřa\add*, marra \add imuddaren\add* ittbuɛen, inni ittbuɛen x wudem n temmurt uřa d marra iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 7:21 \xt Lk. 17:27. \x*  
\v 22 Marra min di iǧa řeɛwin n arruḥ n tudart ɣarsen deg wenzaren nsen zi marra min din \add iǧan\add* x řbarr, immut.  
\v 23 Uca marra min din iǧan x wudem n temmurt ittwamḥa, zi bnadem ař řmař d imuddaren inni ittbuɛen d ijḍaḍ n ujenna. Ina ttwateḥḥan zi temmurt. Nuḥ weḥḥdes i iqqimen d marra min kides i iǧan deg uɣarrabu. \x ◘ \xo 7:23 \xt 2 Bṭ. 2:5. \x*  
\v 24 Geɛɛden waman x temmurt mya u-xemsin n wussan.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\m
\v 1 Uca ixarreṣ AREBBI di Nuḥ u di marra řmař \add n řexřa\add* d marra řebhayem i tuɣa akides deg uɣarrabu. Igga AREBBI ad yekk ijj n usemmiḍ x temmurt ařami arsan waman.  
\v 2 Bellɛent řɛunṣarat n \add waman\add* ihewřen d tburjatin n ujenna uca ibedd wenẓar zeg ujenna.  
\v 3 Uca, am dd-ttasen ttraḥen, dewřen-dd waman zi temmurt. Awarni mya u-xemsin n wussan neqṣen waman.  
\v 4 Deg uyur wiss sebɛa, deg wass wiss sbeɛṭac n uyur \add nni\add*, yarsa uɣarrabu x idurar n Ararat.  
\v 5 Qqimen waman neqqṣen ař ayur wiss ɛecra. Deg uyur wiss ɛecra, deg \add wass\add* amezwaru n uyur, ḍharent-i-dd tqiccatin n idurar.   
\m
\v 6 Awarni řami ɛdun arebɛin n wussan, yarzem Nuḥ taburjet n uɣarrabu nni \add dayes\add* tuɣa igga,  
\v 7 uca issekk abaɣeř. Wanita iffeɣ, iqqim ittraḥ ittas-dd ařami bdan waman ttaẓɣen x temmurt.  
\v 8 Xenni issekk ssenni tadbirt, ḥima ad iẓar, ma aman neqṣen x wudem n temmurt.  
\v 9 \add Maca\add* war tufi tedbirt mani ɣa tessars tařeqqa n uḍar nnes uca teɛqeb-dd ɣares ɣar uɣarrabu, minzi aman tuɣa aten \add ɛad\add* x wudem n marra tammurt. Isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes, iṭṭef i-tt uca issidef i-tt-i-dd ɣares deg uɣarrabu.  
\v 10 Iraja ɛad sebɛa n wussan nneɣni, \add xenni\add* issekk tadbirt ɛawed zeg uɣarrabu.  
\v 11 Uca tadbirt teɛqeb-dd ɣares ɣar tmeddit, u xzar, aqa afar n zzitun deg uqemmum nnes. \add Xenni\add* ifhem Nuḥ belli aman neqṣen zi temmurt.  
\v 12 Iraja ɛad sebɛa n wussan, \add xenni\add* issekk tadbirt \add ɛawed\add* uca nettat war ɣares dd-teɛqib ɛad.  
\v 13 Deg useggʷas wiss setta-mya u-waḥit \add n Nuḥ\add*, deg \add uyur\add* amezwaru, deg \add wass\add* amezwaru n uyur nni, uẓɣen waman x temmurt. Iksi Nuḥ \add tawwart n\add* useqqaf n uɣarrabu, ixzar ɣar barra, uca xzar, udem n temmurt aqa yuẓeɣ.  
\v 14 Deg uyur wiss tnayen, deg wass wiss sebɛa u-ɛicrin n uyur \add nni\add*, tuẓeɣ temmurt.   
\m
\v 15 Xenni issiweř AREBBI ak-d Nuḥ, inna:  
\v 16 “Ffeɣ zeg uɣarrabu, cek d temɣart nnec d iḥenjiren nnec d temɣarin n iḥenjiren nnec akidek.  
\v 17 Marra min iddaren i iǧan akidek, zi marra min ɣarsen arrimet n weysum, zeg ijḍaḍ, zi řmař u zi marra \add imuddaren\add* nni ittbuɛen x temmurt, ejj i-ten ad ffɣen akidek, ejj i-ten ad mṭarracen x temmurt, ad arren řɣiǧet uca ad mmarenyen x temmurt.” \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt Amz. 1:22, 28; 9:1. \x*  
\v 18 Iffeɣ Nuḥ d iḥenjiren nnes d temɣart nnes d temɣarin n iḥenjiren nnes akides.  
\v 19 Marra řmař \add n řexřa\add*, marra min ittbuɛen, d marra ijḍaḍ, d marra min ittenhezzan x temmurt ffɣen zeg uɣarrabu ɛlaḥṣab řaǧat nsen.   
\m
\v 20 Ibna Nuḥ ijj n uɛalṭar i SIDI uca iksi zi marra řmař n řeḥřař u zi marra ijḍaḍ n řeḥřař uca iqeddem tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ x uɛalṭar. \f ◼ \fr 8:20 \ft \+fk aɛalṭar\ft - niɣ ‘řmedbeḥ’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 8:20 \xt Lawi 11. \x*  
\v 21 Uca icemm SIDI řefwaḥet ittfuḥen uca inna SIDI deg wuř nnes: “War ttɛiqqibeɣ ɛad ad neɛřeɣ tammurt x ssibbet n bnadem, minzi min dd-itteffɣen zeg wuř n bnadem d aɛeffan waha zi temẓi nnes. War ttɛiqqibeɣ ɛad ad wteɣ marra min iddaren am mammec ggiɣ. \x ◘ \xo 8:21 \xt Amz. 6:5; Awřn. 22:15; Mt. 15:19. Mk. 7:21-23\x*  
\v 22 Marra ussan i ɣa teqqim temmurt teǧa, ad tiři tyarza d tmeyra, teṣmeḍ d řeḥmu, anebdu d řmecta uca ass d ǧiřet war ttbeddin \add ɛemmarṣ\add*.” \f ◼ \fr 8:22 \ft \+fk tayarza\ft  - niɣ ‘amud’. \fk tameyra\ft  - niɣ ‘tafersit’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 8:22 \xt Irm. 33:20, 25. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Řɛahd n Arebbi ak-d Nuḥ  
\m
\v 1 Xenni ibarek AREBBI Nuḥ d iḥenjiren nnes uca inna asen: “Jjem-dd řɣiǧet, marenyem u ɛemmarem tammurt! \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt Amz. 1:28; 8:17. \x*  
\v 2 Tiggʷudi d řɛurret zi kenniw ad iřint x marra řmař \add n řexřa\add*, x marra ijḍaḍ n ujenna u x marra min ittbuɛen x temmurt u x marra iseřman di řebḥar: aqa mmewcen deg ufus nwem.  
\v 3 Marra min ittbuɛen, min iddaren, ad awem yiři d macca. Necc ad awem t wceɣ marra, am d awem wciɣ afsu aziza, \x ◘ \xo 9:3 \xt Amz. 1:29. \x*  
\v 4 maca aysum ak-d buḥbeř nnes i iǧan d idammen nnes, war \add ten\add* ttᵉttem. \x ◘ \xo 9:4 \xt Lawi 3:17; 7:26; 17:14; 19:26; Aɛwd. 12:23. \x*  
\v 5 D tidett ad ttareɣ idammen nwem n řeɛmur nwem, ad ten ttareɣ zeg ifassen n marra imuddaren, uřa zeg ifassen n bnadem, u zeg ifassen n umas n kuř ijjen ad ttareɣ řeɛmar n bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Uf. 21:12, 28. \x*  
\v 6 Wi ɣa issizzřen idammen n bnadem, idammen nnes ad ten ssizzřen s ufus n bnadem, minzi AREBBI igga bnadem di ṣṣifet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt Amz. 1:27; Igjd. 4:13; Mt. 26:52; Asa. 13:10. \x*  
\v 7 U kenniw, jjem-dd řɣiǧet, dewřem deg waṭṭas, mṭarrcem di temmurt uca dewřem deg waṭṭas xas.” \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Amz. 1:28; 8:17. \x*   
\m
\v 8 Uca issiweř AREBBI ak-d Nuḥ d iḥenjiren nnes nni ɣares, inna:  
\v 9 “Necc, xzar, Necc tteggeɣ Řɛahd inu akidwem u ak-d zzariɛet nwem awarni awem, \x ◘ \xo 9:9 \xt Ica. 54:9. \x*  
\v 10 u ak-d marra buḥbeř iddaren nni iǧan akidwem, ak-d ijḍaḍ, ak-d řmař u ak-d marra řmař \add n řexřa\add* x temmurt inni akidwem, \add wah, ak-d\add* marra min dd-iffɣen zeg uɣarrabu ař marra min iddaren x temmurt.  
\v 11 Ad ggeɣ Řɛahd inu akidwem, aqa marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum war ttwakessin ɛad s waman n sseḥřet, u war din tᵉttiři ɛad sseḥřet i ɣa yareddǧen tammurt.”  
\v 12 Xenni inna AREBBI: “D ta ad tiři d řeɛřamet n Řɛahd tenni i ɣa ggeɣ jar ayi d kenniw d marra řeɛmar iddaren akidwem, i \add marra\add* jjiřat \add i\add* řebda:  
\v 13 Ad ggeɣ řqews inu deg iseynuten wenni i ɣa yiřin d řeɛřamet n Řɛahd jar ayi d temmurt.  
\v 14 Xmi ɣa bḍiɣ iseynuten x temmurt, xenni ad imsar belli řqews-a ad dd-iḍhar deg iseynuten.  
\v 15 Xenni ad idareɣ Řɛahd inu jar ayi d kenniw d marra řeɛmar iddaren n marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum. War dd-ddikkʷiřen waman d sseḥřet ɛawed, maḥend ad ssɣarqen marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum.  
\v 16 Ad dd-iḍhar řqews deg iseynuten, uca Necc ad t ẓareɣ ḥima ad idareɣ Řɛahd i řebda jar AREBBI d marra řeɛmar iddaren di marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum i iǧan x temmurt.”  
\v 17 Uca inna AREBBI i Nuḥ: “D ta d řeɛřamet n Řɛahd inu wenni i ɣa ggeɣ jar ayi d marra imeddaren s arrimet n weysum i iǧan x temmurt.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tarwa n Nuḥ  
\m
\v 18 Tarwa n Nuḥ inni dd-iffɣen zeg uɣarrabu \add tuɣa aten d\add* Cam d Ḥam d Yafat. Ḥam tuɣa d babas n Kenɛan. \f ◼ \fr 9:18 \ft \+fk Kenɛan\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘tammurt iwaṭan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 9:18 \xt Amz. 6:10. \x*  
\v 19 Ina d třata n iḥenjiren n Nuḥ. Zzaysen ttwabezzɛen \add iwdan\add* di marra tammurt.  
\v 20 Ibda Nuḥ \add ixeddem\add* am ufeǧaḥ, iẓẓu tizayarin deg umarjeɛ n uḍiř.  
\v 21 \add Umi\add* iswa binu, iscar uca iɛarra ixef nnes di řwesṭ n uqiḍun nnes.  
\v 22 Iẓra Ḥam, babas n Kenɛan, tuɛɛaryent n babas uca inna t i tnayen n aytmas di barra.  
\v 23 Ksin Cam d Yafat ca n werruḍ, ssarsen t x tɣarḍin n tnayen idsen nsen uca uyuren ɣar ḍeffar, dřin tuɛɛaryent n babatsen. Arrin aɣembub nsen ɣar ḍeffar, war ẓrin ca tuɛɛaryent n babatsen.  
\v 24 Ifaq-dd Nuḥ zi ssekra nnes uca idweř yargeb x min d as igga mmis amaẓuẓ.  
\v 25 Inna: “D amenɛuř \add i yeǧa\add* Kenɛan! Ad yiři d amsexxar \add qaɛ\add* n imsexxaren i aytmas!”  
\v 26 Uca inna: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI n Cam. Kenɛan ad yiři d amsexxar i nitni.  
\v 27 Zeɛma ad iwesseɛ AREBBI tazeddiɣt i Yafat, ad izdeɣ deg iqiḍan n Cam, u Kenɛan ad asen yiři d amsexxar.”  
\v 28 Awarni sseḥřet iddar Nuḥ \add ɛad\add* teřt-mya u-xemsin n iseggʷusa.  
\v 29 Ammu i iddar Nuḥ tesɛa-mya u-xemsin n iseggʷusa, xenni immut.  
\m \bd Ina d imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen zeg ayt n Nuḥ:\bd* Cam, Ḥam d Yafat.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\s1 Tarwa n Cam, Xam d Yafit  
\m
\v 1 Ttwarwen asen-dd iḥenjiren awarni i sseḥřet. \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt [1 Im. 1:1-27] — 1 Im. 1:4\x*  *   
\b  
\m
\v 2 \bd Ayt n Yafat\bd* \add tuɣa aten d\add* Jumar, Majuj, Maday, Yawan, Tubal, Macik d Tiras. \f ◼ \fr 10:2 \ft \+fk Jumar\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni břa řɛib’ niɣ ‘wenni ikemřen’. \fk Majuj\ft  - niɣ ‘Maxux’, niɣ ‘Magug’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:2 \xt 1 Im. 1:5. \x*   
\m
\v 3 Iḥenjiren n Jumar, \add tuɣa aten d\add* Ackanaz, Rifat d Tujarma.   
\m
\v 4 Iḥenjiren n Yawan \add tuɣa aten d\add* Ilica, Tarcic d Ikittiyyen d Idudaniyyen. \f ◼ \fr 10:4 \ft \+fk Ikittiyyen d Idudaniyen\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘tiqebbař n Kit d Dudan’.\f*   
\m
\v 5 Zzaysen i ttwabḍant tegzirin n řegnus di temmura nsen, kuř ijjen ɛlaḥsab iřes nnes uca \add marra\add* ɛlaḥsab řaǧ nsen u di řegnus nsen.   
\b  
\m
\v 6 \bd Ayt n Ḥam\bd* \add tuɣa aten d\add* Kuc, Miṣrayim, Fuṭ d Kenɛan. \x ◘ \xo 10:6 \xt 1 Im. 1:8. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Iḥenjiren n Kuc \add tuɣa aten d\add* Seba, Ḥawila, Sabta, Raɛama d Sabtaka. Iḥenjiren n Raɛama \add tuɣa aten d\add* Caba d Dadan.   
\m
\v 8 Kuc ijja-dd Nimrud. Wanita ibda ad yiři d jjiheř di temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 10:8 \xt 1 Im. 1:10. \x*  
\v 9 Wa tuɣa d anegmar d ameqqran zzat i wudem n SIDI. X uya qqaren: ‘Anegmar ameqqran am Nimrud zzat i wudem n SIDI.’  
\v 10 Amezwar n tgeldit nnes tuɣa atent \add d tineddam n\add* Babil d Irix d Akkad d Kalna di temmurt n Cinɛar.  
\v 11 Zi temmurt nni dd-iffeɣ ɣar Accur uca ibna \add din\add* Ninwa, Riḥubut-Ɛir d Kalaḥ  
\v 12 d Risin jar Ninwa d Kalaḥ, nettat d tandint tameqqrant.   
\m
\v 13 Miṣrayim ijja-dd Iludiyyen, Iɛanamiyyen, Ilahabiyyen, Inaftuḥiyyen,   
\m
\v 14 Ifatrusiyyen, Ikasluḥiyyen, inni zi dd-iqqarṣen Ifilisṭiniyyen, uřa d Ikafturiyyen.   
\m
\v 15 Kenɛan ijja-dd Ṣidun, amenzu nnes, d Ḥit  
\v 16 d Uyabusi d Umuri d Ujirjaci  
\v 17 d Uḥiwi d Uɛarqi d Usini  
\v 18 d Urwadi d Uṣamari d Uḥamati. Awarni as mbezzɛent marra řaǧat n Kenɛan.  
\v 19 Tuɣa aymir n ayt n Kenɛan zi Ṣidun ɣar Xirar ař Ɣazza \add u\add* ssenni ɣar Sadum d Ɛamurra d Adma d Ṣabuyim ař Lacaɛ. \f ◼ \fr 10:19 \ft \+fk Xirar\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘amcan i inewjiwen’. \fk Ɣazza\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘jjehd’. \fk Adma\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘tammurt tazeggʷaɣt’. \fk Ṣabuyim\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘iɣayḍen n wezɣar’ niɣ ‘aẓri n weẓri’ niɣ ‘iɛebbuzen’ niɣ ‘tandint n řɛeskar’.\f*   
\m
\v 20 Ina d ayt n Ḥam ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, ɛlaḥsab iřsawen nsen, di timmura nsen u ak-d řegnus nsen.   
\b  
\m
\v 21 I \bd Cam\bd*, wenni d jedd n marra ayt n Ɛabir, umas n Yafat, ameqqran, ttwarwen as-dd ɛawed iḥenjiren.  
\v 22 Iḥenjiren n Cam \add tuɣa aten d\add* Ɛilam, Accur, Arfakcad, Lud d Aram. \x ◘ \xo 10:22 \xt Amz. 11:10; 1 Im. 1:17. \x*   
\m
\v 23 Iḥenjiren n Aram \add tuɣa aten d\add* Ɛuṣ d Ḥul d Jatir d Mac.   
\m
\v 24 Arfakcad ijja-dd Calaḥ u Calaḥ ijja-dd Ɛabir. \x ◘ \xo 10:24 \xt 1 Im. 1:18. \x*   
\m
\v 25 Ttwarwen-dd i Ɛabir tnayen n iḥenjiren. Ijjen qqaren as Falaj, minzi deg wussan nnes tᵉttwafeǧeq temmurt, u qqaren as i umas Yuqṭan. \f ◼ \fr 10:25 \ft \+fk Falaj\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘abeṭṭu’ niɣ ‘afeǧeq’. \fk tettwafeǧeq\ft  - awař-a izemmar ad iceyyar ɣar (1) ubeṭṭu n iwdan umi SIDI ibeṭṭa iřes nsen uca dewřen nitni ad ssiwřen ɛřam kuř iřsawen jar asen (xzar Amz. 11:1-9), niɣ ɣar (2) ubeṭṭu n umaḍal (niɣ ‘ddunnit’) deg iziynan, ixs ad yini Amrika, Ifriqiyya, Asiya, Ustraliya d Urupa, maɣar deg umezwaru tuɣa tammurt d ijj n wemcan (xzar Amz. 1:9, 10). \fk Yuqṭan\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘ameẓyan’.\f*   
\m
\v 26 Yuqṭan ijja-dd Almudad, Calaf, Haḍarmawt, Yaraḥ,  
\v 27 Haduram, Uzal, Diqla,  
\v 28 Ɛubal, Abimayil, Caba,  
\v 29 Ufir, Ḥawila d Yubab. Marra ina \add tuɣa aten d\add* iḥenjiren n Yuqṭan.  
\v 30 Tammurt mani tuɣa zeddɣen \add tuɣa-tt\add* zi Mica ař Safar, adrar n ccarq.   
\m
\v 31 Ina d ayt n Cam ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen u ɛlaḥsab iřsawen nsen, di temmura nsen u ak-d řegnus nsen.   
\b  
\m
\v 32 Tina d řaǧat n iḥenjiren n Nuḥ, ɛlaḥsab mammec dd-xeřqen, ak-d řegnus nsen. Zzaysen i zi ttwabḍan řegnus di temmurt awarni i sseḥřet. *   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Ṣṣumɛet n Babil  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa marra tammurt s yiřes d ijjen u s řhard d ijjen.  
\v 2 Imsar řami fesyen iqiḍan nsen \add uca ffɣen-dd\add* zi ccarq, ufin ijj n řewḍa di temmurt n Cinɛar, uca \add qqimen\add* zeddɣen dinni. \x ◘ \xo 11:2 \xt Amz. 10:10. \x*  
\v 3 Nitni nnan, kuř ijj i wenneɣni: “Araḥem-dd, ad negg iẓra zi třaxt, ad ten nesseḥma!” Ammu i d asen tedweř třaxt d aẓru u acarmuḍ \add idweř\add* ɣarsen d tarrist.  
\v 4 \add Xas\add* uca nnan: “Zid, ad nebna ict n tendint d ict n ṣṣumɛet, taqiccat nnes \add ad dd-taweḍ\add* ɣar ujenna, u jjem aneɣ ad negg ijj n yisem i neccin, ḥima war nᵉttemsebḍi ca x wudem n marra tammurt.” \x ◘ \xo 11:4 \xt Aɛwd. 1:28\x*   
\m
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* ihwa-dd SIDI, ḥima ad iẓar tandint d ṣṣumɛet nni bnan tarwa n bnadem.  
\v 6 Inna SIDI: “Xzar, aqa aten d řgens d ijjen u marra ina ɣarsen ijj n yiřes. Wa d beddu n min ɣa ggen. Řexxu war din min ten i ɣa issbedden x webrid nsen nni nwan ad ggen.  
\v 7 Araḥem-dd, ad nehwa uca ad nessxarweḍ iřes nsen, ḥima kuř ijjen war ifehhem \add ɛad\add* iřes n wenni t yudsen.”  
\v 8 Ammu i ten izzuzar SIDI ssenni x wudem n marra tammurt uca ssbedden řebni n tendint. \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Aɛwd. 32:8; Řex. 17:26. \x*  
\v 9 X uya i d as řaɣan \add i tendint nni\add* s yisem n ‘Babil’, minzi din issxarweḍ SIDI iřes n marra tammurt u ssenni i ten izzuzar SIDI x wudem n marra tammurt.  
\m \bd Ina d imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen \+bdit zi\+bdit* Cam.\bd* \f ◼ \fr 11:9 \ft \+fk Babil\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘axarweḍ’ niɣ ‘Arebbi issxarwaḍ’.\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tarwa n Cam  
\m
\v 10 Umi tuɣa ɣar Cam mya n iseggʷusa, ijja-dd \bd Arfakcad\bd*, tnayen n iseggʷusa awarni i sseḥřet. \f ◼ \fr 11:10 \ft \+bd afessar\+bd* - deg wedlis Amezwaru 5:32 neqqar aqa Cam ittwaxeřqed-dd awarni řami tuɣa Nuḥ ɣares 500 n iseggʷusa. Deg useggʷas wiss setta mya n tudart n Nuḥ tebda sseḥret (Amz. 7:11). Tuɣa tusa-dd sseḥřet ijj n useggʷas x temmurt. Ak-d ineɣmisen i nufa deg wawařen n aya-ya nessen aqa Nuḥ tuɣa ɣares 502 n iseggʷusa řami dd-ittwaxeřq Cam. \fk Cam\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘isem’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:10 \xt [1 Im. 1:1-27] — Amz. 10:22-31; 1 Im. 1:17. \x*  
\v 11 Awarni řami dd-ijja Arfakcad, iddar Cam \add ɛad\add* xemsa-mya n iseggʷusa, uca ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin. \f ◼ \fr 11:11 \ft \+bd afessar\+bd* - aqa Cam idweř ɣares 600 n iseggʷusa. S uyenni tuɣa ɛad iddar řami tuɣa Ibrahim ɣares 50 n iseggʷusa.\f*   
\m
\v 12 Iddar Arfakcad xemsa u-třatin n iseggʷusa, \add xenni\add* ijja-dd \bd Calaḥ\bd*. \f ◼ \fr 11:12 \ft \+fk Calaḥ\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘řesnaḥ’ niɣ ‘arraw’.\f*  
\v 13 Awarni řami dd-ijja Arfakcad Calaḥ, iddar \add ɛad\add* arebɛa-mya u-třata n iseggʷusa, uca ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.   
\m
\v 14 Iddar Calaḥ třatin n iseggʷusa, \add xenni\add* ijja-dd \bd Ɛabir\bd*. \f ◼ \fr 11:14 \ft \+fk Ɛabir\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘tammurt n ujemmaḍ’.\f*  
\v 15 Awarni řami dd-ijja Calaḥ Ɛabir, iddar \add ɛad\add* arebɛa-mya u-třata n iseggʷusa, uca ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.   
\m
\v 16 Iddar Ɛabir arebɛa u-třatin n iseggʷusa, \add xenni\add* ijja-dd \bd Falaj\bd*. \f ◼ \fr 11:16 \ft \+fk Falaj\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘abeṭṭu’ niɣ ‘afeǧeq’.\f*  
\v 17 Awarni řami dd-ijja Falaj, iddar Ɛabir \add ɛad\add* arebɛa-mya u-třatin n iseggʷusa, uca ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.   
\m
\v 18 Iddar Falaj třatin n iseggʷusa, \add xenni\add* ijja-dd \bd Raɛuw\bd*. \f ◼ \fr 11:18 \ft \+fk Raɛuw\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘ameddukkeř’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:18 \xt 1 Im. 1:25 \x*  
\v 19 Awarni řami dd-ijja Raɛuw, iddar Falaj \add ɛad\add* mitayen u-tesɛa n iseggʷusa, uca ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.   
\m
\v 20 Iddar Raɛuw tnayen u-třatin n iseggʷusa, \add xenni\add* ijja-dd \bd Saruj\bd*.\f ◼ \fr 11:20 \ft \+fk Saruj\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘taseṭṭa’ niɣ ‘řfarɛ’.\f*  
\v 21 Awarni řami dd-ijja Saruj, iddar Raɛuw \add ɛad\add* mitayen u-sebɛa n iseggʷusa, uca ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.   
\m
\v 22 Iddar Saruj třatin n iseggʷusa, \add xenni\add* ijja-dd \bd Naḥur\bd*.\f ◼ \fr 11:22 \ft \+fk Naḥur\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘aneffeḥ yuǧɣen’.\f*  
\v 23 Awarni řami dd-ijja Naḥur, iddar Saruj \add ɛad\add* mitayen n iseggʷusa, uca ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.   
\m
\v 24 Iddar Naḥur tesɛa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa, \add xenni\add* ijja-dd \bd Taraḥ\bd*.\f ◼ \fr 11:24 \ft \+fk Taraḥ\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘amcan n wareyyeḥ’.\f*  
\v 25 Awarni řami dd-ijja Naḥur Taraḥ, iddar \add ɛad\add* mya u-tesɛaṭac n iseggʷusa, uca ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.   
\m
\v 26 Iddar Taraḥ sebɛin n iseggʷusa, \add xenni\add* ijja-dd \bd Abram\bd*, Naḥur d Haran.  
\m \bd Ina d imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen \+bdit zi\+bdit* Taraḥ.\bd* \f ◼ \fr 11:26 \ft \+fk Abram\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘tababat iɛuǧen’ niɣ ‘babas n Aram’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 27 Taraḥ ijja-dd Abram, Naḥur d Haran, u Haran ijja-dd Luṭ. \x ◘ \xo 11:27 \xt Yac. 24:2; 1 Im. 1:26. \x*  
\v 28 Immut Haran zzat i babas Taraḥ di temmurt mani dd-ixřeq netta, di Ur n Ikaldaniyyen.  
\v 29 Uca ksin Abram d Naḥur i yixef nsen timɣarin. Isem n temɣart n Abram tuɣa-t d Saray u isem n temɣart n Naḥur d Milka, yeǧis n Haran, babas n Milka d Yiska. \x ◘ \xo 11:29 \xt Amz. 22:12; 22:20. \x*  
\v 30 Saray tuɣa-tt war dd-tᵉttiruw, tuɣa war ɣares bu uḥenjir. \x ◘ \xo 11:30 \xt Amz. 16:1, 2; 18:11, 12. \x*  
\v 31 Uca iksi Taraḥ Abram, mmis, d Luṭ mmis n Haran, mmis n mmis, d Saray, tasřit nnes, tamɣart n mmis Abram, uca nitni ffɣen jmiɛ zi Ur n Ikaldaniyyen, ḥima ad raḥen ɣar temmurt n Kenɛan. Iwḍen ɣar Ḥaran uca zeddɣen dinni. \f ◼ \fr 11:31 \ft \+fk Ikaldaniyyen\ft  - Ikaldaniyyen tuɣa zeddɣen di jjwayeh n Ur, ict n tendint di tgeldit n Misuputamiya. Deg wussan-a nessen belli jjwayeh n Misuputamiya aqa-tent d ccamal n Lɛiraq. Ař i řexxu aṭṭas n iwdan di ccamal n Lɛiraq ssawařen s tutlayt n Tkaldanit.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:31 \xt Yac. 24:2; Naḥ. 9:7; Řex. 7:4. \x*  
\v 32 Umi tegga Taraḥ mitayen u-xemsa n iseggʷusa, immut Taraḥ di Ḥaran.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Tařaɣit n Arebbi x Abram  
\m
\v 1 Inna SIDI i Abram: “Ffeɣ zi temmurt nnec, zi temmurt mani dd-txeřqed u zi taddart n babac, ruḥ ɣar temmurt i d ac ɣa ssecneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt Řex. 7:3; Ɛbr. 11:8. \x*  
\v 2 Ad zzayek dd-ssuffɣeɣ ijj n řgens imɣar, ad cek barkeɣ u ad ssemɣareɣ isem nnec uca iři d cek \add ɛawed\add* d lbaraka.  
\v 3 Ad barkeɣ wenni cek i ɣa ibarken d wenni cek i ɣa ineɛřen, ad t neɛřeɣ. Dayek i ɣa ttwabarkent marra řaǧat n temmurt.” \x ◘ \xo 12:3 \xt Amz. 18:18; 22:18; 26:4; Řex. 3:25; Gal. 3:8. \x*  *   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Uca iruḥ Abram am mammec d as inna SIDI, uca iruḥ Lut akides. Tuɣa Abram ɣares xemsa u-sebɛin n iseggʷusa umi dd-iffeɣ zi Ḥaran.  
\v 5 Uca indeh Abram Saray tamɣart nnes, d Luṭ mmis n umas, d marra agřa i yarebḥen, d iwdan d řmař nni dd-kesben di Ḥaran. Ffɣen \add zi Ḥaran\add* ḥima ad raḥen ɣar temmurt n Kenɛan uca iwḍen ɣar temmurt n Kenɛan. \x ◘ \xo 12:5 \xt Řex. 7:4. \x*  
\v 6 Iẓwa Abram zi temmurt nni ɣar wemcan n Cakim ař tacejjart n yigg n Mura. Di řweqt nni tuɣa ayt n Kenɛan \add zeddɣen\add* di temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 12:6 \ft \+fk Cakim\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘taɣruḍt’ niɣ ‘aɛrur’. \fk tacejjart n yigg\ft  - niɣ ‘ibejji’. Isem nnes s tlatinit ‘Pistacia Terebintus’, xzar Amawal Amecṭuḥ n Omar Kerdja (424, 437).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:6 \xt Amz. 10:18, 19; 13:7. \x*  
\v 7 Iban-dd SIDI i Abram, inna as: “I zzariɛet nnec umi i ɣa wceɣ tammurt-a.” Uca ibna din ijj n uɛalṭar \add min xef issars taɣarṣt\add* i SIDI, wenni d as dd-ibanen. \f ◼ \fr 12:7 \ft \+fk aɛalṭar\ft - niɣ ‘řmedbeḥ’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:7 \xt Amz. 13:15; 15:18; 17:8; 24:7; 26:4; Aɛwd. 34:4. \x*   
\m
\v 8 Xenni iɛdu ssenni ɣar idurar i iǧan x ccarq n Bayt-Il uca iwta dinni iqiḍan nnes, ijja Bayt-Il x jjihet n řɣarb u Ɛay x ccarq. Din ibna ijj n uɛalṭar i SIDI uca iřaɣa Isem n SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 12:8 \ft \+fk Bayt-Il\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘taddart n Arebbi’. \fk Ɛay\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘řxarbet’.\f*   
\m
\v 9 Awarni man aya ifsi Abram iqiḍan nnes, immuṭṭi \add zeg wemcan ɣar wemcan\add*, ɣar \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Abram di Miṣra  
\m
\v 10 Idweř řaẓ di temmurt uca ikemmeř Abram x webrid nnes, ihwa ɣar Miṣra, ḥima ad izdeɣ din am ubarrani, minzi \add tuɣa\add* řaẓ imɣar di temmurt.  
\v 11 Řami dd-tiweḍ řweqt nni umi i ɣa yudef ɣar Miṣra, inna i Saray, tamɣart nnes: “Xzar, aqa ssneɣ belli cem d tamɣart dayes aẓri.  
\v 12 Xmi cem i ɣa ẓaren Imiṣriyyen, zemmaren ad inin: ‘Ta d tamɣart nnes!’, ad ayi nɣen uca ad cem jjen di tudart.  
\v 13 Ini, aqa cem d učma, ḥima ad ayi yiři řxir di ṭṭweɛ nnem uca ad iqqim řeɛmar inu iddar i cem.” \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt Amz. 20:12; 26:7. \x*   
\m
\v 14 Imsar umi yudef Abram ɣar Miṣra, ẓrin Imiṣriyyen belli tamɣart teṣbeḥ aṭṭas.  
\v 15 Uřa d řḥukkam n firɛun, \add ajeǧid\add*, ẓrin tt uca ssemɣaren tt ɣar Firɛun uca iwyen tt ɣar taddart n firɛun.  
\v 16 Uca imṣuref \add Firɛun\add* mlih ak-d Abram di ṭṭweɛ nnes. \add Ammu\add* i iksi uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin d yeɣyař d isemɣan d tiyya d teɣyař d iřeɣman. \f ◼ \fr 12:16 \ft \+fk iřeɣman\ft  - iřeɣman di Israil u di temmura nneɣni di Ccarq Ameřwasu d iřeɣman s yijj n tgeɛrurt waha.\f*  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* SIDI iwta firɛun d \add aytbab n\add* taddart nnes s jjrayeḥ mɣarent di řesbab n Saray, tamɣart n Abram. \x ◘ \xo 12:17 \xt Izhd. 105:14. \x*  
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* firɛun iřaɣa-dd i Abram, inna as: “Manawaya i dayi teggid? Maɣar war d ayi tennid belli nettat d tamɣart nnec?  
\v 19 Mayemmi tennid: ‘Nettat d učma!’, ařami tt ggiɣ necc d tamɣart i yixef inu? Řexxu xzar, aqa ac tamɣart nnec, ksi \add tt\add*, tbeɛɛded!”  
\v 20 Yumur firɛun iryazen nnes xas uca ssqebbḍen t ak-d temɣart nnes u ak-d marra min tuɣa ɣares.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Abram d Luṭ farqen  
\m
\v 1 Ammu i yuyur Abram zi Miṣra ɣar \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub \add n Kenɛan\add*, netta d temɣart nnes, ak-d marra min ɣares, d Luṭ akides.  
\v 2 Abram tuɣa ɣares aṭṭas n wagřa d řebhayem d nnuqart d wureɣ.  
\v 3 Uca immuṭṭi \add zeg wemcan ɣar wemcan\add* zi \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub ɣar Bayt-Il ař amcan mani tuɣa iǧa uqiḍun nnes qbeř, jar Bayt-Il d Ɛay, \x ◘ \xo 13:3 \xt Amz. 12:8. \x*  
\v 4 ař amcan n uɛalṭar i tuɣa igga qbeř, \add min xef issars tiɣarṣa d tewhibin\add*, uca dinni iřaɣa Abram Isem n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 13:4 \xt Amz. 4:26; 12:8. \x*  
\v 5 Uca Luṭ, wenni yuyuren ak-d Abram, tuɣa ɣares ɛawed uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin d iqiḍan.  
\v 6 Tammurt war d asen tiriw ḥima ad qqimen zeddɣen jmiɛ, minzi agřa nsen imɣar aṭṭas ař war zemmaren ad \add din\add* zedɣen jmiɛ. \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt Amz. 36:7. \x*  
\v 7 Uca imsar umcubbec jar imeksawen n řebhayem n Abram d imeksawen n řebhayem n Luṭ. Tuɣa ayt n Kenɛan d Ifiriziyyen zeddɣen řexdenni di temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 13:7 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 13:7 \xt Amz. 12:6. \x*  
\v 8 Inna Abram i Luṭ: “War ittiři ɛad umcubbec jar ayi d cek, jar imeksawen inu d imeksawen nnec, minzi neccin d iryazen awmaten.  
\v 9 Ma war tarzem temmurt zzatec? Ttzawgeɣ cek ad xafi tebḍiḍ, ma x uzeřmaḍ, niɣ x yefus! Mařa cek truḥed x yefus, necc ad raḥeɣ x uzeřmaḍ.” \x ◘ \xo 13:9 \xt Amz. 20:15; 34:10. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Issgeɛɛed Luṭ tamuɣři nnes uca iẓra adewwar n \add yeɣzar n\add* L’Urdun tuɣa marra iswa. Qbeř areddeǧ zi SIDI tuɣa Sadum d Ɛamurra am jjennet n SIDI, am temmurt n Miṣra xmi dd ɣa tased ɣar Ṣuɣar.  
\v 11 Uca ixḍar Luṭ i yixef nnes marra adewwar n \add yeɣzar n\add* L’Urdun u ifsi Luṭ iqiḍan nnes \add uca yuyur\add* ɣar ccarq. \add Ammu i\add* mmsebḍan nitni ijjen x wenneɣni.   
\m
\v 12 Abram izdeɣ di temmurt n Kenɛan, \add maca\add* Luṭ izdeɣ di tneddam n udewwar \add n L’Urdun\add*, iwta iqiḍan nnes ař Sadum.  
\v 13 Iryazen n Sadum tuɣa aten d iɛeffanen d imednab ak-d SIDI ař ṭṭarf. \x ◘ \xo 13:13 \xt Amz. 18:20; Ḥiz. 16:49. \x*  
\v 14 Awarni řami xas immsebḍa Luṭ, inna SIDI i Abram: “Sarreḥ řexxu tiṭṭawin nnec, texzared zeg wemcan mani teǧid ɣar ccamal, ɣar ljanub, ɣar ccarq u ɣar řɣarb,  
\v 15 minzi marra tammurt i tᵉttwařid, ad ac tt wceɣ, i cek d zzariɛet nnec i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 13:15 \xt Amz. 12:7; 15:7, 18; 17:8; 26:4; Aɛwd. 34:4; Řex. 7:5. د\x*  
\v 16 Ad ggeɣ zzariɛet nnec am tɛejjajt n temmurt, ḥima, mařa izemmar ḥed ad iḥseb taɛejjajt n temmurt, uřa d zzariɛet nnec tzemmar ɛawed ad tᵉttwaḥseb. \x ◘ \xo 13:16 \xt Amz. 15:5; 17:4; Aɛwd. 10:22; Irm. 33:22; Rum. 4:17, 18; Ɛbr. 11:12. \x*  
\v 17 Kkar, cuq di temmurt di tuzzeggart nnes d tiru nnes, minzi i cek umi tt i ɣa wceɣ.”  
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* ikkes Abram iqiḍan nnes uca yuyur ad izdeɣ ɣar tcejjura n yigg n Mamri, inni iǧan di Ḥabrun. Dinni ibna ijj n uɛalṭar i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 13:18 \xt Amz. 14:13. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Abram ifekk Luṭ uca imsagar ak-d Malkiṣadiq  
\m
\v 1 Deg wussan n Amrafil, ajeǧid n Cinɛar, d Ariyuc, ajeǧid n Illasar, d Kidurlaɛumer, ajeǧid n Ɛilam, d Tidal, ajeǧid n řegnus, imsar belli  
\v 2 ina ggin řbaruḍ ak-d Bira, ajeǧid n Sadum u ak-d Bircaɛ, ajeǧid n Ɛamurra, u \add ak-d\add* Cinab, ajeǧid n Adma, u \add ak-d\add* Cim’ibar, ajeǧid n Ṣabuyim, u \add ak-d\add* ujeǧid n Bilaɛ, wenni iǧan d Ṣuɣar.  
\v 3 Marra ina munen di řewḍa n teɣzurt n Siddim, aqa d Řebḥar Ameǧaḥ. \f ◼ \fr 14:3 \ft \+fk Řebḥar Ameǧaḥ\ft  - niɣ ‘Ill Ameǧaḥ’.\f*  
\v 4 Tuɣa xeddmen tenɛac n iseggʷusa i Kidurlaɛumir, \add maca\add* ɣar useggʷas wiss třeṭṭac ɣewwɣen.  
\v 5 Uca deg useggʷas wiss arbeɛṭac yusa-dd Kidurlaɛumir d ijeǧiden i \add yeǧan\add* akides uca ɣeřben x Irafawiyyen di Actirut-Qarnaym, x Izuziyyen di Ham, x Imitiyyen di Cawa-Qaryatayim \f ◼ \fr 14:5 \ft \+fk Irafawiyyen\ft  - ijj n řgens n jjwaheř amecnaw Iɛanaqiyyen d Izuziyyen d Imiyyen. Isem wanita uřa d isem n marra řegnus-a inni jar asen jjwaheř.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 14:5 \xt Amz. 15:20; Aɛwd. 2:10, 11. \x*  
\v 6 u x Ixuriyyen deg idurar nsen n Saɛir ař Faran, wenni \add iǧan\add* zzat i řexřa.  
\v 7 \add Awarni aya\add* dewřen-dd, usin-dd ɣar Ɛayn-Micfat, wenni d Qadac, uca ɣeřben \add x yewdan nni izeddɣen di\add* marra tammurt n ayt n Ɛamaliq u ɛawed x Imuriyyen inni izeddɣen di Haṣṣun-Tamar. \f ◼ \fr 14:7 \ft \+fk Ɛayn-Micfat\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘anu n řḥukm’. \fk Kades\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘amqeddas’. \fk Haṣṣun-Tamar\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘azbar n tini’.\f*   
\m
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ ujeǧid n Sadum d ujeǧid n Ɛamurra d ujeǧid n Adma d ujeǧid n Ṣabuyim d ujeǧid n Bilaɛ, aqa-tt d Ṣuɣar. Ruḥen nitni ɣar řewḍa n teɣzurt n Siddim, maḥend ad mmenɣen  
\v 9 ak-d Kidurlaɛumir, ajeǧid n Ɛilam d Tidɛal, ajeǧid n řegnus, d Amrafil, ajeǧid n Cinɛar, d Aryuk, ajeǧid n Illasar: arebɛa n ijeǧiden \add ggin řbaruḍ\add* ak-d xemsa. \f ◼ \fr 14:9 \ft \+fk ajeǧid n Juyim\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘ajeǧid n řegnus’.\f*  
\v 10 Tuɣa řewḍa n teɣzurt n Siddim teccur s wanuten n tizeft. Uca arewřen ijeǧiden n Sadum d Ɛamurra uca wḍan daysen, u inni iqqimen arewřen ɣar idurar.  
\v 11 Ksin marra agřa n Sadum d Ɛamurra d marra macca i xeznen uca uyuren.  
\v 12 Ksin ɛawed Luṭ, mmis n umas n Abram, d wagřa nnes uca ruḥen. Netta tuɣa izeddeɣ di Sadum.   
\m
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ijjen zeg inni yarewřen, inna man aya i Abram, Aɛibrani, wenni tuɣa izeddɣen ɣar tcejjura n yigg n Mamri, aryaz d Amuriy, umas n Ackul d Ɛanir. Nitni d arfiqen di řɛahd n Abram. \f ◼ \fr 14:13 \ft \+fk Aɛibrani\ft  - tanita d twařa tamezwarut i nᵉttaf isem-a deg Wedlis Iqeddsen. Deg wedlis ‘Amezwaru’, udem 39, ayat 4 d 17 uřa deg wudem 41, ayet 21 nᵉttaf isem-a am uceyyar ɣar Yusuf u deg wedlis Amezwaru (Amz. 43:32) am ijj n uceyyar ɣar marra ihenjiren n Yaɛqub (xzar ɛawed Amz. 40:15).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 14:13 \xt Amz. 13:18. \x*  
\v 14 \add Řami\add* isřa Abram belli umas ṭṭfen t d ameḥbus, yiwi \add iryazen\add* inni idarrben i umenɣi, inni dd-ittwaxeřqen di taddart nnes, di teřt-mya u-tmenṭac, uca iḍfar i-ten ař Dan.  
\v 15 S ǧiret bḍan xasen nitni, \add ggin terfiqin\add*, netta d imsexxaren nnes, uca iɣřeb xasen uca iḍfar i-ten ɣar \add tendint n\add* Ḥuba, tenni \add iǧan\add* x uzeřmaḍ n Dimacq.  
\v 16 Yarra-dd marra agřa uřa d umas Luṭ d wagřa nnes uřa d timɣarin d řgens.   
\m
\v 17 Umi dd-iɛqeb, awarni řami iɣřeb netta x Kidurlaɛumir u x ijeǧiden nni tuɣa akides, iffeɣ ujeǧid n Sadum ḥima ad t iřqa di Řewḍa n Teɣzurt n Cawa, tenni iǧan d Taɣzurt n Ujeǧid.  
\v 18 U Malkiṣadiq, ajeǧid n Calim, yiwi-dd aɣrum d binu. Netta tuɣa d akehhan n Arebbi, Amɛuǧi x kuřci. \f ◼ \fr 14:18 \ft \+fk Malkiṣadiq\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘ajeǧid amsegged’ niɣ ‘ajeǧid d amtiqqi’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 14:18 \xt Ɛbr. 7:1, 2, 3. \x*  
\v 19 Ibark i-t, inna as: “Ad ittwabarek Abram zi Arebbi, Amɛuǧi x kuřci, wenni iggin ijenwan d temmurt.  
\v 20 Ad ittwabarek Arebbi, Amɛuǧi x kuřci, wenni isellmen iɣrimen nnec deg ifassen nnec!” Uca \add Abram\add* iwca as řeɛcur n marra.   
\m
\v 21 Uca inna ujeǧid n Sadum i Abram: “Ewc ayi marra min \add iddaren\add*, maca ksi agřa i yixef nnec.”  
\v 22 \add Maca\add* Abram yarra-dd x ujeǧid n Sadum: “Aqa ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu ɣar SIDI Arebbi, Amɛuǧi x kuřci, wenni iggin ajenna d temmurt, \add jjuǧeɣ\add*  
\v 23 maḥend war kessiɣ afiřu niɣ taḥezzemt n sandaliyat uřa \add ca n řḥajjet\add* zi marra min iǧan nnec, ḥima war teqqared: ‘Necc sstejjareɣ Abram!’  
\v 24 War ɣari dayes bu tasɣart! Mɣir min ccin imsexxaren d tesɣart n iryazen nni kidi iruḥen, Anir d Ickul d Mamri, ejj i-ten ad ksin tasɣart nsen!”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Řɛahd n Arebbi ak-d Abram  
\m
\v 1 Awarni man aya yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Abram deg ijj n řewḥiy. Inna as “War tteggʷed ca, Abram, Necc d aseřqi i cek, řmunet nnec temɣar aṭṭas \add d Necc\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt Izhd. 16:6; 18:3; 19:12. \x*  
\v 2 Uca inna Abram: “Sidi inu, SIDI, min d ayi ɣa tewced, maɣar necc ad raḥeɣ ammu břa mmi u Aliɛazir zi Dimacq ad yiři \add amecnaw\add* mmi x wagřa n taddart inu?” \f ◼ \fr 15:2 \ft \+fk Aliɛazir\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni ɣar iǧa Arebbi d amɛawen nnes’ niɣ ‘wenni umi iwca Arebbi afus’.\f*  
\v 3 Inna Abram ɛawed: “Xzar, war d ayi tewcid zzariɛet, s uyenni, \add wenni iǧan am\add* mmi n taddart inu, ad yiři d awrit inu!” \f ◼ \fr 15:3 \ft \+fk zzariɛet\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘tarrawt’.\f*  
\v 4 Uca xzar, awař n SIDI yusa-dd ɣares, inna: “War cek iwarret ca wa, maca wenni i ɣa iffɣen zzayek ad yiři d awrit nnec.”  
\v 5 Issuffeɣ i-t ɣar barra, inna: “Xzar ɣar ujenna, tḥesbed itran, mařa tzemmared ad ten tḥesbed!” Uca inna as: “Ammu i ɣa tiři zzariɛet nnec!” \x ◘ \xo 15:5 \xt Uf. 32:13; Aɛwd. 10:22; Rum. 4:18; Ɛbr. 11:12. \x*  
\v 6 Uca netta yumen di SIDI uca iḥseb as t-i-dd d tasegda. \f ◼ \fr 15:6 \ft \+fk iḥesb as t-i-dd d tasegda\ft  - niɣ ‘igga as t i netta d tasegda’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 15:6 \xt Rum. 4:3, 9, 18, 22; Gal. 3:6; Yaɛ. 2:23. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Inna as ɛawed: “Necc d SIDI, wenni cek dd-yiwyen zi Ur n Ikaldaniyyen, ḥima ad ac wceɣ tammurt-a d řwart.” \x ◘ \xo 15:7 \xt Izhd. 105:11. \x*  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* netta inna: “\add A\add* Sidi inu, SIDI, s minzi i ɣa ssneɣ, belli ad tt warteɣ?”  
\v 9 Inna as Netta: “Awi ayi-dd ict n tɛejmit n třata n iseggʷusa d ijj n iɣayḍ n třata iseggʷusa d ijj n icarri n třata iseggʷusa d ict n tejlilleḥt d ijj n wedbir d ameẓyan.”  
\v 10 Netta yiwi-dd ɣares marra man aya, ibḍa ten x wezyen u igga kuř azyen qibač i wenneɣni, \add maca\add* war ibḍi ca ijḍaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 15:10 \xt Irm. 34:18, 19\x*  
\v 11 Hwan-dd ijḍaḍ ittkeccaḍen x imurḍas, \add maca\add* Abram yuẓẓeř xasen.  
\v 12 Ɣar uɣeǧay n tfuct, imsar aqa yusa as-dd i Abram ijj n yiḍeṣ yuǧeɣ, uca xzar, tiggʷudi \add d\add* taǧest iḥedqen wḍan-dd xas.  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* inna i Abram: “Ssen s tidett aqa zzariɛet nnec ad tiři d tabarranect deg ict n temmurt i war iǧin nnes uca ad asen xedmen \add am isemɣan\add* u nitni ad xasen ggen aɣiř arebɛa-mya n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 15:13 \xt Uf. 12:40; Řex. 7:6; Gal. 3:17. \x*  
\v 14 \add Maca\add* řgens umi ɣa xedmen am isemɣan, ad xasen ḥekmeɣ ɛawed, uca awarni man aya ad ffɣen s wagřa imɣar. \x ◘ \xo 15:14 \xt Uf. 3:22; 11:2; 12:35,36. \x*  
\v 15 Ad tᵉttwassmuned ɣar řejdud nnec s řehna uca ad cek neḍřen am umeccaybu iweqqar. \x ◘ \xo 15:15 \xt Amz. 25:7, 8. \x*  
\v 16 Jjiř wiss arebɛa ad dd-iɛqeb danita, minzi \add řqedd n\add* řmuɛṣiyyet n Imuriyyen ɛad war ikemmeř.” \x ◘ \xo 15:16 \xt Uf. 12:40. \x*  
\v 17 Řami teɣři tfuct uca tedweř d taǧest, tuɣa din afarran iddexxnen u iɛdu ijj n weṣfeḍ n tmessi jar izeynan nni. \f ◼ \fr 15:17 \ft \+bd afessar\+bd* - řami ggin tnayen n ijeǧiden zic ijj n řɛahd di Ccarq-Ameřwasu ksin nitni ijj n umeddar i tɣarṣt, bḍan t d izeynan uca ssarsen azyen ɣar ijj n uɣezdis u azyen ɣar ijj n uɣezdis nneɣni. Xenni tuɣa x ujeǧid nni tuɣa d amuqřiř zzaysen ad yuyur di řwest n tnayen n iziynan am iqqar aqa ajeǧid wenni d ameqqran zzaysen ɣares řḥeqq ḥima ad kides igg amecnaw min igga ak-d umuddar i umi ɣarṣen, mařa netta war ikemmeř řɛahd i igga akides (xzar Irm. 34:18-20). Deg wawařen-a nettwařa aqa Arebbi wenni d ameqqran x Ibrahim, tuɣa iggur di řwest n izeynan n umeddar di ṣṣifet n wesfeḍ am tuɣa Ibrahim ittbedda ɣar uɣezdis. Man aya ixs ad yini aqa Arebbi s Yixef nnes d Netta i iqeḍɛen řɛahd ak-d Ibrahim minzi Arebbi ittḥinna x bnadem, issen bnadem war izemmar ad ikemmeř uřa d ijj n řɛahd akides. Bnadem izemmar mɣir ad ittwassenjem xmi i ɣa yamen di Řɛahd i igga Arebbi di Mmis, ixs ad yini di Lmasiḥ wenni iwcin Ixef nnes d tɣarṣt i ddnub n iwdan.\f*  
\v 18 Deg wass nni nnit igga SIDI ijj n Řɛahd ak-d Abram, inna: “I zzariɛet nnec umi wciɣ tammurt-a zeg iɣzar n Miṣra ař iɣzar ameqqran, iɣzar n Lfuraṭ: \x ◘ \xo 15:18 \xt Amz. 12:7; 13:15; 24:7; 26:4; Uf. 32:13; Aɛwd. 1:8; 34:4. \x*  
\v 19 \add tammurt n\add* Iqiniy\add yen\add*, Iqeniziy\add yen\add*, Iqadmiy\add yen\add*,  
\v 20 Iḥittiy\add yen\add*, Ifirziy\add yen\add*, Irafawiyyen,  
\v 21 Imuriy\add yen\add*, ayt n Kenɛan, Igirgaciy\add yen\add* d Iyibusiy\add yen\add*.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 Hajar d Ismaɛil  
\m
\v 1 Saray, tamɣart n Abram, war d as dd-tiruw ca. Tuɣa ɣares ict n tayya zi Miṣra qqarent as Hajar.  
\v 2 Tenna Saray i Abram: “Aqa teẓrid belli SIDI iṭṭef xafi tarwa. Adef x tayya inu, balak ad zzayes ksiɣ tarwa.” Abram tuɣa issḥessa ɣar Saray. \f ◼ \fr 16:2 \ft \+fk ɣar Saray\ft  - am ikmeř ‘ɣar tmijja n Saray’.\f*  
\v 3 Awarni řami izdeɣ Abram ɛecra n iseggʷusa di temmurt n Kenɛan, tiwi-dd Saray, tamɣart n Abram, tayya nnes Hajar, tenni zi Miṣra, uca tewca as-dd i Abram, aryaz nnes, d tamɣart nnes.  
\v 4 Yudef x Hajar uca nettat teksi ddeyset. Umi teẓra belli teksi ddeyset, xenni tedweř lallas tᵉttwasseḥqar di tiṭṭawin nnes.  
\v 5 Tenna Saray i Abram: “Zi ssibbet nnec ggin dayi řmunkar. Necc ggiɣ tayya inu deg weḥsin nnec. Umi teẓra belli teksi ddeyset, dewřeɣ d tameḥguret di tiṭṭawin nnes. Ejj ad iḥkem SIDI jar ayi d cek!”  
\v 6 Inna Abram i Saray: “Xzar, tayya nnem deg ifassen nnem. Egg zzayes min tᵉttwařid cem mliḥ di tiṭṭawin nnem.” Uca Saray tqemmeɛ i-tt u xenni nettat tarweř zzayes.   
\m
\v 7 Uca lmalak n SIDI iřqa i-tt ɣar tařa n waman di řexřa, ɣar tařa deg webrid ittawyen ɣar Cur. \f ◼ \fr 16:7 \ft \+fk Cur\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘řḥiḍ’. Tandint-a tuɣa ɣar weymir jar Kenɛan d Miṣra.\f*  
\v 8 Inna: “Hajar, tayya n Saray, manis dd-tusid u mani ɣa traḥed?” Nettat tenna: “Ttrakkwařeɣ zeg wudem n lalla Saray!”  
\v 9 Xenni inna as lmalak n SIDI: “Dweř ɣar lallam, uḍar sadu ifassen nnes.”  
\v 10 Inna as ɛawed lmalak n SIDI: “Ad kettareɣ aṭṭas zzariɛet nnem, ař war izemmar ad tᵉttwaḥseb řami i ɣa tiři deg waṭṭas.”  
\v 11 Inna as lmalak n SIDI ɛawed: “Aqa řexxu, teksid ddeyset uca ad tarwed aseymi. Ad as tegged Ismaɛil, minzi SIDI isřa am di řemḥayen nnem. \f ◼ \fr 16:11 \ft \+fk Ismaɛil\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘Arebbi ad iseř’ niɣ ‘wenni umi i ɣa iseř Arebbi’ niɣ ‘wenni i d as ittesřan Arebbi’.\f*  
\v 12 Uca netta ad yiři d ijj n bnadem amecnaw asnus n řexřa. Afus nnes ad yiři x marra, u afus n marra ad yiři xas. Ad izdeɣ arendad n marra aytmas.” \x ◘ \xo 16:12 \xt Amz. 25:18. \x*  
\v 13 U nettat třaɣa x Yisem n SIDI i ɣares-dd issiwřen, \add tenna:\add* “Cek d Arebbi i ittwařan!”, minzi tenna: “Ma war da ẓriɣ wenni d ayi ittwařan?”  
\v 14 X uya semman anu nni: anu ‘Laḥay-Ru’i’. Xzar, aqa-t jar Qadac d Barad. \f ◼ \fr 16:14 \ft \+fk anu Laḥay-Ru’i\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘anu n wenni iddaren u ixzar dayi’. \fk Barad\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘tebrurri’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 16:14 \xt Amz. 24:62; 25:11. \x*  
\v 15 Uca turuw-dd Hajar i Abram aseymi. Igga as Abram isem n mmis nni \add i d as\add* dd-turuw Hajar ‘Ismaɛil’. \x ◘ \xo 16:15 \xt Gal. 4:22. \x*  
\v 16 Abram tuɣa ɣares setta u-tmanyin n iseggʷusa, umi dd-turuw Hajar Ismaɛil i Abram.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 17
\s1 Řɛahd n Arebbi ak-d Ibrahim  
\m
\v 1 \add Řami\add* tuɣa ɣares ɣar Abram tesɛa u-tesɛin n iseggʷusa, iban as-dd SIDI i Abram, inna as: “Necc d Arebbi Amzemmar x kuřci! Uyur zzat i wudem inu uca iři \add d bnadem\add* ikemmřen! \f ◼ \fr 17:1 \ft \+fk Amzemmar x kuřci\ft  - wenni ɣares tizemmar x marra min iǧan.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 17:1 \xt Amz. 5:22. \x*  
\v 2 Necc ad ggeɣ Řɛahd inu jar ayi d cek uca ad cek sskettareɣ s yijj n cckel imɣar.” \x ◘ \xo 17:2 \xt Amz. 12:2; 13:16; 15:5, 18; Uf. 2:24; 6:4; Lawi 26:42. \x*  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* iwḍa Abram x uɣembub nnes uca issiweř AREBBI akides, inna as:  
\v 4 “Xzar, Necc \add ad ggeɣ\add* Řɛahd inu akidek uca cek ad tiřid d babatsen n waṭṭas n řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 17:4 \xt Rum. 4:17. \x*  
\v 5 War ittiři isem nnec ɛad ‘Abram’ maca \bd ‘Ibrahim’\bd*, minzi Necc ggiɣ cek d babatsen n waṭṭas n řegnus.  
\v 6 Uca Necc ad cek arreɣ ad tegged řɣiǧet aṭṭas s waṭṭas u ad cek arreɣ d řegnus, uca ijeǧiden ad zzayek dd-ffɣen. \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt Mt. 1:6. \x*  
\v 7 Ad ggeɣ Řɛahd inu jar ayi d cek d zzariɛet nnec awarni ac di \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen, am yijj n Řɛahd i řebda, ḥima ad iřiɣ d AREBBI i cek u i zzariɛet nnec awarni ac. \x ◘ \xo 17:7 \xt Amz. 13:15. \x*  
\v 8 Ad ac wceɣ, i cek u i zzariɛet nnec awarni ac, tammurt mani tzeddɣed am ubarrani, marra tammurt n Kenɛan d agřa i řebda. Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI i nitni.” \x ◘ \xo 17:8 \xt Amz. 15:18; Aɛwd. 1:8. \x*  
\v 9 Inna AREBBI ɛawed i Ibrahim: “Cek ad teḥḍid Řɛahd inu, cek d zzariɛet nnec awarni ac, di \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen.  
\v 10 D wa d Řɛahd inu wenni i ɣa teḥḍam jar ayi-dd d kenniw d zzariɛet nnec awarni ac: ittxeṣṣa ad ixten zzaywem marra min iǧan d awtem.  
\v 11 Kenniw ad txetnem aysum n řeɛdařyet nwem uca man aya ad tiři d řeɛřamet n Řɛahd jar ayi-dd d kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 17:11 \xt Řex. 7:8; Rum. 4:11. \x*  
\v 12 Mmis n tmenya n wussan ad ixten jar awem, mkuř awtem di \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem, \add am\add* wenni dd-ixeřqen di taddart nnec \add am\add* wenni ittwasɣen s nnuqart zi kuř abarrani u war \add iǧin\add* zi zzariɛet nnec. \x ◘ \xo 17:12 \xt Lawi 12:3; Lk. 2:21. \x*  
\v 13 \add Am\add* wenni dd-ixeřqen di taddart nnec, \add am\add* wenni tesɣid s nnuqart, ittxeṣṣa as ad ixten. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa yiři Řɛahd inu deg weysum nwem d Řɛahd i řebda.  
\v 14 Aryaz war ixtinen, wenni řeɛdařyet nnes war tt xtin, aryaz nni ittxeṣṣa ad t qessen zi řgens nnes, aqa yarẓa Řɛahd inu.” \f ◼ \fr 17:14 \ft \+fk aryaz nni\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar nni’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 Inna AREBBI ɛawed i Ibrahim: “I Saray tamɣart nnec war d as třiɣid \add ɛad\add* ‘Saray’, maca ‘Sara’ d wa i ɣa yiřin isem nnes. \f ◼ \fr 17:15 \ft \+fk Saray\ft  - ad taɣ isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘yeǧis n ujeǧid’ (‹’amira’›), maca ɛlaḥsab inneɣni ‘tamɣart imeḥden’. \fk Sara\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘tajeǧidt’ niɣ ‘yemmatsen n řegnus’.\f*  
\v 16 \add Minzi\add* ad tt barkeɣ u zzayes ad ac wceɣ mmic. \add Wah\add*, ad tt barkeɣ uca nettat ad tedweř d řegnus u ijeǧiden n řegnus ad zzayes dd-ffɣen!”  
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* iwḍa Ibrahim x uɣembub nnes uca iḍḥec, inna deg wuř nnes: “Aryaz n mya n iseggʷusa ma ad as dd-ittwaxřeq mmis? U Sara, tenni ɣar iǧa tesɛin n iseggʷusa, \add ma ɛad\add* ad dd-taruw?”  
\v 18 Inna Ibrahim i AREBBI: “Mři Ismaɛil iddar qibač i wudem nnec!”  
\v 19 \add Maca\add* AREBBI inna: “Lla, ɛad \bd Sara, tamɣart nnec, d tenni d ac dd ɣa yarwen aseymi, uca cek ad as třaɣid Isḥaq. Necc ad ggeɣ Řɛahd inu akides d Řɛahd i řebda, i zzariɛet nnes awarni as.\bd*\f ◼ \fr 17:19 \ft \+fk Isḥaq\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘netta iḍeḥḥec’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 17:19 \xt Amz. 18:10; 21:2. \x*  
\v 20 Zi jjihet n Ismaɛil, aqa seǧeɣ ac. Xzar, Necc barkeɣ t uca ad t arreɣ ittaruw řɣiǧet u ad t arreɣ d aṭṭas. Tenɛac n řḥukkam i dd ɣa yejj, ad t ggeɣ d ijj n řgens imɣar. \x ◘ \xo 17:20 \xt Amz. 16:10; 25:12, 16. \x*  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* ad ggeɣ Řɛahd inu ak-d Isḥaq, wenni i d ac dd ɣa taruw Sara di řweqt-a, deg useggʷas i dd ɣa yasen.” \x ◘ \xo 17:21 \xt Amz. 21:2. \x*  
\v 22 \add Umi\add* ikemmeř awař nnes akides, igeɛɛed AREBBI, \add iggʷej\add* x Ibrahim.   
\m
\v 23 Iksi Ibrahim mmis Ismaɛil d marra isemɣan i dd-ittwaxeřqen di taddart nnes d marra inni immesɣen s nnuqart, marra \add min iǧan d\add* awtem jar aytbab n taddart n Ibrahim uca ixten řeɛdařyet nsen deg wass nni am mammec d as inna AREBBI.  
\v 24 Tuɣa ɣar Ibrahim tesɛa u-tesɛin n iseggʷusa umi ixten deg weysum n řeɛdařyet nnes. \f ◼ \fr 17:24 \ft \+fk tesɛa u-tesɛin n iseggʷusa\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini belli Isḥaq ittwaxeřqed-dd umi tuɣa Ibrahim ɛad ittwaxten (Amz. 18:10-14 d 21:5), aqa-t awarni řami igga Arebbi řɛahd nnes akides (xzar Amz. 17:21). Maca Ismaɛil ittwaxřeq-dd qbeř mma igga Arebbi řɛahd nnes ak-d Ibrahim.\f*  
\v 25 Igga mmis Ismaɛil třeṭṭac n iseggʷusa, umi t xetnen deg weysum n řeɛdařyet nnes.  
\v 26 Ixten Ibrahim d mmis Ismaɛil deg wass d ijjen.  
\v 27 Xetnen akides marra iryazen n taddart nnes, inni dd-ittwaxeřqen di taddart nnes uřa d inni immesɣen s nnuqart zeg ubarrani. \f ◼ \fr 17:27 \ft \+fk zeg ubarrani\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘zi mmis n ubarrani’.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 18
\s1 Awař n SIDI x třařit n Isḥaq  
\m
\v 1 Uca iḍhar SIDI i Ibrahim ɣar tcejjura n yigg n Mamri \add umi\add* tuɣa yareyyeḥ ɣar wadaf n uqiḍun nnes di ṭṭḥa n uziř.  
\v 2 Issgeɛɛed tamuɣři nnes, iẓra, aqa din třata n yeryazen qibač nnes. \add Umi\add* ten iẓra, ikkar ittazzeř ɣarsen zi wadaf n uqiḍun. Uca ibendeq \add s uɣembub nnes\add* ɣar temmurt, \f ◼ \fr 18:2 \ft \+fk ibendeq\ft  - niɣ ‘isjed’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 18:2 \xt Ɛbr. 13:2. \x*  
\v 3 inna: “\add A\add* Sidi inu, mařa \add řexxu\add* ufiɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, ttzawageɣ cek, war ɛeddu x umsexxar nnec.  
\v 4 Ejj \add imsexxaren inu\add* ad dd-awyen cwayt n waman uca sirdem iḍaren nwem uca zzřem cwayt sadu tcejjart-a. \f ◼ \fr 18:4 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  
\v 5 Ad dd-awyeɣ ařeqquz n weɣrum ḥima ad ttwaneɛcen wuřawen nwem, xenni ad teɛdum. Aqa x uya i dd-tekkim zzat i umsexxar nwem!” Nitni nnan: “Egg am mammec tennid.”   
\m
\v 6 Iruḥ Ibrahim deɣya ɣar uqiḍun ɣar Sara, inna: “Deɣyat, \add ksi\add* třata n řeqyas n waren azdad, eggw \add i-ten\add* uca egg \add zzayes\add* tifḍirin.” \f ◼ \fr 18:6 \ft \+fk ijj n řeqyas\ft  - ɛřayen 7-8 litru.\f*  
\v 7 \add Xas uca\add* yuzzeř Ibrahim ɣar ifunasen uca iṭṭef-dd ijj n umeẓyan n ufunas igma d lemliḥ, iwca i-t i ubřiɣ, uca wa iqeǧeq, ḥima ad t issewjed.  
\v 8 Netta iksi ɛawed ddhen d uɣi d umeẓyan n ufunas nni issewjed, uca issars \add i-t\add* zzatsen, u netta tuɣa ibedd qibač nsen sadu tcejjart, uca ccin.  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* nnan as: “Mani teǧa Sara tamɣart nnec?” Yarra-dd xasen: “\add Aqa-tt din\add* deg uqiḍun.”  
\v 10 Uca Netta inna: “D tidett ad ɣarek dd-dewřeɣ ɣar řweqt n tudart u xzar, ad ɣares yiři uḥenjir ɣar Sara, tamɣart nnec.” U Sara tesřa ɣar wadaf n uqiḍun nni \add iǧan\add* awarni as. \x ◘ \xo 18:10 \xt Amz. 17:19, 21; 21:2. \x*  
\v 11 Ibrahim d Sara tuɣa wsaren, uyuren deg wussan, uca Sara tuɣa tbedd as tubbart n temɣarin. \x ◘ \xo 18:11 \xt Amz. 17:17; Rum. 4:19; Ɛbr. 11:11. \x*  
\v 12 Uca teḍḥec Sara deg wuř nnes, tenna: “Awarni tewsar inu, ma ad ɣari yiři řxir\add -a\add* d lemliḥ qaɛ, \add am\add* iǧa sidi inu uřa d netta iwsar?” \x ◘ \xo 18:12 \xt Řqḍ. 19:26; 1 Bṭ. 3:6. \x*  
\v 13 Inna SIDI i Ibrahim: “Maɣar teḍḥec Sara, tenna: ‘Ma zemmareɣ ad arweɣ am wsareɣ řexxu?’  
\v 14 Ma aqa din ca n řḥajjet x SIDI tewɛar? Ad ɣarek dd-ɛeqbeɣ di řweqt i negga, ɣar řweqt n tudart uca \add ad yiři\add* ɣar Sara mmis!” \x ◘ \xo 18:14 \xt Mt. 19:26; Lk. 1:37. \x*  
\v 15 Sara tenkar, tenna: “War ḍeḥceɣ ca!”, minzi tuɣa teggʷed. Netta inna as: “Lla, aqa cem tḍeḥced!”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Taẓaǧit n Ibrahim x Sudum  
\m
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* kkaren iryazen nni ssenni, sewḍen ɣar Sadum, uca iruḥ Ibrahim akidsen, issqebbeḍ i-ten.  
\v 17 Uca inna SIDI: “Ma ad ffareɣ Necc x Ibrahim min i ɣa ggeɣ? \x ◘ \xo 18:17 \xt Ɛam. 3:7. \x*  
\v 18 Ad yiři Ibrahim zeɛma d ijj n řgens imɣar ijhed, aqa ad dayes ttwabarken marra řegnus n ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 18:18 \xt Amz. 12:3; 22:18; 26:4; Řex. 3:25; Gal. 3:8. \x*  
\v 19 Minzi Necc qqneɣ ixef inu akides, ḥima ad isseřmed iḥenjiren nnes uřa d taddart nnes awarni as, maḥend ad ḥḍan abrid n SIDI, ad ggen tasegda d řḥeqq, ḥima SIDI ad dd-yawi i Ibrahim min tuɣa xas inna.”  
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI: “Tɣuyyit n Sadum d Ɛamurra temɣar aṭṭas u ddnub nsen deqřen.  
\v 21 Ad dd-hwiɣ, ad ẓareɣ ma ggin nican am tɣuyyit nsen i ɣari dd-yusin niɣ lla, ad ssneɣ.”  
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* dewřen iryazen ssenni uca ṭṭfen \add abrid\add* ɣar Sadum. \add Maca\add* Ibrahim tuɣa iqqim ɛad ibedd zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 23 Uca iqarreb-dd Ibrahim, inna: “Ma s tidett ad taredǧed ɛawed amsegged ak-d uɛeffan?  
\v 24 Aqa dinni balak xemsin n imseggaden daxeř i tendint. Ma s tidett ad ten taredǧed, u war tsemmḥed deg wemcan nni di ṭṭweɛ n xemsin n imseggaden i dayes iǧan?  
\v 25 Iggʷej xak ad tegged aya, ad tenɣed amsegged ak-d uɛeffan, \add wah,\add* iggʷej xak ad yiři umsegged meḥsub am uɛeffan. Aqa řqaḍi n ddunect ma war ittegg s řḥeqq?” \x ◘ \xo 18:25 \xt Rum. 3:6. \x*  
\v 26 \add Řexdenni\add* inna as SIDI: “Mařa ufiɣ di Sadum xemsin n imseggaden daxeř i tendint, ad semḥeɣ i wemcan di ṭṭweɛ nsen.”  
\v 27 Ibrahim yarra-dd, inna: “Xzar řexxu, bdiɣ zeɛɛmeɣ ad ssiwřeɣ ak-d Sidi inu, \add waxxa\add* necc d cař d yiɣɣeḍ.  
\v 28 Ad taɣ neqṣen zi xemsin n imseggaden xemsa, ma ad taredǧed x xemsa nni marra tandint?” Inna: “War \add tt\add* ttaredǧeɣ mařa ufiɣ din xemsa u-rebɛin.”  
\v 29 Yarni deg wawař akides, inna as: “Ad taɣ ad yiři ad ittwaf din arebɛin!” Yarra-dd Netta: “War \add tt\add* tteggeɣ ca di ṭṭweɛ n arebɛin \add nni\add*.”  
\v 30 \add Xas uca\add* inna: “War ttxeyyiq řexxu Sidi inu, xmi ɣa ssiwřeɣ \add ɛawed\add*. Ad taɣ ad yiři din třatin!” Yarra-dd: “War \add tt\add* ttaredǧeɣ mařa ufiɣ din třatin.”  
\v 31 Inna \add ɛawed\add*: “Xzar řexxu, bdiɣ zeɛmeɣ ad ssiwřeɣ ak-d Sidi inu. Ad taɣ ad yiři din \add mɣir\add* ɛicrin!” Yarra-dd: “War \add tt\add* ttaredǧeɣ ca di ṭṭweɛ n ɛicrin \add nni\add*.”  
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* inna: “War ttxeyyiq řexxu Sidi inu, xmi ɣa ssiwřeɣ \add ɛawed\add*. Ad taɣ ad yiři din \add mɣir\add* ɛecra!” Yarra-dd: “War \add tt\add* ttaredǧeɣ di ṭṭweɛ n ɛecra \add nni\add*.”  
\v 33 \add Xenni\add* iruḥ SIDI awarni řami ikemmeř awař \add nnes\add* ak-d Ibrahim uca Ibrahim idweř-dd ɣar wemcan n tzeddiɣt nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 19
\s1 Tarewřa n Luṭ zi Sudum  
\m
\v 1 Uca iwḍent xenni tnayen n lmalakat \add nni\add* ɣar Sadum s ǧiřet. Tuɣa Luṭ iqqim ɣar tewwart n Sadum. Umi \add ten\add* iẓra Luṭ, ikkar maḥend ad ten iřqa uca ibendeq \add s uɣembub nnes\add* ɣar temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 19:1 \ft \+fk ibendeq\ft  - niɣ ‘isjed’.\f*  
\v 2 Inna: “Xzar, \add a\add* isiditen inu, ttzawageɣ kenniw ad dd-tasem ɣar taddart n umsexxar nwem uca ad \add dayes\add* tessensem, ad tessirdem iḍaren nwem. Xenni ad tfaqem zic, ad tkemmřem x webrid nwem.” \add Maca\add* nitni nnan: “Lla, aqa deg wazzay ad neqqim ad nessens.” \x ◘ \xo 19:2 \xt Amz. 18:4. \x*  
\v 3 \add Maca\add* netta ikellef xasen aṭṭas ařami akides ruḥen, udfen ɣar taddart nnes uca igga asen amensi, iggʷa aɣrum břa antun uca ccin. \x ◘ \xo 19:3 \xt Ɛbr. 13:2. \x*   
\m
\v 4 Aqa qbeř i ɣa ṭṭṣen, qewwaren i taddart iryazen n tendint, iryazen n Sadum, zeg umeẓyan ař awessar, marra iwdan zi marra imucan iṭṭurfen \add n tendint\add*.  
\v 5 Nitni řaɣan i Luṭ, nnan as: “Mani ǧan iryazen inni ɣarek dd-yusin ǧiret-a? Suffeɣ i-ten-dd, ḥima ad ten nessen.” \f ◼ \fr 19:5 \ft \+fk ḥima ad ten nessen\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini aqa iryazen n Sadum tuɣa xsen ad ten ɣeṣben.\f*  
\v 6 Iffeɣ-dd ɣarsen Luṭ, ɣar tewwart, uca iqqen tawwart awarni as.  
\v 7 Inna: “Ttzawgeɣ, \add a\add* aytma inu, war tteggem \add qaɛ\add* řɣar!  
\v 8 Xzar, ɣari tnayen n yessi, tinni \add ɛad\add* war issinen aryaz. Ejj ayi ad awem tent i-dd-ssuffɣeɣ barra uca ggem daysent min tᵉttwařam mliḥ di tiṭṭawin nwem. Mɣir i iryazen-a war daysen tteggem walu, aqa x uya dd-usin nitni swadday n tiři n tzeqqa inu ɣar tmensiwt.” \f ◼ \fr 19:8 \ft \+bd afessar\+bd* - ad taɣ igga Luṭ ammu maḥend ad yejj yessis ad tᵉttwaɣeṣbent zeg iryazen n Sadum, minzi tuɣa itteggʷed řḥukm n Arebbi x tmegga n iryazen nni ixsen ad ggen min war iḥeǧřen, min iǧan ḍidd i ṭṭbiɛet n bnadem maḥend ad ittwagg. Issen Luṭ aqa Arebbi tuɣa iḥekkem x ddunect s sseḥřet deg wussan n Nuḥ maɣar ‘tarwa n Arebbi’ (aqa-ten d lmalakat n Arebbi) usin-dd ɣar yessis n bnadem u man aya d nnɛi di tiṭṭawin n Arebbi (xzar Amz. 6:1-4, Yahuda 6,7). Ammu ixḍar Luṭ ḥima ad iwc tiḥenjirin nnes maḥend ad issenjem tandint n Sadum zi řḥukm ameqqran n Arebbi.\f*  
\v 9 Nitni nnan: “Aggʷej diha!” Uca nnan \add ɛawed\add*: “Aqa wanita yusa-dd \add da\add* d abarrani uca ixs ad \add xaneɣ\add* iḥkem am řqaḍi! Řexxu ad cek nḍarr ktar zzaysen.” Uca ggin aṭṭas n uɣiř x weryaz nni, x Luṭ, uca qarrben-dd ḥima ad arẓen tawwart. \x ◘ \xo 19:9 \xt Uf. 2:14; Řex. 7:27; 2 Bṭ. 2:7, 8. \x*  
\v 10 \add Maca\add* iryazen nni sswiẓẓḍen afus nsen, ssidfen Luṭ ɣar taddart akidsen uca bellɛen tawwart.  
\v 11 Nitni wtin iryazen \add nni tuɣa ibedden\add* ɣar tewwart n taddart s tuddarɣeč, am umeẓyan am umeqqran, \add ařami\add* ssihřen nitni ixef nsen di tarezzut x tewwart.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* nnan iryazen nni i Luṭ: “Wi ɣarek da ɛad? Ma aḍeggʷař niɣ iḥenjiren niɣ tḥenjirin, marra inni ɣarek di tendint, ejj i-ten ad ffɣen zeg wemcan-a.  
\v 13 Aqa ad nareddeǧ amcan-a, minzi tɣuyyit nnes temɣar zzat i wudem n SIDI, u SIDI issekk aneɣ-dd, ḥima ad tt nareddeǧ.”   
\m
\v 14 Iffeɣ Luṭ uca issiweř ak-d iḍeggʷařen nnes, inni iggin ad meřcen yessis, inna: “Kkarem, ffɣem zeg wemcan-a, minzi SIDI ad yareddeǧ tandint-a.” \add Maca\add* iban-dd ittqeṣṣar di tiṭṭawin n iḍeggʷařen nnes.  
\v 15 Umi iṣbeḥ řhař, ssqeǧqent lmalakat Luṭ, nnant: “Kkar, teksid tamɣart nnec d tnayen n yessic, \add tinni akidek\add*, ḥima war thelliked ca di řmuɛṣiyyet n tendint-a.”  
\v 16 \add Maca\add* netta war izɛim. Xenni ṭṭfen iryazen nni afus nnes d ufus n temɣart nnes d ifassen n tnayen n yessis, minzi SIDI tuɣa ixs ad xas iḥinn. Nitni ssuffɣen t ɣar barra, nedhen t barra i tendint.  
\v 17 Ařami ten ssuffɣen barra, inna Netta: “Senjem ixef nnec! War xezzar awarni ac, war ttbeddi di jjihet-a am tekmeř. Arweř ɣar idurar, ḥima war tᵉttwateḥḥid ca.” \f ◼ \fr 19:17 \ft \+fk ixef nnec\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar nnec’.\f*  
\v 18 Inna asen Luṭ: “Lla, ttzawageɣ, \add a\add* Sidi inu!  
\v 19 Xzar, amsexxar nnec yufa arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, \add wah\add* tessemɣared tamexsiwt nnec icewwaren, tenni kidi teggid umi d ayi tejjid ddareɣ. \add Maca\add* war zemmareɣ ad arewřeɣ ɣar idurar qbeř d ayi ɣa iṭṭef řɣar uca ad mmteɣ!  
\v 20 Xzar řexxu, tandint-a aqa tudes-dd aṭṭas, \add aqa\add* zemmareɣ ad dinni arewřeɣ. Nettat d tameɛnanuct. Ejj ayi ad arewřeɣ řexxu dinni. Ma war teǧi d \add ict n tendint\add* d tameɛnanuct? \add Xenni\add* zemmareɣ ad qqimeɣ ddareɣ.”  
\v 21 Yarra-dd xas: “Xzar, tiweḍ ayi-dd ɛawed tzawegt nnec x uya, war ttareddǧeɣ ca tandint min xef tessiwřed.  
\v 22 Qeǧeq, arweř din, minzi war zemmareɣ ad ggeɣ walu ař dd ɣa tawḍed ɣar dinni.” X uya semman isem n tendint \add nni\add* Ṣuɣar. \f ◼ \fr 19:22 \ft \+fk Ṣuɣar\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘ameẓyan’ niɣ ‘amuqřiř’.\f*  
\v 23 \add Ařami\add* yiweḍ Luṭ ɣar Ṣuɣar, tenqar-dd tfuct x temmurt.   
\m
\v 24 Ijja SIDI ad iwwet wenẓar x Sadum u x Ɛamurra, d řecbareyyet d tmessi zeg ujenna zi ɣar SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 19:24 \ft \+bd afessar\+bd* - deg wussan-a ufin imusnawen n umezruy marra min iqqimen n tneddam nni d iɣɣeḍ. Ittɣiř asen aqa řqedd n řeḥmu di Ɣammura yiweḍ ɣar 3000 Salsiyus. Řeḥyuḍ d txudam n wureɣ dewřen d iɣɣeḍ. Řecbareyyet ad tafed ɛad řexxu di jjwayeh n Řebḥar Immuten.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 19:24 \xt Aɛwd. 29:22; Ica. 13:19; Irm. 20:16; 50:40; Igjd. 4:6; Ḥiz. 16:50; Ḥuc. 11:8; Ɛam. 4:11; Ṣaf. 2:9; Lk. 17:29; 2 Bṭ. 2:6; Yah. 7. \x*  
\v 25 Yareddeǧ Netta tineddam nni d marra adewwar nni, ak-d marra imezdaɣ n tneddam nni uřa d aɣemmuy n temmurt.  
\v 26 Tamɣart nnes, \add tenni tuyur\add* ɣar ḍeffar nnes, texzar awarni as uca tedweř d ijj n uqellij n tmeǧaḥt. \x ◘ \xo 19:26 \xt Lk. 17:32. \x*   
\m
\v 27 Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ zic ikkar Ibrahim, \add yuyur\add* ɣar wemcan mani tuɣa ibedd zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 28 Isweḍ ɣar Sadum d Ɛamurra u ɣar marra tammurt n udewwar nni, uca iẓra belli ddexxan ittgeɛɛad zi temmurt am ddexxan n ict n tefqunt.  
\v 29 Ařami yareddeǧ AREBBI tineddam n udewwar \add nni\add*, ifekkar AREBBI di Ibrahim uca issekk Luṭ barra zi řwesṭ n uceřwaw, umi iqřeb tineddam i di izdeɣ Luṭ. \f ◼ \fr 19:29 \ft \+fk aceřwaw\ft  - s lḥarf ‘aneqřeb’\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Luṭ d yessis  
\m
\v 30 Igeɛɛed Luṭ zi Ṣuɣar uca iruḥ izdeɣ ak-d tnayen n yessis deg idurar, minzi iggʷed \add ad iqqim\add* izeddeɣ di Ṣuɣar. Uca izdeɣ deg ifri ak-d tnayen n yessis.  
\v 31 Tenna tmenzut i tmaẓuẓt: “Babatneɣ d awessar, war iqqim uɛezri di temmurt ad xaneɣ dd-yadef am mammec teggur di marra ddunect.  
\v 32 Zid, ejj aneɣ ad newc binu i babatneɣ ad issu uca ad kis nezzeř, \add maḥend\add* ad newc tudart i zzariɛet n babatneɣ.” \f ◼ \fr 19:32 \ft \+fk zzariɛet\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘tarwa’.\f*  
\v 33 Di ǧiřet nni wcint binu i babatsent, iswa. \add Xenni\add* tudef tmenzut, tᵉṭṭeṣ ak-d babas, \add maca\add* netta war yuci ca belli tezzeř akides niɣ tekkar \add ɛawed\add*.  
\v 34 Tiwecca nnes tenna tmenzut i tmaẓuẓt: “Aqa necc zzřeɣ ǧiret iɛdun ak-d baba, ad as newc ad issu binu ɛawed ǧiret-a. \add Xenni\add* ad tadfed cem ad kides tezzřed, maḥend ad dd-nejj jjiř ad iqqim iddar zi ẓẓariɛet n babatneɣ.”  
\v 35 Wcint binu i babatsent ɛawed di ǧiret nni, iswa. \add Xenni\add* tekkar tmaẓuẓt uca tᵉṭṭeṣ ak-d babas. \add Maca\add* netta war yuci ca belli tezzeř akides niɣ tekkar \add ɛawed\add*.  
\v 36 \add Ammu\add* ksint tnayen n yessis n Luṭ s ddeyset zi babatsent.  
\v 37 Uca turuw-dd tmenzut aseymi, třaɣa isem nnes Mu’ab. Wa d babatsent n ayt n Mu’ab ɣar ass\add -a\add*. \f ◼ \fr 19:37 \ft \+fk Mu’ab\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘zi baba’.\f*  
\v 38 Tamaẓuẓt ɛawed turuw-dd aseymi uca třaɣa isem nnes Ben-Ɛammi. Netta d babatsen n iḥenjiren n Ɛammun ɣar ass-a. \f ◼ \fr 19:38 \ft \+fk Ben-Ɛammi\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘mmis n řgens inu’.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 20
\s1 Ibrahim ak-d Abimalik, ajeǧid n Jirar  
\m
\v 1 Ssenni issmuṭṭiy Ibrahim iqiḍan nnes, \add yuyur\add* ɣar Temmurt n Ljanub. Izdeɣ netta jar Qadac d Cur uca iqqim am ubarrani di Jirar.  
\v 2 \add Umi\add* inna Ibrahim x Sara tamɣart nnes: “Nettat d učma i teǧa!”, issekk Abimalik, ajeǧid n Jirar, yiwi \add akis\add* Sara. \f ◼ \fr 20:2 \ft \+fk Abimalik\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘babas n ujeǧid’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:2 \xt Amz. 12:13; 26:7. \x*  
\v 3 \add Maca\add* iḍhar-dd AREBBI i Abimalik di tarjit n ǧiret, inna as: “Aqa řexxu ad temmted di ssibbet n temɣart, tenni dd-tiwyed akidek, \add minzi\add* nettat temřec ak-d weryaz.”  
\v 4 \add Maca\add* Abimalik tuɣa war ɣares dd-iqarreb, inna: “\add A\add* Sidi inu, ma \add xenni\add* ad tawḍed ad tenɣed ijj n řgens iseggden?  
\v 5 Ma war d ayi inni netta: ‘Nettat d učma \add i teǧa\add*!’, u nettat s yixef nnes tenna ɛawed: ‘Netta d uma \add i yeǧa\add*!’ S tidett n wuř u s ifassen izdigen i ggiɣ aya.”  
\v 6 Inna as AREBBI di tarjit: “Necc ssneɣ ɛad belli teggid man aya s tidett n wuř, x uya ḥḍiɣ cek ḥima war xafi txeṭṭiḍ u war cek jjiɣ ad tt tḥadid.  
\v 7 Řexxu, arr tamɣart ɣar weryaz nnes, minzi netta d anabi uca netta ad xak iẓẓaǧ, ḥima ad teddared. \add Maca\add* mařa war tt tarrid ca, ssen belli aqa ad temmted, cek d marra min iǧan nnec!”  
\v 8 Ikkar Abimalik zic ɣar ṣṣbeḥ. Iřaɣa i marra imsexxaren nnes, inna marra awařen-a deg imezzuɣen nsen uca iryazen nni dewřen ggʷeden aṭṭas.  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa Abimalik x Ibrahim uca inna as: “Min d aneɣ teggid d min di xḍiɣ akidek umi tɣeḍred xafi u x tgeldit inu ddenb ameqqran? Cek teggid akidi min war icuwwaren ad \add t\add* tegged.”  
\v 10 Uca \add yarni\add* inna Abimalik i Ibrahim: “Min cek yejjin řami teggid man aya?”  
\v 11 Inna Ibrahim: “Minzi nwiɣ: ‘Nican war dinni tiggʷudi zi AREBBI deg wemcan-a uca ad ayi nɣen di ssibbet n temɣart inu.’  
\v 12 Uca s tidett nettat ɛawed d učma. Nettat d yeǧis n baba, maca war teǧi d yeǧis n yemma uca tedweř d tamɣart inu.  
\v 13 Umi d ayi issetleɛ AREBBI zi taddart n baba, nniɣ as: ‘Ad yiři wa d \add řeɛřamet n\add* tmexsiwt nnec icewwaren i necc, aqa ad tinid di marra imucan mani ɣa naweḍ: Netta aqa d uma!’” \x ◘ \xo 20:13 \xt Amz. 12:13. \x*  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* iksi Abimaliki uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin d isemɣan d tiyya uca iwca i-ten i Ibrahim uca yarr as Sara, tamɣart nnes.  
\v 15 Inna Abimalik: “Xzar, tammurt inu aqa-tt qibač nnec. Zdeɣ mani i d ac dd-\add iḍhar\add* mliḥ di tiṭṭawin nnec.”  
\v 16 I Sara inna: “Xzar, wciɣ ařef n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart i umam. Aqa atent d ařeḥḥaf x tiṭṭawin i kuřci inni kidem iǧan, \add wah,\add* i kuřci idweř am-dd d ttiqart.”  
\v 17 Iẓẓuǧ Ibrahim i AREBBI uca AREBBI issgenfa Abimalik d temɣart nnes d temsexxarin nnes uca urwent.  
\v 18 Minzi tuɣa SIDI ibelleɛ qaɛ marra řemřawat n \add temɣarin di\add* taddart n Abimalik di ssibbet n Sara, tamɣart n Ibrahim.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 21
\s1 Axřaq n Isḥaq  
\m
\v 1 Uca yarzef SIDI ɣar Sara, am mammec t inna, uca ikemmeř SIDI \add awař\add* i inna i Sara. \x ◘ \xo 21:1 \xt Amz. 17:19; 18:10. \x*  
\v 2 Teksi Sara s ddeyset uca turuw-dd ijj n useymi i Ibrahim x tewsar nnes, di řmijar nni i d as inna AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 21:2 \xt Amz. 18:10, 14; Gal. 4:23; Ɛbr. 11:11. \x*  
\v 3 Uca iřaɣa Ibrahim i mmis aseymi, wenni d as dd-turuw Sara, Isḥaq.  
\v 4 Ibrahim ixten i mmis Isḥaq umi tuɣa ɣares tmenya n wussan, am mammec d as yumur AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 21:4 \xt Amz. 17:10. \x*  
\v 5 Tuɣa ɣar Ibrahim mya n iseggʷusa, ařami ɣares dd-ixřeq mmis Isḥaq.  
\v 6 Tenna Sara: “Isseḍḥec ayi AREBBI u kuř ijj wenni i ɣa isřan \add i man aya\add*, ad iḍḥec \add ɛawed\add* akidi.”  
\v 7 Tenna \add ɛawed\add*: “Man wen \add izeɛmen\add* ad yini i Ibrahim, aqa Sara ad tessuṭṭeḍ iseyman? Aqa urweɣ \add as-dd\add* aḥenjir x tewsar nnes!”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Sara d Hajar  
\m
\v 8 Igma useymi uca ittwakkes as uṭṭuḍ. Deg wass i d as kksen uṭṭuḍ i Isḥaq, issewjed Ibrahim ict n zzardet temɣar.  
\v 9 \add Umi\add* teẓra Sara mmis n Tmiṣrect Hajar, wenni dd-turuw \add Hajar\add* i Ibrahim, iqeṣṣar xas,  
\v 10 tenna i Ibrahim: “Aẓẓeř x tayya-ya d mmis, minzi mmis n tayya-ya war iwarret ca ak-d mmi, ak-d Isḥaq.” \x ◘ \xo 21:10 \xt Gal. 4:30. \x*  
\v 11 Awař-a iban-dd d aɛeffan aṭṭas di tiṭṭawin n Ibrahim di ssibbet n mmis.  
\v 12 \add Maca\add* inna AREBBI i Ibrahim: “War ttejji aḥenjir d tayya nnec ad iřin d tisineft di tiṭṭawin nnec. Seř ɣar marra min i d ac ɣa tini Sara, minzi di Isḥaq ad ac tiři zzariɛet. \f ◼ \fr 21:12 \ft \+fk zzariɛet\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘tarwa’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 21:12 \xt Rum. 9:7; Ɛbr. 11:18. \x*  
\v 13 Ad ggeɣ ɛawed ijj n řgens zi mmis n tayya-ya, minzi uřa d netta d zzariɛet nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 21:13 \xt Amz. 16:10; 17:20. \x*  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Ibrahim zic uca iksi aɣrum d ict n tecyart n waman, iwca \add i-ten\add* i Hajar, issars \add as ten\add* x teɣruḍt. \add Iwca as ɛawed\add* aḥenjir uca issqebbeḍ i-tt. Uca nettat truḥ, tennejru di řexřa n Bi’r-Sebɛa.  
\v 15 \add Řami\add* neqṣen waman zi tecyart, tenḍar aḥenjir sadu ijj n cbarq,  
\v 16 uca truḥ teqqim qibač nnes řaggʷaj n tecti n řqews, minzi tenna: “War zemmareɣ ad ẓareɣ meřmi i ɣa immet uḥenjir.” \add Ammu\add* i teqqim qibač nnes uca tessgeɛɛed tmijja nnes, tesɣuyyu.  
\v 17 Isřa AREBBI ɣar tmijja n uḥenjir uca lmalak n AREBBI iřaɣa i Hajar zeg ujenna, inna as: “Min cem yuɣin, Hajar? War tteggʷed ca, minzi AREBBI isřa řḥess n uḥenjir, din mani iǧa.  
\v 18 Kkar, sgeɛɛed aḥenjir uca ṭṭef as deg ufus nnem, minzi ad zzayes ggeɣ ijj n řgens imɣar.” \x ◘ \xo 21:18 \xt Amz. 16:10; 17:20. \x*  
\v 19 Uca yarzem AREBBI tiṭṭawin nnes, teẓra řɛunṣar n waman. Truḥ, tɛemmar tacyart s waman, tewca as i uḥenjir, ad isu.  
\v 20 Tuɣa AREBBI ak-d uḥenjir, iyma, izdeɣ di řexřa u tuɣa-t d amjebbad n řqews.  
\v 21 Tuɣa izeddeɣ di řexřa n Faran uca teksi as-dd yemmas tamɣart zi temmurt n Miṣra.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řɛahd jar Ibrahim d Abimalik  
\m
\v 22 Di řweqt nni d ict imsar, belli Abimalik ak-d Fikul, akumandar n řɛeskar nnes, issiweř ak-d Ibrahim, inna: “AREBBI aqa-t akidek di marra min tᵉttegged. \f ◼ \fr 21:22 \ft \+fk Fikul\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘aqemmun n marra’. Aqa netta x marra iɛeskariyyen u tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad as ṭṭaɛen di marra min yumur netta.\f*  
\v 23 Řexxu, jaǧ ayi ɣar AREBBI, aqa war tᵉttɣeccid iḥenjiren inu uřa d ayyawen inu! \add Maca\add* s muxas tamexsiwt icewwaren i kik ggiɣ qbeř, ad zzayes tegged cek akidi u ak-d temmurt mani teqqimed am ubarrani.” \x ◘ \xo 21:23 \xt Amz. 14:23. \x*  
\v 24 Inna Ibrahim: “Necc ad jjaǧeɣ!”  
\v 25 \add Xas uca\add* iɛeyyeb Ibrahim Abimalik x řɛunṣar n waman nni iṭṭfen \add zzayes\add* imsexxaren n Abimalik s uɣiř.  
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* inna Abimalik: “Necc war ssineɣ wi iggin man aya u cek war d ayi t tennid ca qbeř. Aqa ař řexxu i zzayek t sřiɣ.”  
\v 27 Iksi Ibrahim uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin uca iwca as ten i Abimalik uca nitni s tnayen idsen ggin ijj n řɛahd \add jar asen\add*.  
\v 28 \add Maca\add* issars Ibrahim sebɛa n txeswin zeg wuǧi ɣar uɣezdis.  
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* inna Abimalik i Ibrahim: “Min ɛnant sebɛa n txeswin nni teggid ɣar uɣezdis?”  
\v 30 Inna netta: “Ksi zeɛma sebɛa aya n txeswin zeg ifassen inu, ḥima ad iřint d cchadet di ṭṭweɛ inu belli necc i iɣzin anu-ya.”  
\v 31 X uya semman amcan nni Bi’r-Sebɛa, minzi nitni s tnayen idsen tuɣa jjuǧen din.  
\v 32 \add Ammu i\add* ggin řɛahd di Bi’r-Sebɛa. \add Awarni man aya\add* ikkar Abimalik ak-d Fikul, akumandar n řɛeskar nnes, iɛqeb ɣar temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen.  
\v 33 Iẓẓu Ibrahim ict n tcejjart n tmarist di Bi’r-Sebɛa uca iřaɣa din isem n SIDI, Arebbi n řebda. \f ◼ \fr 21:33 \ft \+fk tacejjart n tmarist\ft  - s tlatinit ‘Tamarix’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 21:33 \xt Amz. 4:26. \x*  
\v 34 Izdeɣ Ibrahim am ubarrani di temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen aṭṭas n wussan.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 22
\s1 Ibrahim iqeddem mmis Isḥaq d taɣarṣt i Arebbi  
\m
\v 1 Awarni man aya temsar, aqa ijarreb AREBBI Ibrahim, inna as: “Ibrahim!” Uca inna as: “Xzar, necc aqa ayi da!”  
\v 2 Inna as Netta: “Ksi ayenni n mmic, wenni texsed, Isḥaq, uca ruḥ ɣar temmurt n Muriya uca tqeddmed t din d taɣraṣt x yijj n wedrar jar idurar i d ac ɣa iniɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 22:2 \xt Ɛbr. 11:17. \x*  
\v 3 Ikkar Ibrahim zic, iḥezzem i weɣyuř nnes uca iksi akides tnayen n imsexxaren nnes d mmis Isḥaq. Iqess akeccuḍ i tewhibt n tɣarṣt, ikkar, iruḥ deg webrid ɣar wemcan i d as inna AREBBI.  
\v 4 Deg wass wiss třata issgeɛɛed Ibrahim tamuɣři nnes uca iẓra amcan zi řaggʷaj.  
\v 5 Inna Ibrahim i imsexxaren nnes: “Rajam da ak-d weɣyuř, necc d uḥenjir ad nraḥ diha, ad nesjed. \add Awarni as\add* ad ɣarwem dd-neɛqeb.”  
\v 6 Iksi Ibrahim akeccuḍ i wecmaḍ n tɣarṣt, issars i-t x mmis Isḥaq u netta \add s yixef nnes\add* iksi s ufus nnes timessi d txedmect, uca \add ammu i\add* ruḥen nitni s tnayen idsen.  
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* issiweř Isḥaq ak-d Ibrahim babas, inna: “Baba inu!” Inna netta: “Xzar, necc aqa ayi da, mmi!” Uca inna netta: “Xzar, \add aqa da\add* timessi d ukeccuḍ, maca mani iǧa izmar i tɣarṣt?” \x ◘ \xo 22:7 \xt Yḥ. 1:29, 36\x*  
\v 8 Inna Ibrahim: “AREBBI Simant nnes ad issarzeq s yezmar i tɣarṣt, \add a\add* mmi!” Uca \add ammu i\add* ruḥen s tnayen idsen  
\v 9 uca iwḍen ɣar wemcan nni i d as inna AREBBI. Din i ibna Ibrahim ijj n uɛalṭar uca iɛdeř akeccuḍ, icarf mmis Isḥaq uca issars i-t x uɛalṭar x ikecwaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 22:9 \xt Yaɛ. 2:21. \x*  
\v 10 \add Xas uca\add* isswiẓẓeḍ Ibrahim afus nnes uca iksi-dd taxedmect, ḥima ad iɣarṣ i mmis.  
\v 11 \add Maca\add* lmalak n SIDI iřaɣa as-dd zeg ujenna, inna as: “Ibrahim, Ibrahim!” Netta inna: “Necc aqa ayi da!”  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna as: “War swiẓẓiḍ afus nnec ɣar uḥenjir. war d ttegg ca, minzi řexxu aqa ssneɣ belli tᵉtteggʷeded AREBBI u war xafi tessɛizzed ayenni n mmic.”  
\v 13 Issgeɛɛed Ibrahim tiṭṭawin nnes, u xzar, aqa awarni as tuɣa ijj n icarri iqqen ɣar cbarq zeg waccawen nnes. Yuyur Ibrahim dinni, iṭṭef icarri uca igga-i-t d taɣarṣt deg wemcan n mmis. \f ◼ \fr 22:13 \ft \+fk accawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iqiccawen’.\f*  
\v 14 Iřaɣa Ibrahim isem n wemcan nni: “SIDI ad issarzeq!” S uyenni iqqar bnadem ař ass-a: “Deg wedrar n SIDI ad yiři yarzeq!” \f ◼ \fr 22:14 \ft \+fk ad issarzeq ... ad ittwassarzeq\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad iẓar ... ad ittwaẓar’. \+bd afessar\+bd* - wa d adrar ‘Muri-Yah’, amcan nni i ɣa isscen Arebbi (Aɛwd. 12:11) d amcan n Zzawect Iqeddsen nni tuɣa din deg wussan awarni man aya. Ad taɣ tuɣa amcan-a uřa d amcan mani tuɣa izeddeɣ Malkiṣadiq, ajeǧid n Salim, ixs ad yini tasɣart n wedrar nni iǧan ɣar ccamal, tenni idewřen d adrar n Zzawect Iqeddsen. Tasɣart n ljanub n wedrar tuɣa d tandint n Dawud. Dawud iṭṭef lburj n ayt n Yabus nni iǧan x wedrar-a (1 Ij. 8:1, 1 Im. 11:5, 2 Ṣm. 5:6, 7, 9). Awarni as isɣa Dawud tasɣart n ccamal n wedrar 'Muri-Yah' zi Arawna, wenni ɣar iǧa ijj n wendrar x wedrar-a mani tuɣa dd-issehwa Lmalak n SIDI afus nnes ařami tbedd jjriḥect nni issiweḍ Lmalak n SIDI x Israil nni dd yusin zi ssibbet n řeḥsab n řgens nni igga Dawud s yixef nnes, břa ma ittar SIDI (xzar 2 Ṣm. 24). Xmi i ɣa nɣar 2 Ṣm. 5:7, 1 Ij. 8:1 u Izhd. 2:6 nᵉttaf aqa nzemmar ad neḥseb adrar-a 'Muri-Yah' d adrar 'Siḥyun', adrar iqeddsen, mani ssarsen Ttabut deg wussan n Dawud (2 Ṣm. 6:17). Idweř Siḥyun d isem aneggar n marra adrar, uřa d isem i tendint n Urcalim marra. Xzar ɛawed afessar ɣar 2 Ij. 19:31.\f*  
\v 15 Iřaɣa-dd lmalak n SIDI wiss martayen zeg ujenna x Ibrahim,  
\v 16 inna: “Minzi teggid man aya uca war xafi tᵉṭṭifed ayenni n mmic, ad jjaǧeɣ x Simant inu, iqqar SIDI, \x ◘ \xo 22:16 \xt Lk. 1:73; Ɛbr. 6:13. \x*  
\v 17 aqa ad cek barkeɣ aṭṭas uca ad kettareɣ zzariɛet nnec aṭṭas am yitran n ujenna u am yijdi x tma n řebḥar. Zzariɛet nnec ad tᵉṭṭef tawwart n řɛedyan nnes d řwart \x ◘ \xo 22:17 \xt Amz. 24:60. \x*  
\v 18 u di zzariɛet nnec ad ttwabarken marra řegnus n temmurt, minzi tesřid i tmijja inu.” \x ◘ \xo 22:18 \xt Amz. 12:3; 18:18; 26:4; Řex. 3:25; Gal. 3:8. \x*  
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb-dd Ibrahim ɣar imsexxaren nnes. Nitni kkaren uca ruḥen jmiɛ \add deg webrid\add* ɣar Bi’r-Sebɛa, uca igga Ibrahim ad izdeɣ di Bi’r-Sebɛa.   
\m
\v 20 Awarni man aya imsar aqa xebbaren Ibrahim, nnan as: “Xzar, ɛawed Milka turuw-dd iḥenjiren i Naḥur umac:  
\v 21 Ɛuṣ, amenzu nnes, d Buz umas, d Qamuwil wenni d babas n Aram,  
\v 22 d Kasad d Ḥazu d Fildac d Yidlaf d Bituwil.”  
\v 23 Bituwil ijja-dd Rifqa. Tmenya aya i dd-turuw Milka i Naḥur, umas n Ibrahim.  
\v 24 U tayya nnes, tenni umi qqaren Riɛuma, turuw \add as\add*-dd ɛawed Ṭabaḥ d Jaḥam d Taḥac d Maɛka. \f ◼ \fr 22:24 \ft \+fk tayya nnes\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘tayya n Naḥur’.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 23
\s1 Řmewt d wenḍeř n Sara  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa ɣar Sara mya u-sebɛa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa. \add Man aya d řmijař n\add* iseggʷusa n tudart n Sara.  
\v 2 Uca temmut Sara di Qaryat-Arbaɛ, ixs ad yini Ḥabrun, di temmurt n Kenɛan. Uca yudef-dd Ibrahim \add ɣar uqiḍun\add*, icḍen x Sara, isɣuy xas.  
\v 3 \add Xas uca\add* ikkar Ibrahim ṭṭarf i umettin nnes, uca issiweř ak-d tarwa n Ḥit, inna:  
\v 4 “Necc d abarrani d amɛezzeb ɣar awem. Wcem ayi mɣir anḍeř d agřa jar awem, ḥima ad neḍřeɣ amettin inu zi zzat inu.” \x ◘ \xo 23:4 \xt Řex. 7:5. \x*  
\v 5 Arrin-dd tarwa n Ḥit x Ibrahim, nnan as:  
\v 6 “Seř ɣarneɣ, \add a\add* sidi inu! Cek d řḥakem n AREBBI jar aneɣ. Nḍeř amettin nnec deg wenḍeř nneɣ iṣebḥen. Uřa d ijj zzayneɣ ad cek iṭṭef x wenḍeř nnes, ḥima ad \add dayes\add* tneḍřed amettin nnec.”  
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Ibrahim, ibendeq zzat i řgens n temmurt, zzat i tarwa n Ḥit  
\v 8 uca issiweř akidsen, inna: “Mařa kenniw s array nwem ad neḍřeɣ amettin inu zi zzat inu, sřem ɣari uca zawgem di ṭṭweɛ inu ɣar Ɛifrun, mmis n Zuhar,  
\v 9 maḥend ad ayi iwc ifri n Makfila, d wenni nnes, ɣar ṭṭarf n yeyyar nnes. Ejj i-t ad ayi t iwc s ttaman nnes ikmeř. Ad yiři d anḍeř inu i ɣa mellkeɣ jar awem.”  
\v 10 Ɛifrun tuɣa iqqim jar tarwa n Ḥit uca Ɛifrun, Aḥitti, yarra-dd x Ibrahim deg imejjan n tarwa n Ḥit d marra inni yudfen ɣar tewwart n tendint nnes, inna:  
\v 11 “Lla, a sidi inu, seř-dd ɣari! Necc ad ac wceɣ iyyar uřa d ifri nni dayes iǧan. Zzat i tiṭṭawin n tarwa n řgens inu ad ac t wceɣ, nḍeř amettin nnec!”  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* ibendeq Ibrahim s uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt zzat i řgens n temmurt  
\v 13 uca issiweř ak-d Ɛifrun deg imezzuɣen n řgens n temmurt, inna: “Ttzawgeɣ, mařa texsed, seř-dd ɣari. Ad ac wceɣ nnuqart n yeyyar, qbeř i-tt zzayi, \add xenni\add* ad dayes neḍřeɣ amettin inu.”  
\v 14 Yarra-dd Ɛifrun x Ibrahim, inna as:  
\v 15 “Sidi inu, seř-dd ɣari! Min ixs ad yini iyyar isekkwan arebɛa-mya ciqlu n nnuqart jar ayi d cek? Nḍeř amettin nnec!” \f ◼ \fr 23:15 \ft \+fk aciql ... iciqlen\ft  - ijj n řeqyas n wureɣ d nnuqart u n řḥajat nneɣni. Aqa din uřa d aciql n Zzawect Iqeddsen (xzar Uf. 38:26).\f*  
\v 16 Isřa Ibrahim i Ɛifrun uca iwzen Ibrahim i Ɛifrun tmenyat n nnuqart i xef issiweř deg imezzuɣen n tarwa n Ḥit: arebɛa-mya ciqlu n nnuqart, am tt nnumen isebbaben. \x ◘ \xo 23:16 \xt Amz. 50:13. \x*  
\v 17 \add Ammu i\add* idweř yeyyar n Ɛifrun, wenni iǧan di Makfila arendad n Mamri, iyyar d ifri wenni dayes iǧan d marra ticejjura inni deg iyyar ɣar iymiren nnes i d as dd-innḍen, \f ◼ \fr 23:17 \ft \+fk Makfila\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘tnayen n tseqqar’ niɣ ‘tasɣart’ (x webrid n umedya: ‘tasɣart n temmurt’).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 23:17 \xt Řex. 7:16. \x*  
\v 18 d agřa n Ibrahim zzat i tarwa n Ḥit d marra inni yudfen ɣar tewwart n tendint.  
\v 19 Awarni aya inḍeř Ibrahim Sara, tamɣart nnes, deg ifri n yeyyar n Makfila qibač i Mamri, wenni iǧan d Ḥabrun di temmurt n Kenɛan.  
\v 20 \add Ammu i\add* idweř iyyar ak-d yefri i dayes iǧan zi tarwa n Ḥit ɣar Ibrahim am wenḍeř nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 24
\s1 Isḥaq d Rifka  
\m
\v 1 Ibrahim tuɣa iwsar u imɣar deg wussan uca SIDI ibarek Ibrahim di kuřci.  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna Ibrahim i umsexxar nnes awessar nni iǧan x taddart nnes, awkiř n marra min ɣares: “Egg řexxu afus nnec sadu tmeṣṣaḍt inu, \x ◘ \xo 24:2 \xt Amz. 47:29. \x*  
\v 3 ad ac ssjjaǧeɣ s SIDI, AREBBI n ijenwan d AREBBI n temmurt, belli war dd-tᵉttiwyed tamɣart i mmi zi tḥenjirin n ayt n Kenɛan mani zeddɣeɣ necc jar asen, \x ◘ \xo 24:3 \xt Amz. 28:1. \x*  
\v 4 \add maca\add* ad traḥed ɣar temmurt \add i zi dd-usiɣ\add*, ɣar raǧ inu, \add maḥend\add* ad dd-tawyed tamɣart i mmi Isḥaq.”  
\v 5 Inna as umsexxar: “Balak war tᵉttexs temɣart ad ayi dd-teḍfar ɣar temmurt-a. Ma ittxeṣṣa ad arreɣ mmic ɣar temmurt nni manis dd-tusid?”  
\v 6 Inna as Ibrahim: “Ḥḍat, war dd-ttarri ca mmi dinni!  
\v 7 SIDI, AREBBI n ijenwan wenni d ayi iṭṭfen zi taddart n baba u zi temmurt n raǧ inu, wenni ɣari issiwřen, ijjuǧ ayi umi d ayi inna: ‘I zzariɛet nnec ad wceɣ tammurt-a!’, d Netta i ɣa issekken lmalak nnes zzat i wudem nnec, maḥend ad tawyed ssenni tamɣart i mmi. \x ◘ \xo 24:7 \xt Amz. 12:1, 7; 13:15; 15:18; 26:4; Uf. 32:13; Aɛwd. 34:4; Řex. 7:5. \x*  
\v 8 Mařa tamɣart war tᵉttexs ad cek dd-teḍfar, ad tiřid třellid zi tjaǧit-a, mɣir war dd-ttarri din mmi.”  
\v 9 Issars umsexxar afus nnes sadu tmeṣṣaḍt n sidis Ibrahim ijjuǧ as x man aya.   
\m
\v 10 Iksi umsexxar ɛecra n iřeɣman zeg iřeɣman n sidis, iruḥ. Tuɣa ɣares ɛřam kuř agřa iɣřan n sidis. Ikkar uca iṭṭef abrid ɣar \add temmurt n\add* Aram-Nahrayn, \add aqa-tt d Misuputamya\add*, ɣar tendint n Naḥur. \f ◼ \fr 24:10 \ft \+fk Aram-Nahrayn\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Aram-Nahrayim’, awař-a wanita ixs ad yini: Aram jar tnayen n iɣezran.\f*  
\v 11 Ɣar uxecci n tmeddit ijja iřeɣman ad jjnen barra i tendint zzat i řɛunṣar n waman, ɣar tsaɛɛet i di dd-ffɣent temɣarin, maḥend ad ayment aman.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna: “SIDI, AREBBI n sidi inu Ibrahim, ttzawageɣ Cek ad ayi tɛawned ass-a uca scen tamexsiwt \add nnec\add* icewwaren i sidi inu Ibrahim.  
\v 13 Aqa ayi ɣar řɛunṣar n waman d tḥenjirin n yeryazen n tendint ad dd-ffɣent maḥend ad ayment aman.  
\v 14 Ejj tabřiɣt nni umi ɣa iniɣ: ‘Sehwa-dd aqbuc nnem, mařa texsed, ad sweɣ!’, \add uca xenni\add* ad tini: ‘Su, ad wardeɣ uřa d iřeɣman nnec!’, aqa d nettat i teggid i umsexxar nnec Isḥaq, u s uya ad ssneɣ aqa tessecned tamexsiwt \add nnec\add* icewwaren i sidi inu.”   
\m
\v 15 Uca ɛad qbeř i ɣa ikemmer awař, iẓra Rifqa, tenni i dd-yurwen i Bituwil, mmis n Milka, tamɣart n Naḥur umas n Ibrahim, teffeɣ-dd \add zi tendint\add* s weqbuc nnes x teɣruḍt. \x ◘ \xo 24:15 \xt Amz. 22:23\x*  
\v 16 Tabřiɣt tuɣa dayes aẓri imɣar, d taɛzarect, war tt issin weryaz. Nettat tehwa-dd ɣar řɛunṣar, teccur aqbuc nnes uca tgeɛɛed ɛawed.  
\v 17 Yuzzeř ɣares umsexxar \add nni\add*, inna: “Ttzawgeɣ cem ad ayi tewced ad sweɣ cwayt n waman zeg weqbuc nnem!”  
\v 18 Nettat tenna: “Su, a sidi inu!” Tqeǧeq tessehwa aqbuc nnes x ufus nnes, tewca as ad isu.  
\v 19 \add Řami\add* d as tewca iswa mliḥ, tenna: “Ad aymeɣ aman ɛawed i iřeɣman nnec, ař ɣarsen i ɣa yiři s zzyada.”  
\v 20 Tqeǧeq tᵉssexwa aqbuc di tarya, tuzzeř ɛawed ɣar řɛunṣar, ḥima ad tayem aman, uca tuyem asen-dd aman i iřeɣman nnes marra.  
\v 21 \add Waxxa\add* itebhet dayes weryaz, isqar, ḥima ad issen ma SIDI issehwen xas abrid nnes niɣ lla.  
\v 22 Umi jjiwnen iřeɣman tisessi, iksi weryaz deg ijj n umur ict n txadent n wureɣ, \add tenni iweznen\add* azyen ciqlu, d tnayen n tmeqyasin i ifassen nnes, \add tinni iweznen\add* ɛecra ciqlu n wureɣ,  
\v 23 inna: “Ini ayi, umi teggid d yeǧis? Ma aqa din amcan di taddart n babam mani nzemmar ad nessens?”  
\v 24 Nettat tenna as: “Necc d yeǧis n Bituwil, mmis n Milka, wenni i-tt-i-dd-yurwen i Naḥur.” \x ◘ \xo 24:24 \xt Amz. 22:23. \x*  
\v 25 Uca tarni tenna as: “Aqa ɛawed ɣarneɣ aṭṭas n uřum d iɣeǧ, u ɣarneɣ ɛawed amcan i tmensiwt.”  
\v 26 Uca yuḍar weryaz uca ibendeq i SIDI,  
\v 27 inna: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI n sidi inu Ibrahim, wenni war ikkisen tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren d řaman nnes zi sidi inu. Indeh ayi SIDI deg webrid ɣar taddart n wawmaten n sidi inu.”   
\m
\v 28 Tuzzeř tebřiɣt, tɛawed timesřayin-a i yemmas di taddart.  
\v 29 Uca Rifqa tuɣa ɣares umas, qqaren as Laban, uca Laban yuzzeř ɣar weryaz nni tuɣa \add din\add* di barra ɣar řɛunṣar.  
\v 30 Tuɣa iẓra taxadent d tnayen n tmeqyasin deg ifassen n učmas uca isřa i wawařen i tuɣa teqqar učmas Rifqa, tenna: “Ammu i kidi issiweř weryaz nni.” Uca yuyur ɣar weryaz. Xzar, ibedd \add diha\add* zzat i iřeɣman, ɣar řɛunṣar.  
\v 31 Inna: “Araḥ-dd, \add a cek d\add* amimun n SIDI! Mayemmi teqqimed di barra, necc aqa sswejdeɣ taddart d wemcan i iřeɣman.”  
\v 32 Iruḥ weryaz akides ɣar taddart u netta iḍřeq i iseɣwan n iřeɣman. Netta iwca asen řum d macca, uca iksi aman, ḥima ad issird iḍaren nnes uřa d iḍaren n iryazen nni kides iǧan.  
\v 33 Issars zzates min ɣa yecc. Uca netta inna: “War ttᵉtteɣ qbeř i ɣa iniɣ tabrat inu.” Netta inna as: “Siweř!”  
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Necc d amsexxar n Ibrahim.  
\v 35 SIDI ibark sidi inu aṭṭas s waṭṭas uca ccan nnes imɣar aṭṭas. Aqa iwca as uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin, nnuqart d wureɣ, isemɣan d tiyya, iřeɣman d yeɣyař.  
\v 36 D Sara, tamɣart n sidi inu, turuw-dd aḥenjir i sidi inu awarni umi tewsar u netta iwca as marra min ɣares.  
\v 37 Uca sidi inu ijja ayi jjuǧeɣ, inna: ‘War dd-ttawi tamɣart i mmi zi tḥenjirin n ayt n Kenɛan inni mani zedɣeɣ di temmurt nsen.  
\v 38 \add Uct xak\add* mařa war ttriḥed ɣar taddart n baba, ɣar raǧ inu uca ad dd-tawyed tamɣart i mmi \add ssenni\add*.’  
\v 39 \add Xenni\add* necc nniɣ i sidi inu: ‘Balak tamɣart war d ayi dd-tḍeffar.’  
\v 40 Uca netta inna ayi: ‘SIDI i umi uyureɣ zzat i wudem nnes, aqa Netta ad dd-issekk lmalak nnes akidek uca ad xak issehwen abrid nnec ař dd ɣa tawyed i mmi ict n temɣart zi řaǧ inu u zi taddart n baba.  
\v 41 Ad tiřid tfekked zi tjaǧit i d ayi tejjuǧed, xmi ɣa traḥed ɣar řaǧ inu u nitni war d ac tt tticen, \add xenni\add* ad cek ssuffɣeɣ zi tjaǧit nnec i tuɣa tejjuǧed.’  
\v 42 Ass-a usiɣ-dd ɣar řɛunṣar uca nniɣ: ‘\add A\add* SIDI, AREBBI n sidi inu Ibrahim, ttzawageɣ ad tᵉsshewned řexxu abrid i di ggureɣ.  
\v 43 Aqa ayi da zzat i řɛunṣar n waman. Ejj ad tiři ammu, aqa taɛzarect, tenni dd ɣa iffɣen, maḥend ad tayem aman u i tenni umi ɣa iniɣ: Ewc ayi ad sweɣ cwayt n waman zeg uqbuc nnem!  
\v 44 uca \add xenni\add* nettat ad ayi tini: Su cek u necc ad aymeɣ ɛawed i iřeɣman nnec!, d ta ad tiři d tamɣart nni d issewjed SIDI i mmis n sidi inu.’  
\v 45 Uca qbeř i ɣa kemmřeɣ \add taẓaǧit-a\add* deg wuř inu, xzar, Rifqa teffeɣ-dd s uqbuc nnes x teɣruḍt nnes, tehwa ɣar řɛunṣar uca tuyem-dd aman. Nniɣ as: ‘Ttzawgeɣ cem ad ayi tewced ad sweɣ!’  
\v 46 Deɣya tessehwa aqbuc nnes, tenna: ‘Su u necc ad ssesweɣ ɛawed iřeɣman nnec!’ Swiɣ uca nettat tewca ɛawed i iřeɣman ad swen.  
\v 47 Sseqsiɣ tt, nniɣ: ‘Umi teggid d yeǧis?’ Nettat tarra: ‘\add Necc d\add* yeǧis n Bituwil, mmis n Naḥur wenni d as dd-yurwen Milka.’ \add Xenni\add* ggiɣ as taxadent di tinzart nnes d tmeqyasin deg ifassen nnes.  
\v 48 \add Xas uca\add* uḍareɣ, bendqeɣ i SIDI uca barkeɣ SIDI, AREBBI n sidi inu Ibrahim, wenni d ayi inedhen nican deg webrid, ḥima ad dd-awyeɣ iǧis n umas n sidi inu d temɣart i mmis.  
\v 49 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, mařa kenniw texsem ad tessecnem tamexsiwt icewwaren d řaman i sidi inu, ini ayi t, mařa lla, ini ayi t \add ɛawed\add*, \add xenni\add* ad kkeɣ yefus niɣ uzeřmaḍ.”  
\v 50 \add Xenni\add* Laban d Bituwil arrin-dd, nnan: “Zi SIDI i dd-iffeɣ uya, war nzemmar ad dayek nini řɣar niɣ řxar.  
\v 51 Xzar, Rifqa qibač nnec, ksi \add tt\add* uca truḥed. Ad tiři nettat d tamɣart n mmis n sidi nnec, am mammec inna SIDI!”   
\m
\v 52 Umi isřa umsexxar n Ibrahim awařen nsen, ibendeq ɣar temmurt zzat i SIDI.  
\v 53 Uca issuffeɣ-dd umsexxar řeqcuɛ n nnuqart d řeqcuɛ n wureɣ d warruḍen, iwca i-ten i Rifqa. Ɛawed iwca tirzifin iɣřan i umas d yemmas.  
\v 54 Ccin, swin, netta d yeryazen inni kis dd-yusin. Ssensen \add din\add* uca faqen ɣar ṣṣbeḥ. \add Xenni\add* inna: “Samḥem ayi ad raḥeɣ \add řexxu\add* ɣar sidi inu!”  
\v 55 Arrin-dd umas d yemmas: “Ejj tabřiɣt akidneɣ waxxa mɣir ɛecra n wussan, awarni as ad tuyured.”  
\v 56 Maca netta inna asen: “War dayi tᵉṭṭifem ɛad umi SIDI issehwen abrid inu! Mɣir ejj ayi ad raḥeɣ ɣar sidi inu.”  
\v 57 Nitni arrin-dd řexdenni: “Ejj aneɣ ad nřaɣa i tebřiɣt, ad nseř \add i min ɣa tini\add* zeg uqemmum nnes.”  
\v 58 Řaɣan i Rifqa uca nnan as: “Ma ad traḥed cem ak-d weryaz-a?” Uca nettat tarra-dd: “Wah, ad raḥeɣ.”  
\v 59 \add Xenni\add* ssqebbḍen nitni Rifqa, učmatsen, ak-d tmeṭṭaḍt nnes, uca \add ssqebbḍen\add* ɛawed amsexxar n Ibrahim d iryazen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 24:59 \xt Amz. 35:8\x*  
\v 60 Uca barken Rifqa, nnan as: “\add A\add* učmatneɣ, ad tawḍed ad temɣared d řuřuf n ɛecra n řuřuf uca zzariɛet nnem ad tᵉṭṭef tawwart n yinni tt icarrhen!” \x ◘ \xo 24:60 \xt Amz. 3:14\x*  
\v 61 Tekkar Rifqa d temsexxarin nnes timeẓyanin, nyint x iřeɣman, ḍfarent aryaz. \add Ammu\add* i dd-yiwi umsexxar Rifqa uca iruḥ.   
\m
\v 62 Aqa iffeɣ-dd Isḥaq zeg wanu n Laḥay-Ru’i. Tuɣa izeddeɣ di Temmurt n Ljanub. \x ◘ \xo 24:62 \xt Amz. 16:14; 25:11. \x*  
\v 63 Iffeɣ-dd Isḥaq maḥend ad iẓẓaǧ deg iyyar. Tuɣa-tt ɣar uweṭṭu n tmeddit. Netta issgeɛɛed tamuɣři nnes, iqceɛ, u xzar, iřeɣman ttqarraben-dd!  
\v 64 Rifqa ɛawed tessgeɛɛed tiṭṭawin nnes, teẓra Isḥaq. Nettat tejja ixef nnes ad tḍar deɣya x weřɣem  
\v 65 uca tenna i umsexxar: “Min iɛna weryaz nni dd-yusin deg iyyar ɣarneɣ?” Uca inna umsexxar: “Wa d sidi inu!” Xenni teksi takenbuct uca třeḥḥef.  
\v 66 Uca iɛawed umsexxar i Isḥaq marra min igga.  
\v 67 Igewwed i-tt Isḥaq ɣar uqiḍun n yemmas Sara, yiwi Rifqa uca nettat tedweř d tamɣart nnes u netta tuɣa ittexs i-tt. Ammu i ifewwej Isḥaq awarni \add řmewt\add* n yemmas.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 25
\s1 Tarwa n Ibrahim  
\m
\v 1 Iksi Ibrahim tamɣart nneɣni, qqaren as Qatura. \f ◼ \fr 25:1 \ft \+fk Qatura\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘řebxur’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 25:1 \xt [1 Im. 1:28-42] \x*  
\v 2 Netta turuw as-dd Zimran, Yaqcan, Midyan, Yicbaq d Cuḥa. \x ◘ \xo 25:2 \xt 1 Im. 1:32. \x*  
\v 3 Yuqcan ijja-dd Caba d Dadan. Uca arrawen n Dadan tuɣa aten d Iccuriyyen d Ilituciyyen d Iliyumiyyen.  
\v 4 Iḥenjiren n Midyan \add tuɣa aten d\add* Ɛiyfa, Ɛifar, Ḥanux, Abidaɛ d Aldaɛa. Marra ina \add tuɣa aten d\add* iḥenjiren n Qaṭura.  
\v 5 Ibrahim iwca marra min ɣares i Isḥaq. \x ◘ \xo 25:5 \xt Amz. 24:36. \x*  
\v 6 Maca i iḥenjiren n tiyya i tuɣa ɣar Ibrahim, iwca asen Ibrahim arriɣalut uca, am t tuɣa \add ɛad\add* iddar, issekk i-ten ssenni ɣar ccarq, ɣar temmurt n ccarq, issiggʷej i-ten x Isḥaq mmis.  
\v 7 Ibrahim tuɣa iddar mya u-xemsa u-sebɛin n iseggʷusa, wa d řmijař n tudart nnes.  
\v 8 Iḍřeq Ibrahim i buḥbeř nnes uca immut di ccib isegged, di tewsar d tyawant. Uca immarni ɣar řgens nnes. \x ◘ \xo 25:8 \xt Amz. 15:15. \x*  
\v 9 Isḥaq d Ismaɛil, iḥenjiren nnes, neḍřen t deg ifri n Makfila deg iyyar n Ɛifrun, mmis n Ṣuḥar, Aḥitti, \add iyyar\add* i iǧan qibač i Mamri.  
\v 10 Ittwanḍeř Ibrahim d temɣart nnes Sara deg iyyar nni isɣa Ibrahim zi tarwa n Ḥit.   
\m
\v 11 Awarni i řmewt n Ibrahim ibarek AREBBI mmis Isḥaq. Uca izdeɣ Isḥaq zzat i wanu n Laḥay-Ru’i. \f ◼ \fr 25:11 \ft \+fk Laḥay-Ru’i\ft  - xzar Amz. 16:14.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 \bd Ina d imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen \+bdit zi\+bdit* Ismaɛil, mmis n Ibrahim,\bd* inni dd-tejja Hajar, tayya n Sara zi Miṣra, i Ibrahim.  
\v 13 D yina d ismawen n iḥenjiren n Ismaɛil, s ismawen nsen ɛlaḥsab axřaq nsen. Amenzu n Ismaɛil \add tuɣa-t d\add* Nabayut, \add xenni\add* Qidar, Adbiyil, Mibsam, \x ◘ \xo 25:13 \xt 1 Im. 1:29. \x*  
\v 14 Misma, Duma, Massa,  
\v 15 Ḥadar, Tayma, Yaṭur, Nafic d Qidma.  
\v 16 D yina d iḥenjiren n Ismaɛil s ismawen nsen, s dcurat nsen d řmarageḥ nsen: tenɛac n řḥukkam s řaǧat nsen.  
\v 17 Tuɣa iddar Ismaɛil mya u-sebɛa u-třatin n iseggʷusa. \add Xenni\add* iḍřeq Ismaɛil i buḥbeř nnes, immut uca immarni ɣar řgens nnes.  
\v 18 Nitni zeddɣen zi Ḥawila ɣar Cur, wenni iǧan arendad n Miṣra, am tᵉṭṭfed abrid ɣar Accur. Netta izdeɣ arendad n marra aytmas.  
\b  
\m \bd Ina d imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen \+bdit zi\+bdit* Isḥaq, mmis n Ibrahim.\bd*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yaɛqub d Ɛisu  
\m
\v 19 Ibrahim ijja-dd Isḥaq.  
\v 20 Tuɣa ɣar Isḥaq arebɛin n iseggʷusa umi yiwi Rifqa d tamɣart. Nettat d yeǧis n Bituwil, Aramiyu zi Faddan-Aram, učmas n Laban, Aramiyu.  
\v 21 Iḥeccem Isḥaq SIDI di ṭṭweɛ n temɣart nnes, tenni tuɣa war ittirwen ca, uca istajeb as SIDI s tẓaǧit nnes yuǧɣen, ařami teksi temɣart nnes, Rifqa, ddeyset. \x ◘ \xo 25:21 \xt Rum. 9:10. \x*  
\v 22 Uca mmdeḥsen iḥenjiren deg uɛeddis nnes. \add Xenni\add* tenna: “Manawya \add ɛawed\add*, mayemmi d ayi ittemsar man aya?”, uca truḥ ad tesseqsa SIDI.  
\v 23 Inna as SIDI: “Aqa din tnayen n řegnus di ddeyset nnem u tnayen n ccuɛub ad mmsebḍan zi dwaxeř nnem. Ijj n cceɛb ad yiři ijhed x cceɛb nneɣni u wenni d amenzu ad ixdem i umaẓuẓ.” \x ◘ \xo 25:23 \xt 2 Ṣm. 8:14; Rum. 9:12. \x*  
\v 24 Ařami dd-iwḍen wussan nnes ad taru, xzar, aqa da deg uɛeddis nnes acniwen.  
\v 25 Iffeɣ-dd umezwar. Tuɣa-t d azeggʷaɣ, iceɛɛar qaɛ am yict n thiḍurt. S uyenni ggin as Ɛisu. \f ◼ \fr 25:25 \ft \+fk Ɛisu\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘azeggʷaɣ’ niɣ ‘iḥḥarcuw’.\f*  
\v 26 Awarni as iffeɣ-dd umas. Iṭṭef afus nnes deg unirz n Ɛisu. S uya semman t s yisem Yaɛqub. Tuɣa ɣar Isḥaq settin n iseggʷusa ɣar wexřaq nsen. \x ◘ \xo 25:26 \xt Ḥuc. 12:4. \x*   
\m
\v 27 \add Řami\add* gman iḥenjiren, idweř Ɛisu d ijj n weryaz issen aneymar, ijj n weryaz n barra, maca Yaɛqub idweř d ijj n weryaz yarsa, wenni izeddɣen deg iqiḍan. \f ◼ \fr 25:27 \ft \+fk aryaz yarsa\ft  - awař Aɛibrani ixs ad yini s lḥarf ‘aryaz ikemřen’ niɣ ‘aryaz břa řɛib’, maca di ca n twařawin am řexxu nzemmar ad nini ‘aryaz amtiqqi’, niɣ ‘aryaz yarsan’.\f*  
\v 28 Isḥaq tuɣa ittexs Ɛisu, minzi iɛjeb as ad yecc aysum n řmař n řexřa, u Rifqa tuɣa tᵉttexs Yaɛqub.  
\v 29 Uca issnenni Yaɛqub ict n macca, umi dd-iɛqeb Ɛisu zi řexřa, yuḥeř.  
\v 30 Inna Ɛisu i Yaɛqub: “Ttzawgeɣ cek ad ayi tewced ad cceɣ zeg uzeggʷaɣ, azeggʷaɣ nni diha, maɣar aqa fniɣ \add s ufadi\add*.” X uya qqaren as ‘Idum’. \f ◼ \fr 25:30 \ft \+fk Idum\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘azeggwaɣ’.\f*  
\v 31 \add Řexdenni\add* inna Yaɛqub: “Zenz ayi ass-a \add řḥeqq\add* nnec \add n\add* umenzu.”  
\v 32 Inna Ɛisu: “Xzar, aqa necc ad mmteɣ, min ɣa ggeɣ s \add řḥeqq n\add* umenzu?” \x ◘ \xo 25:32 \xt Ica. 22:13; 1 Kur. 15:32. \x*  
\v 33 \add Xenni\add* inna Yaɛqub: “Jaǧ ayi řexxu!” Uca ijjuǧ as, izzenz i Yaɛqub \add řḥeqq n\add* umenzu nnes.  
\v 34 \add Xas uca\add* iwca Yaɛqub i Ɛisu aɣrum d umecři n řeɛdes, u Ɛisu icca, iswa, ikkar, iruḥ. \add Ammu\add* isseḥqar Ɛisu \add řḥeqq n\add* umenzu nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 26
\s1 Řɛahd jar Isḥaq d Abimalik  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa iǧa řaẓ di temmurt, ijj n řaẓ nneɣni x umezwar nni tuɣa iǧan deg wussan n Ibrahim. S uya iruḥ Isḥaq ɣar Abimalik, ajeǧid n Ifilisṭiniyyen, ɣar \add jjwayeh n\add* Jirar.  
\v 2 \add Dinni\add* iban as-dd SIDI, inna: “War hekkwi ca ɣar Miṣra. Zdeɣ di temmurt i d ac ɣa iniɣ.  
\v 3 Zdeɣ di temmurt-a am ubarrani u Necc ad kik iřiɣ, ad cek barkeɣ, minzi i cek u i zzariɛet nnec umi ɣa wceɣ marra timmura-ya uca ad kemmřeɣ tjaǧit i jjuǧeɣ i Ibrahim babac. \x ◘ \xo 26:3 \xt Amz. 13:15; 15:18. \x*  
\v 4 Ad kettareɣ zzariɛet nnec am yitran n ujenna uca ad wceɣ i zzariɛet nnec marra timmura-ya. Marra řegnus n ddunect ad ttwabarken di zzariɛet nnec, \x ◘ \xo 26:4 \xt Amz. 12:3; 18:18; 22:18. \x*  
\v 5 minzi isřa Ibrahim i wawař inu uca iḥḍa min d as wciɣ maḥend ad iḥḍa: řumurat inu, tiweṣṣa inu d izerfan inu.”  
\v 6 Ammu i iqqim Isḥaq izeddeɣ di Jirar.   
\m
\v 7 \add Řami\add* t sseqsan iryazen n wemcan nni x temɣart nnes, inna asen: “Nettat d učma!”, minzi iggʷed ad yini: “D tamɣart inu!”. \add Maɣar inna deg yixef nnes:\add* “Mařa war nniɣ amenni ad ayi nɣen iryazen n wemcan-a di ṭṭweɛ n Rifqa, minzi aqa dayes aẓri.”  
\v 8 Řami din izdeɣ aṭṭas n wussan, imsar belli Abimalik, ajeǧid n Ifilisṭiniyyen, ixzar-dd zi řkazi, iẓra Isḥaq ittɛatab Rifqa, tamɣart nnes.  
\v 9 Uca iřaɣa Abimalik x Isḥaq, inna as: “Xzar, ta s tidett d tamɣart nnec! Mammec teggid tennid aneɣ d učma?” Isḥaq inna as: “S minzi nniɣ \add i yixef inu\add*: ‘Aqa tiři ad ayi nɣen x ssibbet nnes.’”  
\v 10 Abimalik inna: “Maɣar d aneɣ teggid aya? X drus ad yiři iṭṭeṣ ca n ijj zi řgens ak-d temɣart nnec uca ad tiři teggid ddenb x yiři nneɣ.”  
\v 11 Yumur Abimalik marra řgens, inna: “Wenni i ɣa iḥadan aryaz-a niɣ tamɣart nnes, ad t nɣen nican!”   
\m
\v 12 Izarɛ Isḥaq di temmurt nni uca iksi aseggʷas nni mya n imuren n zzyada, \add minzi\add* ibark i-t SIDI.  
\v 13 Temmarni ccenɛet n weryaz \add nni\add* uca netta iqqim imeqqar, ařami tedweř ccenɛet nnes d tameqqrant aṭṭas.  
\v 14 Tuɣa ɣares uǧi u ɣares \add ɛawed\add* ifunasen d tfunasin d waṭṭas n isemɣan, ařami zzayes usmen Ifilisṭiniyyen.  
\v 15 Marra anuten nni ɣzan imsexxaren deg wussan n Ibrahim babas, netyen ten Ifilisṭiniyyen uca ccuren ten s ucař.  
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* inna Abimalik i Isḥaq: “Beɛɛed xaneɣ, minzi tdewřed tjehded xaneɣ s waṭṭas.”  
\v 17 Isḥaq iruḥ ssenni, iwta iqiḍan nnes di teɣzurt n Jirar uca izdeɣ dinni.  
\v 18 Uca idweř Isḥaq iɣza anuten n waman inni tuɣa ɣzin deg wussan n Ibrahim babas, inni netyen Ifilisṭiniyyen awarni i řmewt n Ibrahim. Isemma ten s ismawen inni d asen iřaɣa babas.  
\v 19 Uca imsexxaren n Isḥaq ɣzan di teɣzurt nni uca ufin din řɛunṣar n waman ddaren.  
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* qacḥen imeksawen n Jirar ak-d imeksawen n Isḥaq, nnan: “Aman nneɣ!” \add S uyenni\add* řaɣan isem n řɛunṣar nni ‘Ɛisiq’, minzi tuɣa ttqacaḥen xas. \f ◼ \fr 26:20 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* ɣzan ijj n řɛunṣar nneɣni uca mmennɣen xas ɛawed. \add S uyenni\add* d as igga isem n ‘Sitna’.  
\v 22 Uca ibeɛɛed ssenni, iɣza ijj n řɛunṣar nneɣni, war xas qicḥen ca uca ggin as isem nnes ‘Raḥubut’, inna: “Řexxu SIDI iwca aneɣ ttasiɛ uca ad ɣarneɣ tiři řɣiǧet di temmurt.”  
\v 23 Uca igeɛɛed ssenni ɣar Bi’r-Sebɛa.   
\m
\v 24 Iban as-dd SIDI di ǧiret nni, inna as: “Necc d AREBBI n Ibrahim babac! War tteggʷed ca, aqa Necc akidek u Necc ad cek barkeɣ, ad kettareɣ zzariɛet nnec di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar inu Ibrahim.”  
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* ibna din ijj n uɛalṭar \add min xef igga taɣarṣt\add*, uca iřaɣa Isem n SIDI. Iwta din aqiḍun nnes uca ɣzin din imsexxaren n Isḥaq ijj n wanu.  
\v 26 Abimalik yusa-dd ɣares zi Jirar, ak-d Aḥuzzat, ameddukkeř nnes, d Fikul, akumandar n řɛeskar nnes.  
\v 27 Inna asen Isḥaq: “Maɣar ɣari dd-tusim, waxxa kenniw tcarrhem ayi uca tessuffɣem ayi xawem?”  
\v 28 Nitni nnan: “Aqa neẓra belli SIDI akidek. S uya nenna, ad din tiři řexxu ict n tjaǧit jaraneɣ, jaraneɣ d cek, uca ejj aneɣ ad kik negg ijj n řɛahd,  
\v 29 ḥima cek war d aneɣ tᵉttegged řɣar, am mammec uřa d neccin war cek nḥidi ca uca aqa nemṣurref akidek mliḥ uca nessekk i cek di řaman. Aqa cek řexxu d amimun n SIDI!”  
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* igga asen ict n zzardet uca ccin, swin.  
\v 31 Kkaren zic uca jjuǧen ijjen i wenneɣni. Xas uca issqebbeḍ i-ten Isḥaq uca ruḥen nitni zi ɣares di řehna.   
\m
\v 32 Deg wass nni d ijj usin-dd imsexxaren n Isḥaq, xebbaren t x wanu i iɣzan uca nnan as: “D aman i nufa.”  
\v 33 Isemma \add anu-ya\add* Sebɛa. X uya i iǧa yisem n tendint nni Bi’r-Sebɛa, ař ass-a.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Timɣarin n Ɛisu  
\m
\v 34 Umi tuɣa ɣar Ɛisu arebɛin n iseggʷusa, yiwi Yudit, yeǧis n Biri, Aḥitti, d tamɣart, uřa d Basmat, yeǧis n Ilun, Aḥitti. \f ◼ \fr 26:34 \ft \+fk Biri\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘anu inu’. \fk Basmat\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘ittfuḥen’ niɣ ‘řeɛṭur’. \fk Ilun\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘tacejjart n řbeǧuḍ’.\f*  
\v 35 Tuɣa atent d tarzugi n wuř i Isḥaq d Rifqa. \x ◘ \xo 26:35 \xt Amz. 27:46. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 27
\s1 Isḥaq ibarek Yaɛqub  
\m
\v 1 Řami idweř Isḥaq d awessar u tiṭṭawin nnes ɛemcent ařami ɛřaḥař war ittwiři, iřaɣa Ɛisu, mmis amenzu, inna as: “Mmi!” Uca netta inna as: “Aqa ayi da!”  
\v 2 Uca inna: “Aqa necc wsareɣ, war ssineɣ ass i di ɣa mmteɣ.  
\v 3 Řexxu, ksi řesnaḥ nnec d weqrab nnec n fřitcat d řqews nnec, teffɣed ɣar řexřa uca gmar ayi-dd taymart i macca.  
\v 4 Sewjed ayi-dd ict n macca icnan i d ayi ɣa iɛejben uca tewced ayi tt-i-dd, ad tt cceɣ, ḥima ad cek barkeɣ qbeř ma ad mmteɣ.”  
\v 5 Rifqa tuɣa tesřa umi issiweř Isḥaq ak-d mmis Ɛisu. Uca iruḥ Ɛisu ɣar řexřa ḥima ad iymar timeyra, maḥend ad tt-i-dd-yawi.  
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* tessiweř Rifqa ak-d Yaɛqub mmis, tenna as: “Xzar, necc sřiɣ babac issawař ak-d Ɛisu umac, inna \add as\add*:  
\v 7 ‘Awi ayi-dd ict n teymart uca sewjed ayi ict n macca lemliḥ, maḥend ad tt cceɣ, ḥima necc ad ac barkeɣ qibač i wudem n SIDI qbeř i ɣa mmteɣ.’  
\v 8 Řexxu, mmi, seř-dd ɣari min zi cek ɣa umureɣ.  
\v 9 Řuh ɣar tḥimart uca awi ayi-dd tnayen n iɣayḍen imeẓyanen zeg iɣayḍen. Necc ad zzaysen sswejdeɣ ict n macca icnan i babac, am mammec d as ittaɛjib  
\v 10 u ittxeṣṣa cek ad t tawyed i babac, ad yecc, ḥima ad cek ibarek qbeř řmewt nnes.”  
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna Yaɛqub i Rifqa, yemmas: “Xzar, Ɛisu uma d aryaz bu-cɛar u necc d aryaz d ařeqqaɣ.  
\v 12 Balak ad ayi iḥada baba uca ad iřiɣ amecnaw aɣeccac di tiṭṭawin nnes. \add Xenni\add* ad ksiɣ ict n nneɛřet xafi, war kessiɣ lbaraka.”  
\v 13 Yemmas tenna as: “Nneɛřet nnec ad tiři xafi, a mmi! Ṭaɛ i wawař inu waha, awyi ten-dd ɣari.”   
\m
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* netta iruḥ, iksi \add ten\add* uca yiwyi \add ten\add* i yemmas. Uca yemmas tegga ict n macca icnan am mammec d as ittaɛjib i babas.  
\v 15 Teksi Rifqa arruḍ ifeccḥen aṭṭas i tuɣa ɣares di taddart zeg warruḍ n Ɛisu, mmis amenzu, uca tarḍ \add i-t\add* Yaɛqub, mmis amaẓuẓ. \f ◼ \fr 27:15 \ft \+fk di taddart\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘deg uqiḍun’.\f*  
\v 16 Tegga as iřem n iɣayḍen imeẓyanen zeg iɣayḍen x ifassen nnes u x yiri nnes ařeqqaɣ.  
\v 17 Tewca macca-ya icnan ak-d weɣrum nni tenggʷa deg ifassen n mmis Yaɛqub.  
\v 18 Netta yusa-dd ɣar babas, inna: “\add A\add* Baba!” Netta inna: “Aqa ayi da! Min teɛnid cek, \add a\add* mmi?”  
\v 19 Inna Yaɛqub i babas: “Necc d Ɛisu, amenzu nnec. Ggiɣ min d ayi tennid. Kkar řexxu, qqim, ecc zi tmeyra inu, ḥima ad ayi ibarek řeɛmar nnec.”  
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* inna Isḥaq i mmis: “Mammec teggid tufid tt deɣya, \add a\add* mmi?” Inna: “Maɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, igga \add i-tt\add* deg webrid inu.”  
\v 21 Isḥaq inna i Yaɛqub: “Qarreb-dd řexxu, ḥima ad cek ḥadiɣ, \add a\add* mmi, ma cek d mmi Ɛisu niɣ lla.”  
\v 22 \add Řami\add* dd-iqarreb Yaɛqub ɣar babas Isḥaq, iḥada t uca inna: “Tmijja d tmijja n Yaɛqub, \add maca\add* ifassen d ifassen n Ɛisu.”  
\v 23 Netta war t iɛqiř, minzi ifassen nnes tuɣa ceɛɛaren amecnaw ifassen n Ɛisu uca ibark i-t.  
\v 24 Inna: “Ma d cek d mmi Ɛisu?” Netta inna: “D necc!”  
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Sqarreb ayi tt-i-dd zzati, ḥima ad cceɣ zi tmeyra n mmi, ḥima necc ad cek barkeɣ.” Issars i-tt-i-dd zzates uca icca. Yiwi as-dd ɛawed binu uca iswa. \f ◼ \fr 27:25 \ft \+fk ḥima necc ad cek barkeɣ\ft  - s lḥarf ‘ḥima ad cek ibarek řeɛmar inu’\f*  
\v 26 Inna as babas Isḥaq: “Qarreb-dd ɣari řexxu, sudem ayi, \add a\add* mmi!”  
\v 27 Uca iqarreb-dd ɣares, issudem i-t. Icemm Isḥaq arriḥet n warruḍ nnes uca ibark i-t, inna: “Xzar, řefwaḥet n mmi am řefwaḥet n yeyyar i ibarek SIDI.  
\v 28 Ad ac iwc AREBBI zi nnda n ujenna u zi řeydam n temmurt uřa d waṭṭas n imendi d binu n jdid. \x ◘ \xo 27:28 \xt Ɛbr. 11:20. \x*  
\v 29 Ad ac xedmen řegnus uca ccuɛub ad ac bendqen. Ḥkem x aytmac u ejj iḥenjiren n yemmac ad ac bendqen! Inni cek i ɣa ineɛřen, ad ttwaneɛřen, u inni cek ɣa ibarken, ad ttwabarken.” \x ◘ \xo 27:29 \xt Amz. 12:3. \x*   
\m
\v 30 Awarni řami ikemmeř Isḥaq lbaraka i Yaɛqub uca am dd-iffeɣ Yaɛqub \add ɛad\add* x babas Isḥaq, iɛqeb-dd Ɛisu, umas, zi teymart nnes.  
\v 31 Issewjed xenni ict n macca icnan uca iksi tt ɣar babas, inna as: “Ttzawgeɣ, baba, kkar tecced zi teymart n mmic, \add ḥima\add* cek ad ayi tbarked.” \f ◼ \fr 27:31 \ft \+fk \+bdit ḥima\+bdit* cek ad ayi tbarked\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ḥima ad ayi ibarek řeɛmar nnec’\f*  
\v 32 Inna as Isḥaq, babas: “Min teɛnid cek?” Netta inna: “Necc d mmic, amenzu nnec, Ɛisu.”  
\v 33 Uca innexřeɛ Isḥaq, inna: “Min iɛna wanita i dd-yusin da, iṭṭef taymart uca yiwi ayi tt-i-dd? Cciɣ zi marra \add man aya\add* qbeř dd-tusid uca necc barkeɣ t u ad ittwabarek ɛawed.”  
\v 34 Umi isřa Ɛisu awařen n babas, isɣuy s yijj n řeɛyad ijhed yarzeg, inna i babas: “Barek ayi uřa d necc, \add a\add* baba!” \x ◘ \xo 27:34 \xt Ɛbr. 12:17. \x*  
\v 35 Inna: “Yusa-dd umac s teḥraymect, iksi lbaraka nnec.”  
\v 36 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Ma war iǧi isem nnes s řḥeqq Yaɛqub? Aqa icmet ayi tnayen n twařawin. Iksi \add řḥeqq n\add* umenzu inu uca aqa řexxu iksi \add ɛawed\add* lbaraka inu.” \add Xenni\add* inna: “Ma war ɣarek teqqim ca n lbaraka i necc?” \x ◘ \xo 27:36 \xt Amz. 25:33. \x*  
\v 37 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd Isḥaq, inna i Ɛisu: “Xzar, necc ggiɣ t d řḥakem xak uca wciɣ as aytmas d imsexxaren, uřa s imendi d binu n jdid ɛewwřeɣ t. Min din ɛad, ad ac wceɣ řexxu, \add a\add* mmi?”  
\v 38 Inna Ɛisu i babas: “Ma ɣarek mɣir lbaraka-ya waha, \add a\add* baba? Barek ayi ɛawed, uřa d necc, \add a\add* baba!” Uca issgeɛɛed Ɛisu tmijja nnes, isɣuy. \x ◘ \xo 27:38 \xt Ɛbr. 12:17. \x*  
\v 39 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd Isḥaq x babas, inna as: “Xzar, ad tiři tzeddiɣt nnec iggʷejjen x řeydam n temmurt u x nnda n ujenna sennej.  
\v 40 S ssif nnec i ɣa teqqimed teddared u ad txedmed i umac. Maca xmi ɣa teqqimed ad tenhezzed, ad imsar ad tawḍed ad tekksed zayřu nnes x yiri nnec.”   
\m
\v 41 Uca icarh Ɛisu Yaɛqub di ssibbet n lbaraka i zi t ibarek babas, uca inna Ɛisu deg wuř nnes: “Ad awḍen wussan n uɛezzi n baba, xenni ad nɣeɣ uma Yaɛqub.”  
\v 42 \add Umi\add* nnan i Rifqa awařen n Ɛisu, mmis amenzu, tᵉssekk ijjen ad iřaɣa i Yaɛqub, mmis amaẓuẓ, tenna as: “Xzar, Ɛisu umac yarezzu mammec zzayek i ɣa ixřef, netta ixs ad cek ineɣ.  
\v 43 Řexxu, \add a\add* mmi, ṭaɛ i wawař inu. Kkar uca tarewřed ɣar Ḥaran ɣar uma Laban.  
\v 44 Zdeɣ akides ca n wussan ař ɣa yarsa wesɛar n umac.  
\v 45 Xmi ɣa ixsi uxeyyeq n umac uca ad ittu min d as teggid, necc ad ssekkeɣ \add ijjen\add*, maḥend ad cek dd-yawi ssenni. Mayemmi i zzaywem ɣa ttwaḥarrmeɣ s tnayen idwem deg ijj n wass?”   
\m
\v 46 Tenna Rifqa i Isḥaq: “Carrheɣ tudart inu di ssibbet n yessis n Ḥit. Mařa Yaɛqub yiwi tamɣart zi tebřiɣin n Ḥit, am tnayen-a, zi tḥenjirin n temmurt-a, man lqima i ɣa yiřin ɣar tudart inu?” \x ◘ \xo 27:46 \xt Amz. 26:35. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 28
\s1 Tarewřa n Yaɛqub d tarjit nnes di Bayt-Il  
\m
\v 1 Iřaɣa Isḥaq i Yaɛqub, ibarek i-t uca issekk i-t, inna as: “War ttawi tamɣart zi yessis n Kenɛan.  
\v 2 Kkar, ruḥ ɣar Fadan-Aram, ɣar taddart n Bituwil, babas n yemmac, uca awi-dd ssenni tamɣart i cek zeg yessis n Laban, umas n yemmac. \x ◘ \xo 28:2 \xt Ḥuc. 12:13. \x*  
\v 3 Arebbi, Amzemmar x kuřci, ad cek ibarek u ad ac iwc řɣiǧet uca ad cek ikettar ař ɣa tdewřed d ijj n wegraw n řegnus.  
\v 4 Iři Netta ad ac iwc lbaraka n Ibrahim, i cek u i zzariɛet nnec akidek, ḥima ad twarted tammurt nni di tzeddɣed am ubarrani, tenni iwca AREBBI i Ibrahim.” \x ◘ \xo 28:4 \xt Amz. 12:7; 13:15; 15:18; 24:7; 26:3; Aɛwd. 34:4; Řex. 7:5. \x*  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* issekk Isḥaq Yaɛqub. Uca netta iruḥ ɣar Faddan-Aram, ɣar Laban, mmis n Bituwil, Aramiyu, umas n Rifqa, yemmas n Yaɛqub d Ɛisu.   
\m
\v 6 \add Umi\add* iẓra Ɛisu belli Isḥaq ibarek Yaɛqub uca issekk i-t-i-dd ɣar Faddan-Aram ḥima ad yawi i yixef nnes tamɣart ssenni, u řami t ibarek, yumur i-t, inna as: “War kessi tamɣart zeg yessis n Kenɛan!”,  
\v 7 uca \add iẓra ɛawed\add* belli Yaɛqub iṭaɛ babas d yemmas, iruḥ ɣar Faddan-Aram,  
\v 8 \add xenni\add* itwařa Ɛisu belli yessis n Kenɛan d tiɛeffanin di tiṭṭawin n babas Isḥaq.  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* iruḥ Ɛisu ɣar Ismaɛil uca yiwi Maḥalat d tamɣart i yixef nnes, yarni tt-i-dd ɣar temɣarin nneɣni. Nettat tuɣa-tt d yeǧis n Ismaɛil, mmis n Ibrahim, učmas n Nabayut.   
\m
\v 10 Uca iffeɣ Yaɛqub zi Bi’r-Sebɛa, iruḥ ɣar Ḥaran.  
\v 11 Yiweḍ ɣar ijj n wemcan mani yensa, minzi tuɣa tafuct teɣri. Iksi zeg yeẓra n wemcan nni, issars i-ten sadu uzeǧif nnes uca iwḍa iṭṭeṣ deg wemcan nni.  
\v 12 Yurja, aqa ijj n ddruj ibedd x temmurt uca ittḥada ixef n ddruj ajenna, u xzar, lmalakat n AREBBI ttařyent hekkwant zzayes. \x ◘ \xo 28:12 \xt Yḥ. 1:52. \x*  
\v 13 U xzar, SIDI ibedd xas, inna: “Necc d SIDI, AREBBI n babac Ibrahim, d AREBBI n Isḥaq. Tammurt i xef tᵉṭṭṣed ad ac tt wceɣ i cek u i zzariɛet nnec. \x ◘ \xo 28:13 \xt Amz. 35:1, 3; 48:3; Aɛwd. 12:20; 19:8. \x*  
\v 14 Ad tiři zzariɛet nnec am ucař n temmurt uca ad tiriwed ɣar řɣarb d ccarq, ɣar ccamal d ljanub. Dayek u di zzariɛet nnec ad ttwabarkent marra řaǧat n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 28:14 \xt Amz. 12:3; 18:18; 22:18; 26:4. \x*  
\v 15 Aqa ayi Necc akidek u Necc ad cek ḥḍiɣ qaɛ mani i ɣa traḥed, ad cek arreɣ ɣar temmurt-a, minzi Necc war cek ttejjiɣ ař ɣa kemmřeɣ min d ac nniɣ.”  
\v 16 Řami dd-ifaq Yaɛqub zeg yiḍeṣ nnes, inna: “S tidett, SIDI aqa-t deg wemcan-a u necc war ssineɣ!”  
\v 17 Tuɣa iggʷed aṭṭas, inna: “Mecḥař issaggʷad wemcan-a! Aqa ta mɣir d Taddart n AREBBI u tanita d tawwart n ujenna!”   
\m
\v 18 Ikkar Yaɛqub uca iksi aẓru nni tuɣa issars sadu uzeǧif nnes, igga i-t am yijj n weẓru n řidaret uca ifarreɣ zzect x uzeǧif n weẓru. \x ◘ \xo 28:18 \xt Amz. 31:13; 35:14. \x*  
\v 19 Igga amcan nni Bayt-Il, maca zeg umezwaru tuɣa isem n wemcan nni Luz.  
\v 20 Uca iwaɛd Yaɛqub, inna: “Mařa AREBBI aqa-t akidi uca ad ayi iḥḍa deg webrid i ɣa uyureɣ, ad ayi iwc aɣrum ḥima ad cceɣ, d warruḍ ḥima ad arḍeɣ  
\v 21 u mařa dewřeɣ ɣar taddart n baba di řaman, xenni SIDI ad yiři d AREBBI i necc.  
\v 22 Uc aẓru-ya i ggiɣ d aẓru n řidaret, ad yiři d Taddart n AREBBI u zi marra min d ayi ɣa tewced, ad ac wceɣ řeɛcur!”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 29
\s1 Řemřac n Yaɛqub ak-d Liya d Raḥil  
\m
\v 1 Iksi Yaɛqub deg iḍaren nnes, iruḥ ɣar temmurt n ayt n ccarq.  
\v 2 Ixzar uca iẓra ijj n wanu deg iyyar u tuɣa din třata n tḥimriwin n wuǧi jnint zzates, minzi zeg wanu nni warrden nitni tiḥimriwin. Tuɣa din ijj n weẓru x uqemmum n wanu.  
\v 3 Ssmunen din marra tiḥimriwin. \add Xas uca\add* kksen aẓru x uqemmum n wanu uca warden uǧi. \add Awarni as\add* arrin aẓru \add ɛawed\add* x uqemmum n wanu.  
\v 4 Inna asen Yaɛqub: “Aytma inu, manis kenniw?” Nitni arrin-dd: “Zi Ḥaran i neǧa.”  
\v 5 Netta inna asen: “Ma tessnem Laban, mmis n Naḥur?” Nitni arrin-dd: “Wah, nessen i-t.”  
\v 6 Inna asen netta: “Mammec iǧa?” Arrin-dd: “Aqa-t mliḥ, aqa da yeǧis Raḥil tusa-dd ak-d wuǧi.”  
\v 7 Inna as: “Aqa da aziř ɛad imɣar, war yeǧi bu řweqt ḥima ad nendeh řebhayem. Wardem uǧi uca ruḥem, maḥend ad ten tarewsem.”  
\v 8 Nitni arrin-dd: “War nzemmar ad \add t\add* negg ař dd ɣa munent marra tiḥimriwin. \add Xenni\add* ad sseḥřuǧden aẓru x uqemmum n wanu, ḥima ad nwared uǧi.”   
\m
\v 9 Řami tuɣa \add ɛad\add* issawař akidsen, tusa-dd Raḥil s wuǧi n babas, minzi nettat tuɣa-tt d tameksawt.  
\v 10 Řami iẓra Yaɛqub Raḥil, yeǧis n Laban, umas n yemmas, ak-d wuǧi n Laban, umas n yemmas, ixecc-dd Yaɛqub uca isseḥřuǧed aẓru x uqemmum n wanu, iward uǧi n Laban, umas n yemmas.  
\v 11 Issudem Yaɛqub Raḥil, issgeɛɛed tmijja nnes uca isɣuy.  
\v 12 Inna Yaɛqub i Raḥil aqa netta zi řaǧ n babas i iǧa, uřa d mmis n Rifqa. Uca nettat tuzzeř, txebbar babas.   
\m
\v 13 Umi isřa Laban řexbar x Yaɛqub, mmis n učmas, yuzzeř ad t iřqa uca idarreɛ as, issudem i-t, indeh i-t ɣar taddart nnes. Uca netta iɛawed marra timesřayin-a i Laban.  
\v 14 Inna as Laban: “D tidett cek d iɣes inu d aysum inu i teǧid.” Uca iqqim ɣares řqedd n ijj n uyur ikmeř.  
\v 15 \add Řexdenni\add* inna Laban i Yaɛqub: “Umi cek d uma i teǧid, ma ad ɣari txedmed baṭeř? Ini ayi min \add i ɣa tiři\add* řmunet nnec?”  
\v 16 Laban ɣares tnayen n yessis. Isem n tmenzut d Liya u isem n tmaẓuẓt, Raḥil.  
\v 17 Tiṭṭawin n Liya tuɣa kecɛent, \add maca\add* Raḥil tuɣa dayes aẓři n waddud u n řxezrat.  
\v 18 Yaɛqub ixs Raḥil. Inna: “Necc ad ɣarek xedmeɣ sebɛa n iseggʷusa x Raḥil yeǧis tmaẓuẓt.” \x ◘ \xo 29:18 \xt Ḥuc. 12:13. \x*  
\v 19 Laban yarra-dd: “Xar ad ac tt wceɣ i cek niɣ ad tt wceɣ i weryaz nneɣni. Qqim akidi.”   
\m
\v 20 \add Ammu\add* i ixdem Yaɛqub x Raḥil sebɛa n iseggʷusa maca ḍharen as-dd \add iseggʷusa nni\add* amecnaw ca n wussan, minzi tuɣa ittexs i-tt.  
\v 21 Inna Yaɛqub i Laban: “Ewc ayi \add řexxu\add* tamɣart inu, minzi aqa kemmřen wussan \add n řmijař\add* inu, \add ařami\add* xas i ɣa yadfeɣ.”  
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* issmun Laban marra iryazen n wemcan nni, igga urar.  
\v 23 Ɣar tmeddit iksi yeǧis Liya uca issiweḍ i-tt ɣares uca yudef xas Yaɛqub.  
\v 24 Iwca Laban tayya nnes Zilpa i yeǧis Liya d tayya.  
\v 25 Tiwecca nnes iẓra \add Yaɛqub\add* belli d Liya. Xenni inna i Laban: “Min d ayi teggid? Ma war d ac xdimeɣ x Raḥil? Maɣar d ayi tcemted?”  
\v 26 Laban inna: “War ittiři uya di temmurt nneɣ ad nessizzar tamaẓuẓt x tmenzut.  
\v 27 Kemmeř ssimana-ya \add n wurar\add* n ta, xenni ad ac newc \add ɛawed\add* tin x řxedmet i ɣa tegged ssa tsawent akidi ɛad sebɛa n iseggʷusa nneɣni.”  
\v 28 Igga Yaɛqub \add amenni\add*, ikemmeř ssimana-ya \add n wurar\add*. \add Xenni\add* iwca as yeǧis Raḥil d tamɣart  
\v 29 uca iwca Laban tayya nnes Bilha i yeǧis Raḥil maḥend ad tiři d tayya nnes.  
\v 30 Yudef \add Yaɛqub\add* ɛawed x Raḥil uca ixs Raḥil ɛad ktar x Liya. Uca isexxar as ɛawed sebɛa n iseggʷusa nneɣni.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Iḥenjiren n Yaɛqub  
\m
\v 31 \add Umi\add* iẓra SIDI belli Liya tuɣa tᵉttwasseḥqar, yarzem řemřawet nnes, \add maca\add* Raḥil tuɣa war dd-tᵉttiruw ca.  
\v 32 Teksi Liya s ddeyset uca turuw-dd aḥenjir, igga as Rubin, minzi tenna: “Aqa SIDI ixzar ɣar řemḥayem inu. Řexxu ad ayi ixs weryaz inu.” \f ◼ \fr 29:32 \ft \+fk Rubin\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘xẓar, ijj n mmis!’.\f*  
\v 33 Teksi ɛawed s ddeyset, turuw-dd aḥenjir, tenna: “Umi isřa SIDI belli necc ttwasseḥqareɣ, iwca ayi ɛawed wa.” Uca tegga as Cimɛun.  
\v 34 Teksi ɛawed s ddeyset, turuw-dd aḥenjir, tenna: “Řexxu twařa-ya ad imun weryaz inu akidi, minzi urweɣ as-dd třata n iḥenjiren.” X uya netta igga as Lawi.  
\v 35 Teksi twařa nneɣni s ddeyset, turuw-dd aḥenjir uca tenna: “Twařa-ya ad qadiɣ SIDI.” X uya tegga as Yahuda. \add Awarni man aya\add* tessbedd tarwa. \f ◼ \fr 29:35 \ft \+fk Yahuda\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘ad ittwasemɣar Arebbi’.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 30
\m
\v 1 \add Umi\add* teẓra Raḥil belli war dd-tiruw i Yaɛqub, tusem zeg učmas, tenna i Yaɛqub: “Ewc ayi tarwa! Mařa war teqbiřed, \add xenni\add* ad mmteɣ.”  
\v 2 Ixeyyeq Yaɛqub x Raḥil, inna: “Ma aqa ayi necc deg wemcan n AREBBI, wenni xam iṭṭfen řɣiǧet n uɛeddis nnem?”  
\v 3 Tenna: “Aqa da tayya inu Bilha. Adef xas, ḥima ad dd-taruw x ifadden inu maḥend uřa d necc ad ɣari tiři tarrawt zzayes.”  
\v 4 Tewca as Bilha, tayya nnes, d tamɣart uca yudef xas Yaɛqub.  
\v 5 Teksi Bilha s ddeyset uca turuw-dd aḥenjir i Yaɛqub.  
\v 6 Tenna Raḥil: “Iwca ayi AREBBI tasɣart uca isřa ɛawed ɣari. Iwca ayi mmi.” X uya tegga as Dan. \f ◼ \fr 30:6 \ft \+fk isřa ɛawed ɣari\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘isřa ɛawed i tmijja inu’.\f*  
\v 7 Teksi Bilha, tayya n Raḥil, twařa nneɣni s ddeyset uca turuw-dd i Yaɛqub aḥenjir wiss tnayen.  
\v 8 Tenna Raḥil: “S imenɣan n AREBBI menɣeɣ ak-d učma uca ɣeřbeɣ.” Tegga as Naftali.   
\m
\v 9 \add Umi\add* teẓra Liya tessbedd tarwa, teksi Zilpa, tayya nnes, tewca i-tt i Yaɛqub d tamɣart,  
\v 10 uca Zilpa, tayya n Liya, turuw-dd aḥenjir i Yaɛqub.  
\v 11 Tenna Liya: “Mana řxir-a!” uca tegga as Jad.  
\v 12 Uca turuw-dd Zilpa, tayya n Liya, aḥenjir wiss tnayen i Yaɛqub.  
\v 13 Uca tenna Liya: “A sseɛd inu!”, minzi tibřiɣin ad ayi ḥesbent d sseɛd!” Uca tegga as Acir.  
\v 14 Deg wussan n tmeyra n irden iffeɣ Rubin uca yufa ‘titeffaḥin n tayri’ deg iyyar uca netta yiwy i-tent i Liya, yemmas. \add Xenni\add* tenna Raḥil i Liya: “Ttzawgeɣ cem ad ayi tewced zi ‘tteffaḥin n tayri’ n mmim.”  
\v 15 \add Maca Liya\add* tenna as: “Ma war iǧi drus ařami tiwyed aryaz inu, umi texsed ɛawed ad dd-tawyed ‘titeffaḥin n tayri’ n mmi?” Tenna Raḥil: “S uya ad iṭṭeṣ akidem ǧiřet-a x ‘tteffaḥin n tayri’ n mmim.” \f ◼ \fr 30:15 \ft \+fk tateffaḥt\ft  - niɣ ‘tadfuyyit’.\f*  
\v 16 \add Umi\add* dd-iɛqeb Yaɛqub zeg iyyar s tmeddit, teffeɣ-dd Liya ɣares tenna as: “Ad xafi tadfed, minzi nican criɣ cek s ‘tteffaḥin n tayri’ n mmi.” Uca \add ammu i\add* iṭṭeṣ akides ǧiret nni.  
\v 17 Isřa AREBBI i Liya uca teksi s ddeyset uca turuw-dd aḥenjir wiss xemsa i Yaɛqub.  
\v 18 Tenna Liya: “AREBBI iwca ayi řmunet inu x umi wciɣ tayya inu i weryaz inu!” Uca tegga as Issakar.  
\v 19 Teksi Liya ɛawed s ddeyset uca turuw-dd aḥenjir wiss setta i Yaɛqub.  
\v 20 Uca tenna Liya: “AREBBI iwca ayi ict n lbaraka tecna. Řexxu ad kidi izdeɣ weryaz inu, minzi urweɣ as-dd setta n iḥenjiren.” Uca tegga as Zabulun.  
\v 21 Awarni as turuw-dd taḥenjirt. Tegga as Dina.   
\m
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* idar AREBBI Raḥil uca isřa as AREBBI uca yarzem řemřawřet nnes.  
\v 23 Teksi s ddeyset uca turuw-dd aḥenjir, tenna: “Ikkes AREBBI řḥegra inu!”  
\v 24 Uca tegga as Yusuf, tenna: “Ad ayi yarni SIDI aḥenjir nneɣni.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řɛaḥd jar Yaɛqub d Laban  
\m
\v 25 Řami dd-turuw Raḥil Yusuf, inna Yaɛqub i Laban: “Sekk ayi uca ad raḥeɣ ɣar dcar inu d temmurt inu.  
\v 26 Ewc ayi timɣarin inu d iḥenjiren inu min zi ɣarek xedmeɣ. \add Xenni\add* ad ffɣeɣ. Aqa cek tessned řxedmet i zi tuɣa d ac ttsexxareɣ.”  
\v 27 Inna as Laban: “Mři ufiɣ řexxu arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec. Aqa ẓriɣ s ijj n řeɛjeb belli SIDI ibarek ayi di ṭṭweɛ nnec.”  
\v 28 \add Yarni\add* inna: “Ini ayi \add zeɛma\add* man řmunet \add i texsed\add*, uca ad ac tt wceɣ.”  
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* inna as: “Cek tessned mammec d ac xedmeɣ d mammec uyureɣ ak-d řebhayem nnec zeg wami kic ǧiɣ.  
\v 30 Minzi drust i tuɣa ɣarek \add řexdenni\add* qbeř i dd-usiɣ, aqa idweř deg waṭṭas, uca ibarek i cek SIDI deg iṣuraf inu. \add Xenni\add* řexxu, meřmi zemmareɣ ad xedmeɣ i taddart \add inu\add*?”  
\v 31 Inna as: “Min d ac i ɣa wceɣ?” Yarra-dd Yaɛqub: “War d ayi ttic walu, maca samḥ ayi aya \add waha\add*, \add xenni\add* ad dd-dewřeɣ ad arewseɣ uǧi nnec ɛawed uca ad ten ḥḍiɣ.  
\v 32 Ass-a ad ɛduɣ x marra \add taḥimart n\add* wuǧi nnec. Egg cek x uɣezdis zzayes marra uǧi ibeqqḍen d iqarqacen, marra uǧi abarcan jar iḥuřiyyen d min iǧan d aqarqac niɣ s ibeqqiḍen jar iɣayḍen. Man aya ad yiři d řmunet inu.  
\v 33 Xmi dd ɣa tased deg ijj n wass n yimař maḥens ad tẓared řmunet inu, ad tban tsegda inu zzat i wudem nnec \add ammu nican\add*: min war iǧin ibeqqeḍ niɣ min war iǧin iqqarqec jar iɣayḍen d min war iǧin d abarcan jar iḥuřiyyen, aqa \add ad ittwaḥseb\add* ittwacar jar min iǧan inu.”  
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* inna Laban: “Xzar, aqa ad yiři am mammec \add i d ayi\add* tennid!”   
\m
\v 35 Deg wass nni ifarq iwetman n iɣayḍen icarḍen d iqarqacen uřa d marra tiɣayḍtin ibeqqḍen d iqarqacen, d marra inni di teǧa temřeř, uřa d marra min iǧan d abarcan jar iḥuřiyyen, uca issars i-ten deg ufus n iḥenjiren nnes.  
\v 36 \add Xenni\add* igga třata n wussan n webrid jar ixef nnes d Yaɛqub. Uca yarwes Yaɛqub uǧi iqqimen n Laban.   
\m
\v 37 \add Xenni\add* iksi Yaɛqub tiseḍwin n ṣṣefṣaf u zi tcejjart n ǧuz u zi tcejjart n dulb. Netta iqeccar i-tent d iceṭṭiḍen d icemřařen umi iɛarra x ucemřař n tseḍwin.  
\v 38 Issars tiseḍwin-a iqeccaren qibač i wuǧi di taryiwin d řeqwareb mani dd-usin wuǧi maḥend ad swent uca dewřent ttweḥḥament xmi dd-tasent ad wardent.  
\v 39 \add Xmi\add* i ɣa iweḥḥem wuǧi ɣar tseḍwin, urwent-i-dd tɣarṭin min icarḍen d min ibeqqḍen d min iqarqacen.  
\v 40 \add Xenni\add* tuɣa ibeṭṭa Yaɛqub iḥuřiyyen uca yarra uǧi s uzeǧif nsen ɣar min icarḍen d min iǧan d abarcan jar wuǧi n Laban. Uca igga tiḥimriwin nnes ɣar uɣezdis, war tent iggi ak-d wuǧi n Laban.  
\v 41 Kuř amuř xmi ttweḥḥament tinni ijehden zeg wuǧi, ittegg Yaɛqub tiseḍwin qibač i wuǧi di taryiwin, ḥima ad weḥḥment ɣar tseḍwin. \f ◼ \fr 30:41 \ft \+fk qibač i wuǧi\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘qibač i tiṭṭawin n wuǧi’.\f*  
\v 42 \add Maca\add* war tent issars ca ak-d tenni iḍeɛfen jar wuǧi. Ammu tuɣa tinni iḍeɛfen i Laban u tinni ijehden i Yaɛqub.  
\v 43 Uca imɣar \add wagřa\add* n weryaz-a břa qeṭṭu. Tuɣa ɣares aṭṭas n wuǧi d tiyya d isemɣan d iřeɣman d yeɣyař.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 31
\s1 Tarewřa n Yaɛqub zi Laban  
\m
\v 1 Uca isřa \add Yaɛqub\add* awařen n iḥenjiren n Laban, nnan: “Yaɛqub iksi marra min tuɣa n babatneɣ u s min tuɣa n babatneɣ aqa ikseb marra aɛuǧi-ya.” \f ◼ \fr 31:1 \ft \+fk aɛuǧi\ft  - niɣ ‘řɛezz’.\f*  
\v 2 Ixzar Yaɛqub ɣar uɣembub n Laban. Xzar, war kides iǧi am iḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ.  
\v 3 Inna SIDI i Yaɛqub: “Dweř ɣar temmurt n řejdud nnec u ɣar řaǧ nnec. Aqa Necc ad iřiɣ akidek.”  
\v 4 Isekk Yaɛqub uca iřaɣa-dd x Raḥil d Liya ɣar yeyyar, ɣar wuǧi nnes.  
\v 5 Inna asent: “Ttwařiɣ belli aɣembub n babatkent war kidi iǧi am iḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ. \add Maca\add* AREBBI n řejdud inu aqa-t akidi.  
\v 6 Kennint tessnent belli aqa xedmeɣ i babatkent s marra min ɣari d jjehd.  
\v 7 \add Maca\add* babatkent iɣecc ayi, ibeddeř řmunet inu ɛecra n twařawin, \add maca\add* AREBBI war d as isemmeḥ ḥima ad ayi igg řɣar.  
\v 8 Mařa netta inna: ‘Ibeqqiḍen ad iřin d řmunet nnec!’, řexdenni marra uǧi urwent-i-dd \add uǧi\add* s ibeqqiḍen, mařa inna: ‘Inni s icariḍen ad iřin d řmunet nnec!’, řexdenni marra uǧi urwent-i-dd \add uǧi\add* s icariḍen.  
\v 9 \add Ammu\add* ikkes AREBBI řebhayem n babatkent uca iwca ayi \add tent\add* i necc.  
\v 10 Imsar ɣar řweqt umi weḥḥment uǧi, ssgeɛɛdeɣ tamuɣři inu uca ẓriɣ di tarjit, aqa da iɣayḍen nni ineggzen x wuǧi, tuɣa aten s icariḍen d ibeqqiḍen d iqarqacen.  
\v 11 Inna ayi lmalak n AREBBI di tarjit ‘Yaɛqub!’ Necc nniɣ ‘Aqa ayi da!’  
\v 12 Inna: ‘Nḍar tiṭṭawin nnec, xzar, marra iɣayḍen, inni ineggzen x wuǧi, aqa aten s icariḍen d ibeqqiḍen d iqarqacen, minzi Necc ẓriɣ marra min d ac ittegg Laban.  
\v 13 Necc d Arebbi n Bayt-Il, mani tdehned aẓru n řidaret u mani d ayi tewcid awař. Kkar řexxu, ffeɣ zi temmurt-a, ɛqeb ɣar temmurt mani txeřqed.’” \x ◘ \xo 31:13 \xt Amz. 28:13, 14, 15. \x*  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* arrint-i-dd Raḥil d Liya, nnant as: “Ma din ɛad ca n tesɣart niɣ ict n řwart i neccin di taddart n babatneɣ?  
\v 15 Ma war nettwiḥsib am tbarraniyyin? Aqa netta izzenz aneɣ u netta aqa iqeṭṭa marra nnuqart nneɣ.  
\v 16 Minzi marra agřa nni ikkes AREBBI i babatneɣ, nneɣ i iǧa u n iḥenjiren nneɣ. Řexxu \add ɛad\add*, egg marra min d ac inna AREBBI.”   
\m
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Yaɛqub uca issgeɛɛed iḥenjiren nnes d temɣarin nnes x iřeɣman.  
\v 18 Igga deg webrid marra řebhayem nnes d marra agřa nnes nni dd-ikseb, aqa řebhayem nni iṭṭef, inni dd-ikseb di Fadan-Aram, ḥima ad dd-iɛqeb ɣar Isḥaq, babas, di temmurt n Kenɛan.  
\v 19 Umi iruḥ Laban ɣar tiřsa n wuǧi nnes, tucar Raḥil řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam n babas.  
\v 20 Yaɛqub ixdeɛ Laban, Aramiyu, řami war d as iɛřim aqa ad yarweř.  
\v 21 Yarweř s marra min ɣares. Ikkar, iẓwa iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* uca yarra azeǧif nnes ɣar idurar n Jilɛad. \f ◼ \fr 31:21 \ft \+fk Jilɛad\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘tawrirt n cchadet’.\f*   
\m
\v 22 Deg wass wiss třata xebbaren Laban, aqa yarweř Yaɛqub.  
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* yiwi aytmas akides, iruḥ awarni as ticři n sebɛa n wussan, ixecc xas deg idurar n Jilɛad.  
\v 24 Uca yusa-dd AREBBI ɣar Laban, Aramiyu, di tarjit di ǧiret, inna as: “Ɣarek ad tessiwřed s řxar niɣ s řɣar ak-d Yaɛqub.”  
\v 25 Ireḥḥeg xenni Laban x Yaɛqub. Yaɛqub tuɣa iwta aqiḍun nnes deg idurar. Laban ɛawed iwta iqiḍan nnes ak-d aytmas deg idurar n Jilɛad.  
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* inna Laban i Yaɛqub: “Min teggid, teẓwid ayi uř uca tiwyid-dd yessi am tmeḥbas n garra?  
\v 27 Mayemmi tarewřed s tnuffra u tucared ayi u \add mayemmi\add* war d ayi txebbared, ḥima ad cek ssqebbḍeɣ s řefraḥet, s řeɣnuj, s ubendir u s řgambri?  
\v 28 War d ayi tejjid ad ssudmeɣ iḥenjiren inu d tḥenjirin inu. Řexxu d tubbuheřya i teggid.  
\v 29 Ɣari tizemmar deg ifassen inu, ḥima ad cek ḍarreɣ, \add maca\add* AREBBI n babatwem issiweř akidi ǧiret-a, inna: ‘Ɣarek ad tessiwřed s řxar niɣ s řɣar ak-d Yaɛqub.’  
\v 30 Uca řexxu tuyured, umi zeɛma tweḥḥced taddart n babac. \add Maca\add* maɣar i d ayi tucared irebbiten inu?”  
\v 31 Yarra-dd Yaɛqub, inna i Laban: “Minzi tuɣa ggʷedeɣ, nniɣ \add ak-d yixef inu\add* ad taɣ ad ayi tekksed yessic s uɣiř!  
\v 32 Ɣar wenni i ɣa tafed l’aṣnam nnec, ejj i-t war iddar \add ɛad\add*! Qibač i wawmaten nneɣ ad tmeyyzed min iǧan nnec jar min iǧan ɣari uca awyi t akidek.” \add Maɣar\add* Yaɛqub war issin belli Raḥil i ten yucaren.   
\m
\v 33 Uca yudef Laban ɣar uqiḍun n Yaɛqub, ɣar uqiḍun n Liya, ɣar uqiḍun n tnayen n tiyya uca war yufi walu. \add Řami\add* dd-iffeɣ zeg uqiḍun n Liya, yudef ɣar uqiḍun n Raḥil.  
\v 34 \add Maca\add* teksi Raḥil řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam, tegga i-tent deg iɣaynen n weřɣem uca teqqim xasen. Yarzu Laban deg uqiḍun am ikmeř, maca war yufi walu.  
\v 35 Tenna i babas: “War ittiři aya d řɣar di tiṭṭawin n sidi inu, minzi war zemmareɣ ad kkareɣ qibač nnec, maɣar aqa ayi s tnamit n temɣarin.” Uca yarzu, maca war yufi řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam.  
\v 36 \add Xenni\add* ixeyyeq Yaɛqub uca imcubbec ak-d Laban. Yaɛqub iṭṭef deg wawař, inna i Laban: “Mani iǧa uxeṭṭu inu? Man wen iǧan d ddenb inu, umi d ayi dd-teḍfared s zzɛaf?  
\v 37 Cek tbeqced marra řqecc inu. Min tufid zi marra řeḥwayej n taddart nnec? Egg i-t da zzat n yaytma d aytmac uca ejj i-ten ad ḥekmen jar aneɣ s tnayen.  
\v 38 Ɛicrin n iseggʷusa i kik kkiɣ. Tixeswin nnec d tɣayḍin nnec ɛemmarṣ ssutment niɣ ɛemmarṣ cciɣ icarriyen n wuǧi nnec.  
\v 39 War d ac iwyeɣ min ittwamezzqen, \add maca\add* xeṭṣeɣ t simant inu. Min ittwacaren zzayi deg wass niɣ di ǧiret, aqa zeg ifassen inu tᵉttared t.  
\v 40 S uziř ittett ayi řeḥmu yuẓɣen \add tiřmect\add* u s ǧiret ttejmideɣ \add zi sqiɛ\add*, \add ařami\add* yarweř iḍeṣ zi ɣari.  
\v 41 Ammu i d ayi tuɣa di taddart nnec ɛicrin n iseggʷusa. Xedmeɣ ɣarek arbeɛṭac n iseggʷusa x tnayen n yessic d setta n iseggʷusa x wuǧi uca tbeddřed řmunet inu ɛecra n twařawin.  
\v 42 Mařa AREBBI n baba, AREBBI n Ibrahim d tiggʷudi n Isḥaq, iři war kidi iǧi, d ṣṣeḥ iři ad ayi tessqaded řexxu s ifassen xwan! Iẓra AREBBI tamara d tumar n ifassen inu uca ideqmar i cek ǧiřet n iḍennaḍ.”   
\m
\v 43 Yarra-dd Laban uca inna i Yaɛqub: “Tiḥenjirin-a d yessi u iḥenjiren-a d iḥenjiren inu, u uǧi-ya d uǧi inu, u marra min tᵉttwařid aqa inu. Min zemmareɣ xenni ad ggeɣ řexxu s yessi niɣ s iḥenjiren nsent nni urwent?  
\v 44 Ɣawer ɛad řexxu, ad negg ijj n řɛahd, necc d cek, ad yiři Netta d cchadet jar ayi d cek!”  
\v 45 Uca iksi Yaɛqub aẓru, issgeɛɛed i-t am weẓru n řidaret.  
\v 46 Uca inna Yaɛqub i yaytmas: “Smunem iẓra!” Ksin iẓra uca ggin taɛurrict uca ccin din x tɛurrict nni.  
\v 47 Uca igga Laban \add i uɛurric n iẓra nni\add* ‘Jigar-Sahaduta’, maca Yaɛqub igga as ‘Jilɛad’.  
\v 48 \add Xenni\add* inna Laban: “Taɛurrict-a ad tiři d cchadet ass-a jar ayi d cek!” X uya tegga as Jilɛad  
\v 49 d Miṣfa, minzi netta inna: “Iři SIDI ad iḥḍa jar ayi d cek, xmi ɣa niři am nᵉnuffar ijjen zeg wenneɣni. \f ◼ \fr 31:49 \ft \+fk Miṣfa\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘lburj i uḥettu’.\f*  
\v 50 Mařa tesseḥqared yessi niɣ ad tmeřced timɣarin nneɣni x yessi, \add am\add* war din iǧi ḥed akidneɣ \add ḥima ad yiři d acehhad\add*, aqa AREBBI ad yiři d acehhad jar ayi d cek!”  
\v 51 Inna ɛawed Laban i Yaɛqub: “Xzar, taɛurrict-a \add n yeẓra\add*, xzar, aẓru n řidaret nni ssbeddeɣ jar ayi d cek.  
\v 52 Taɛurrict-a \add n yeẓra\add* d weẓru-ya n řidaret ad cehden belli necc war ɣarek dd-ẓekkʷiɣ ca x tɛurrict-a uca uřa d cek war ɣari dd-tẓekkʷwid ca i řɣar x tɛurrict-a uřa x weẓru-ya n řidaret!  
\v 53 AREBBI n Ibrahim d AREBBI n Naḥur, aqa AREBBI n babatsen, ejj i-t ad iḥkem jar aneɣ!” \add Maca\add* Yaɛqub ijjuǧ s ‘Tiggʷudi n Isḥaq babas’.  
\v 54 \add Xenni\add* iɣarṣ Yaɛqub i yict n tɣarṣt deg idurar uca iřaɣa i yaytmas ad ccen aɣrum. Uca ccin aɣrum, senssen ǧiret nni deg idurar.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 32
\s1 Asřaḥ jar Yaɛqub d Ɛisu  
\m
\v 1 Ikkar Laban ɣar tuffut n ṣṣbeḥ, issudem iḥenjiren nnes d yessis, ibark i-ten. \add Xenni\add* iruḥ Laban, iɛqeb ɣar wemcan nnes.  
\v 2 Uca iṭṭef Yaɛqub ɛawed abrid nnes uca usint-i-dd lmalakat n AREBBI, řqant t-i-dd. \x ◘ \xo 32:2 \xt Amz. 48:16. \x*  
\v 3 Inna Yaɛqub umi ten iẓra: “Řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n AREBBI d wa!”, uca iřaɣa isem n wemcan nni Maḥanayim.  
\v 4 Issekk Yaɛqub ireqqasen ɣar zzat, ɣar Ɛisu umas ɣar temmurt n Saɛir, aqa-tt d jjihet n Idum.  
\v 5 Uca iweṣṣa i-ten, inna asen: “Ammu i ɣa tinim i sidi inu Ɛisu: ‘Ammu i iqqar umsexxar nnec Yaɛqub: Tuɣa zeddɣeɣ ak-d Laban am ubarrani uca qqimeɣ din ař i řexxu.  
\v 6 Ɣari ifunasen d yeɣyař d wuǧi d isemɣan d tiyya uca ssekkeɣ \add ireqqasen\add*, maḥend ad \add t\add* iniɣ i sidi inu, maḥend ad afeɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec.’”   
\m
\v 7 Ireqqasen dewřen-dd ɣar Yaɛqub, nnan: “Nruḥ ɣar umac Ɛisu, u netta ɛawed yusa-dd ad cek iřqa u aqa din arebɛa-mya n yeryazen akides.”  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* Yaɛqub tudef i-t tiggʷudi temɣar uca issqenḍ i-t řḥař. Netta ibḍa iwdan, inni akides d wuǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin d iřeɣman x tnayen n řemrageḥ n řɛeskar.  
\v 9 Inna: “Mařa yusa-dd Ɛisu ɣar ijj n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, ad xas iɣřeb, \add xenni\add* ad yarweř řmargeḥ n řɛeskar i iqqimen.”  
\v 10 Uca inna Yaɛqub: “\add A\add* AREBBI n baba Ibrahim d AREBBI n baba Isḥaq, \add a\add* SIDI, \add Cek\add* wenni d ayi innan: ‘Dweř ɣar temmurt nnec d raǧ nnec uca Necc ad ac ggeɣ min icnan!’ \x ◘ \xo 32:10 \xt Amz. 31:13. \x*  
\v 11 Aqa ayi qell x marra timegga n tmexsiwt icewwaren d marra řaman i tessecned i umsexxar nnec, minzi ẓwiɣ L’Urdun s teɣɣarct inu \add řami dd-ffɣeɣ\add* uca řexxu dewřeɣ-dd d tnayen n řemrageḥ n řɛeskar.  
\v 12 Fekk ayi řexxu zeg ufus n Ɛisu uma, minzi tteggʷedeɣ balak ad dd-yas uca ad ineɣ uřa d tiyemmatin ak-d iḥenjiren!  
\v 13 Uca Cek tennid: ‘Necc ad kik ggeɣ mliḥ, ad ggeɣ zzariɛet nnec am yijdi n řebḥar i war izemmar ad ittwaḥseb zi ssibbet n ubarru nnes!’” \x ◘ \xo 32:13 \xt Amz. 28:13. \x*   
\m
\v 14 Issens din ǧiřet nni uca iksi zi min dd-yusin deg ifassen nnes d agřa, maḥend ad t yewc d arriɣalu i umas Ɛisu:  
\v 15 mitayen n tɣayḍin d ɛicrin n imuyan d mitayen n txeswin d ɛicrin n icarriyyen  
\v 16 d třatin n třeɣmin issuṭṭuḍen ak-d tarwa nsent, arebɛin n tfunasin timeẓyanin, ɛecra n ifunasen imeẓyanen d ɛicrin n teɣyař d ɛecra n yeɣyař imeẓyanin.  
\v 17 Isseɛdu ten ɣar ifassen n imsexxaren nnes, kuř taḥimart weḥḥdes, uca inna i imsexxaren nnes: “Ɛdum kenniw \add řexxu\add* zzat inu, ggem ttasiɛ jar tḥimart d tḥimart.”  
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* yumur umezwar, inna as: “Mařa yusa-dd Ɛisu i umsagar akidek uca isseqsa ac, inna: ‘Wi cek yiřan d mani ɣa traḥed?’ u ‘Umi tina i iǧan zzatek?’,  
\v 19 \add řexdenni\add* ad tinid: ‘D arriɣalu i yeǧa n umsexxar nnec Yaɛqub, wenni dd-issekk i sidi inu Ɛisu. Xzar, netta ɛawed \add yusa-dd\add* awarni \add aneɣ\add*!’”  
\v 20 Yumur ɛawed wenni wiss tnayen d wiss třata inni igguren awarni i tḥimriwin, inna: “Siwřem awařen-a d ijjen ak-d Ɛisu, xmi t ɣa teřqam.  
\v 21 Kenniw ɛawed ad tinim: ‘Xzar, amsexxar nnec Yaɛqub yusa-dd awarni aneɣ!’” Minzi inna: “Ad t ssareyyḥeɣ s arriɣalu-ya i dd-yusin zzat inu. Xenni awarni man aya ad ẓareɣ aɣembub nnes, balak ad iqbeř aɣembub inu \add zzates\add*.”  
\v 22 \add Ammu\add* i issizzar arriɣalu zzates ɣar ujemmaḍ am issens netta ǧiret nni di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.   
\m
\v 23 Ikkar ǧiřet nni uca iksi tnayen n temɣarin nnes d tnayen n tiyya nnes d ḥiṭac n iḥenjiren nnes, iẓwa amcan n uẓekkwu n \add yeɣzar n\add* Yabbuq.  
\v 24 Yiwyi i-ten uca isseẓwa ten i teɣzurt u \add marra\add* min ɣares isseɛdu t ɣar ujemmaḍ.   
\m
\v 25 \add Maca\add* iqqim Yaɛqub weḥḥdes u netta immuɣzeř ak-d ijj n Weryaz ařmi d tuffut n řefjar.  
\v 26 \add Umi\add* iẓra Wanita aqa war xas iqedd ca, iḥada t ɣar wemcan n temqiqqect n tmeṣṣaḍt nnes, maḥend ad dd-tenxuxer tamqiqqect n tmeṣṣaḍt n Yaɛqub umi kides tuɣa ittmuɣzuř.  
\v 27 Inna: “Ejj ayi ad raḥeɣ, aqa iṣbeḥ řḥař.” Maca netta inna: “War Cek ttejjiɣ, mɣir mařa tbarked ayi.” \x ◘ \xo 32:27 \xt Ḥuc. 12:4. \x*  
\v 28 Uca Netta inna as: “Mammec d ac qqaren?” Yarra-dd xas: “Yaɛqub.”  
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* inna as: “War d ac qqaren ɛad Yaɛqub, maca Israil, minzi temmenɣed ak-d AREBBI d iwdan, uca cek tɣeřbed.” \f ◼ \fr 32:29 \ft \+fk Israil\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘Arebbi ittmenɣa’ niɣ ‘netta ittmenɣa ak-d Arebbi’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 32:29 \xt Amz. 35:10. \x*  
\v 30 Isseqsa Yaɛqub \add xenni\add*, inna: “Ini ayi řexxu Isem nnec!” Yarra-dd xas: “Maɣar tesseqsid x Yisem inu?” Uca ibark i-t din.  
\v 31 Uca isemma Yaɛqub amcan nni Fanuwil, inna: “Minzi ẓriɣ AREBBI aɣembub deg uɣembub uca injem řeɛmar inu.”  
\v 32 Tenqar-dd xas tfuct umi tuɣa iɛdu x Fanuwil, uca yuyur ittzeḥḥef zi tmeṣṣaḍt nnes.  
\v 33 X uya war ttᵉtten ayt n Israil ař ass-a zeg weẓwar igdaren i ittekken x temqiqqect n tmeṣṣaḍt, minzi iḥada tameṣṣaḍt n Yaɛqub ɣar mani iǧa weẓwar igdaren.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 33
\m
\v 1 Issgeɛɛed Yaɛqub tamuɣři nnes uca iẓra Ɛisu d arebɛa-mya n yeryazen akides xeccen-dd. Ifarq \add Yaɛqub\add* iḥenjiren x Liya d Raḥil d tnayen n tiyya.  
\v 2 Igga tiyya d tarwa nsent ɣar zzat, awarni asent Liya d tarwa nnes u Raḥil d Yusuf d ineggura.  
\v 3 Umi iɛdu zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen, ibendeq ɣar temmurt sebɛa n twařawin ařami dd-yiweḍ ɣar umas. \f ◼ \fr 33:3 \ft \+fk zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘zzat i iɣembab nsen’.\f*  
\v 4 Ɛisu yuzzeř-dd ḥima ad t iřqa, idarreɛ as, ingez as x yiri nnes, issudem i-t uca run s tnayen.  
\v 5 \add Xas uca\add* issgeɛɛed tiṭṭawin nnes, iẓra timɣarin d iḥenjiren nni uca inna: “Min ɛnan ina inni akidek?” Netta yarra-dd xas: “D tarwa nni iwca AREBBI zeg arḍa \add nnes\add* i umsexxar nnec.”  
\v 6 Uca reḥḥgent-i-dd tiyya, nitenti d tarwa nsent, uca bendqent.  
\v 7 Treḥḥeg-dd ɛawed Liya d iḥenjiren nnes uca bendqen. Řexdenni iqarreb-dd Yusuf d Raḥil uca bendqen.  
\v 8 Inna as: “Min texsed ak-d ubarru-ya n řɛeskar nni řqiɣ?” Netta inna: “\add Necc ssekkeɣ t,\add* maḥend ad afeɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin n sidi inu!”  
\v 9 Inna Ɛisu: “Aqa ɣari aṭṭas, uma inu! Ad yiři i cek min iǧan nnec!”  
\v 10 \add Xas uca\add* inna Yaɛqub: “Lla, ttzawageɣ cek! Mařa ufiɣ řexxu arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, ksi arriɣalu inu zeg ifassen inu, maɣar ẓriɣ udem nnec axmi ẓriɣ udem n AREBBI uca tqebřed xafi s řemřaḥet.  
\v 11 Ttzawgeɣ cek, ksi lbaraka inu i d ac dd-iwyeɣ, minzi AREBBI imṣurruf akidi s arḍa uca necc ɣari kuřci.” Ikellef i-t uca iksi t.   
\m
\v 12 Netta inna: “Ejj aneɣ ad nefsi iqiḍan nneɣ, ad nraḥ. Necc ad raḥeɣ zzatec.”  
\v 13 \add Maca\add* netta inna as: “Sidi inu issen, aqa iḥenjiren-a arehfen u aqa ɣari uǧi d tfunasin urwent ssuṭṭuḍent. Mařa bnadem izeyyar xasent aṭṭas, \add waxxa mɣir i\add* yijj n wass, ad immet wuǧi marra.  
\v 14 Ad iɛdu řexxu sidi inu zzat i uɣembub n umsexxar nnes u necc ad dd-aseɣ cwayt cwayt ak-d iṣuraf n řeksibet i iǧan zzati uřa ak-d iṣuraf n iḥenjiren, ař dd ɣa awḍeɣ ɣar sidi inu di Saɛir.”  
\v 15 Inna Ɛisu: “Ad jjeɣ řexxu akidek \add ca n\add* iwdan inni iǧan akidi.” \add Maca\add* netta inna: “Umi ddegga? Ejj ayi ad afeɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin n sidi inu!”  
\v 16 Iɛqeb-dd Ɛisu deg wass nni x webrid ɣar Saɛir.   
\m
\v 17 Uca ifsi Yaɛqub iqiḍan nnes, \add yuyur\add* ɣar Sukkut, ibna din taddart i yixef nnes uca igga iɛuccuten n tseṭṭa i řebhayem nnes. X uya iřaɣa isem n wemcan nni Sukkut, \add ixs ad yini ‘Iɛuccuten’\add*. \f ◼ \fr 33:17 \ft \+fk Sukkut\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘Iɛuccuten’.\f*  
\v 18 Umi dd-iɛqeb Yaɛqub zi Fadan-Aram, yusa-dd ɣar Calim, ict n tendint n Cakim, tenni iǧan di temmurt n Kenɛan, uca iwta iqiḍan nnes zzat i tendint. \x ◘ \xo 33:18 \xt Yac. 24:32; Řex. 7:16. \x*  
\v 19 Isɣa ṭṭarf n yeyyar mani iwta iqiḍan nnes, zeg ifassen n iḥenjiren n Ḥamur, babas n Cakim, s mya n iziynat n nnuqart iweznen. \f ◼ \fr 33:19 \ft \+fk Ḥamur\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘aɣyuř’.\f*  
\v 20 Issgeɛɛed din ijj n uɛalṭar \add min xef temmars tɣarṣt\add* uca iřaɣa as: ‘Arebbi \add d\add* AREBBI n Israil!’ \f ◼ \fr 33:20 \ft \+fk Arebbi (d) AREBBI n Israil!\ft  - niɣ ‘AREBBI n Israil d Arebbi!’\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 34
\s1 Asnuqqeb n Dina zi Cakim, mmis n Ḥamur  
\m
\v 1 Dina, yeǧis n Liya, tenni dd-turuw i Yaɛqub, teffeɣ, ḥima ad temmeřqa ak-d yessis n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 34:1 \xt Amz. 30:21. \x*  
\v 2 Cakim, mmis n Ḥamur Aḥiwi, řḥakem n temmurt nni, iẓra i-tt, iksi tt uca iṭṭeṣ akides, issexsar i-tt.  
\v 3 Iṭṭarbeṭ di Dina, yeǧis n Yaɛqub, u netta ixs tabřiɣt uca issiweř ɣar wuř n tebřiɣt.  
\v 4 Issiweř Cakim ɣar Ḥamur babas, inna as: “Awyi ayi-dd tabřiɣt-a d tamɣart.”   
\m
\v 5 Řami isřa Yaɛqub belli Cakim iḍeyyeɛ \add ccaraf n\add* yeǧis Dina, tuɣa iḥenjiren nnes ak-d řebhayem deg iyyar. Issusem Yaɛqub ařami dd-ɛeqben nitni.  
\v 6 Iruḥ Ḥamur, babas n Cakim ɣar Yaɛqub, ḥima ad kis issiweř.  
\v 7 Tarwa n Yaɛqub dewřen-dd zeg iyyar uca areggben x řexbar. Xeyyqen x man aya \add deg wuř\add* u ffugmen aṭṭas, minzi igga řefḍiḥet-a di Israil umi iṭṭeṣ ak-d yeǧis n Yaɛqub. man aya war icuwwar ad t yegg.  
\v 8 Issiweř Ḥamur akidsen, inna: “Řeɛmar n mmi Cakim iqqen ɣar yeǧitwem, ttzawageɣ, ad as tt tewcem d tamɣart,  
\v 9 uca ad nemḍeggwař. Ad aneɣ tewcem yeǧitwem, kenniw ad teksim yessitneɣ i yixef nwem.  
\v 10 Zedɣem akidneɣ, minzi tammurt aqa-tt zzatwem. Zedɣem u uyurem dayes uca ṭṭfem dayes agřa i kenniw.”  
\v 11 Uca inna Cakim \add ɛawed\add* i babas d aytmas: “Ejj ayi ad afeɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nwem uca ad wceɣ min d ayi ɣa tinim.  
\v 12 \add Waxxa\add* ad tessḍeqřem xafi \add řeḥmeř\add* aṭṭas \add n\add* ṣṣadaq d ssunan, aqa necc ad wceɣ mecḥař ma d ayi ɣa tinim. Wcem ayi mɣir tabřiɣt d tamɣart.”  
\v 13 Arrin-dd iḥenjiren n Yaɛqub x Cakim d Ḥamur, babas, s ict n teḥraymect, minzi aqa issexsar Dina, učmatsen.  
\v 14 Nitni ssiwřen, nnan asen: “War nzemmar ad negg ammu, ad newc učmatneɣ i weryaz nni \add ɛad\add* s řeɛdařyet. Degga d řɛar xaneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 34:14 \xt Amz. 17:12, 13, 14. \x*  
\v 15 Mɣir s umtawi-ya waha ad kenniw nseɛɛef, mařa teggim am neccin, ad tᵉttwaxetnem marra iwetman nwem.  
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* ad awem newc yeǧitneɣ uca ad neksi yessitwem, ad kidwen nezdeɣ, ad niři d ijj n řgens.  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* mařa war d aneɣ tesřim di tmesřact n wextan, \add xenni\add* ad neksi yeǧitneɣ uca ad nuyur.”  
\v 18 Banen wawařen nsen mliḥ deg imezzuɣen n Ḥamur u deg imejjan n Cakim, mmis n Ḥamur. \f ◼ \fr 34:18 \ft \+fk imezzuɣen\ft  - niɣ ‘imejjan’.\f*  
\v 19 Aɛezri war d as icqi ad igg man aya, minzi netta ittexs aṭṭas yeǧis n Yaɛqub u netta tuɣa-t qaɛ mweqqar di marra taddart n babas.   
\m
\v 20 Uca usin-dd Ḥamur d mmis Cakim ɣar tewwart n tendint nnes, ssiwřen ak-d yeryazen n tendint, nnan:  
\v 21 “Iryazen-a d imhudnen akidneɣ. Ejj aneɣ ad ten nejj ad zedɣen di temmurt-a uca ad dayes uyuren. Xzar, tammurt tewseɛ i nitni ɣar marra iɣezdisen nnes. Neccin ad neksi yessitsen d timɣarin, ad asen newc yessitneɣ.  
\v 22 \add Maca\add* s umtawi-ya waha ad seɛɛfen yeryazen-a, ḥima ad kidneɣ zedɣen u ḥima ad dewřen d ijj n řgens \add akidneɣ\add*, mařa marra iryazen i iǧan jar aneɣ ad ttwaxetnen am mammec ttwaxetnen nitni.  
\v 23 Řebhayem nsen d agřa nsen d marra řmař nsen, ma war ttiřin nneɣ? Ejj aneɣ ad ten nseɛɛef, \add xenni\add* ad zedɣen akidneɣ.”  
\v 24 Marra inni dd-yusin ɣar tewwart n tendint nnes sřin i Ḥamur d mmis Cakim uca marra iryazen inni dd-yusin ɣar tewwart n tendint nnes, ttwaxetnen.  
\v 25 Umi tuɣa ɛad daysen řehriq deg wass wiss třata, temsar belli iḥenjiren n Yaɛqub, Cimɛun d Lawi, aytmas n Dina, aqa kuř ijj zzaysen iksi ssif nnes uca ruḥen ɣar tendint mani d asen ittɣiř aqa dayes řaman uca nɣin marra iryazen. \x ◘ \xo 34:25 \xt Amz. 49:6. \x*  
\v 26 Nɣin Ḥamur d mmis Cakim s řeqḍeɛ n ssif uca ksin Dina zi taddart n Cakim, ffɣen.  
\v 27 Tarwa n Yaɛqub usin-dd ɣar yinni ittwanɣen uca keccḍen tandint, minzi nitni ssexsaren učmatsen.  
\v 28 Ksin uǧi nsen d ifunasen d tfunasin nsen d yeɣyař nsen d marra min tuɣa di tendint u deg iyyar.  
\v 29 Ksin marra agřa nnes uca iwyen-dd marra iḥenjiren d temɣarin nsen d imeḥbas uca ucaren marra min tuɣa di tudrin.  
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* inna Yaɛqub i Cimɛun d Lawi: “Kenniw tessidfem ayi deg imxumbar ařami d ayi tessarzgem ɣar imezdaɣ n temmurt-a, ɣar ayt n Kenɛan d Ifiriziyyen. D necc ɣari ijj n wuru n yeryazen \add waha\add*. \add Mařa\add* ad munen x uzeřmaḍ inu, ad ayi qeẓẓren, ad iřiɣ areyyteɣ, necc d taddart inu.”  
\v 31 Nitni nnan: “Ma iɛeddeř xenni ad iḥseb učmatneɣ amecnaw ict n lfasda?”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 35
\s1 Aɛqab n Yaɛqub ɣar Bayt-Il  
\m
\v 1 Uca inna AREBBI i Yaɛqub: “Kkar, geɛɛed ɣar Bayt-Il uca qqim din. Egg din ijj n uɛalṭar \add min xef i ɣa tessarsed taɣarṣt\add* i Arebbi, wenni d ac dd-ibanen umi dd-tarewřed zeg uɣembub n umac Ɛisu.” \x ◘ \xo 35:1 \xt Amz. 27:43; 28:12, 13. \x*  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna Yaɛqub i řwacun \add n taddart\add* nnes u i marra inni tuɣa akides: “Kksem irebbiten iɣriben nni iǧan jar awem, sizedgem ixef nwem uca beddřem arruḍ nwem. \f ◼ \fr 35:2 \ft \+fk irebbiten iɣriben\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini ‘laṣnam’. Uřa di ayet 4.\f*  
\v 3 Ad nekkar, ad ngeɛɛed ɣar Bayt-Il. Necc ad ggeɣ din ijj n uɛalṭar i Arebbi nni xafi dd-yarrin deg wass n řeḥṣaret inu, d wenni tuɣa akidi deg webrid nni uyureɣ.”  
\v 4 Uca wcin i Yaɛqub marra irebbiten iɣriben nni tuɣa ɣarsen uřa d tixrazin deg imezzuɣen nsen uca iffar i-ten Yaɛqub sadu tcejjart n yigg i tuɣa zzat i Cakim. \f ◼ \fr 35:4 \ft \+fk nni tuɣa ɣarsen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘inni deg ifassen nsen’\f*  
\v 5 \add Řami\add* fesyen iqiḍan, \add uyuren\add* ssenni, tuɣa tiggʷudi n AREBBI x tneddam nni tuɣa di jjwayeh i d asen dd-innḍen, ařami nitni war ḍeffaren iḥenjiren n Yaɛqub.  
\v 6 Ammu i yiweḍ Yaɛqub ɣar Luz di temmurt n Kenɛan, aqa-tt d Bayt-Il, netta d marra řgens i tuɣa akides.  
\v 7 Ibna din ijj n uɛalṭar uca iřaɣa i wemcan nni Il-Bayt-Il, minzi dinni i d as dd-iḍhar AREBBI, umi dd-yarweř zeg uɣembub n umas. \x ◘ \xo 35:7 \xt Amz. 28:19. \x*   
\m
\v 8 Temmut Dibura, tamesseṭṭaḍt n Rifqa uca neḍřen tt swadday i Bayt-Il, sadu tabeǧuḍt uca iřaɣa isem nnes ‘Allun-Bakut’, \add aqa-tt d ‘tabeǧuḍt n imeṭṭawen’\add*.  
\v 9 Iḍhar as-dd ɛawed AREBBI i Yaɛqub umi dd-idweř zi Fadan-Aram uca ibark i-t. \x ◘ \xo 35:9 \xt Ḥuc. 12:5. \x*  
\v 10 Inna as AREBBI: “Isem nnec d Yaɛqub. Zi ssa d tsawent war tteggen ɛad isem nnec ‘Yaɛqub’, maca ‘Israil’, d wa i ɣa yiřin d isem nnec.” Uca isemma t Israil. \x ◘ \xo 35:10 \xt Amz. 32:27; 2 Ij. 17:34. \x*  
\v 11 Inna as AREBBI: “Necc d Arebbi, Amzemmar x kuřci! Egg řɣiǧet, mmarniy! Zzayek i ɣa iffeɣ ijj n řgens, wah, d ijj n wegraw n řegnus ad ffɣen zzayek u ijeǧiden ad ffɣen zi tejɛinna nnec. \x ◘ \xo 35:11 \xt Amz. 17:1, 6; 28:3; 48:3 \x*  
\v 12 Uca tammurt-a i wciɣ i Ibrahim d Isḥaq, i cek umi tt i ɣa wceɣ uca uřa i zzariɛet nnec awarni ac ad wceɣ tammurt.”  
\v 13 \add Xas uca\add* igeɛɛed AREBBI sennej zeg wemcan mani kides issiweř.  
\v 14 Yaɛqub issgeɛɛed ijj n weẓru n řidaret deg wemcan mani kis issiweř, ijj n weẓru n řidaret. Iseyyeb xas ict n tewhibt n useyyeb uca ifarreɣ zzect x uzeǧif nnes. \x ◘ \xo 35:14 \xt Amz. 28:18. \x*  
\v 15 Igga Yaɛqub isem n wemcan mani kides issiweř AREBBI ‘Bayt-Il!’   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Axřaq n Binyamin d řmewt n Raḥil  
\m
\v 16 Fesyen nitni iqiḍan nsen, \add ffɣen\add* zi Bayt-Il uca umi tuɣa tteggwijen mɣir cwayt x Ifrata, xenni turuw-dd Raḥil u teɛdu xas tarwa teqseḥ. \f ◼ \fr 35:16 \ft \+fk Ifrata\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘min itticen řɣiǧet’ niɣ ‘wenni itticcen řɣiǧet’.\f*  
\v 17 Imsar, umi teɣɣuḍed di tarwa nnes, tenna as řqabřa: “War tteggʷed, aqa wa ɛawed ad yiři d mmim!”  
\v 18 Řami teḍřeq i buḥbeř am temmut \add din\add*, aqa třaɣa as Bin-Uni, \add isem-a ixs ad yini ‘mmis n řeḥriq inu’\add*, \add maca\add* babas iřaɣa as Binyamin, \add ixs ad yini ‘mmis n zzhar inu’\add*. \f ◼ \fr 35:18 \ft \+fk Bin-Oni\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘mmi n řeḥriq inu’. \fk Binyamin\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘mmi n ufus yefusi’.\f*  
\v 19 \add Ammu\add* i temmut Raḥil uca neḍřent tt deg webrid ɣar Ifrata, ixs ad yini Bayt-Laḥm. \x ◘ \xo 35:19 \xt Amz. 48:7. \x*  
\v 20 Uca igga Yaɛqub ijj n weẓru n řidaret x wenḍeř nnes. D wa d aẓru n řidaret n Raḥil x wenḍeř n Raḥil ař ass-a.   
\b  
\m
\v 21 \add Xas uca\add* ifsi Israil iqiḍan uca iwta aqiḍun nnes x uɛeddu n Majdal-Ɛidr.  
\v 22 Umi izdeɣ Israil di temmurt nni, imsar belli Rubin iruḥ iṭṭeṣ ak-d Bilha, tayya n babas, uca yiweḍ ad \add t\add* ifhem Israil.  
\b  
\m \bd Aqa \+bdit řexxu\+bdit* iwḍen ayt n Yaɛqub tenɛac\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 35:22 \xt Amz. 49:4. \x*   
\m
\v 23 \bd Tarwa n Liya\bd* \add tuɣa aten\add*: Rubin, amenzu n Yaɛqub d Cimɛun d Lawi d Yahuda d Issakar d Zabulun. \x ◘ \xo 35:23 \xt Amz. 46:8; Uf. 1:2. \x*  
\v 24 \bd Tarwa n Raḥil\bd* \add tuɣa aten\add*: Yusuf d Binyamin.  
\v 25 \bd Tarwa n Bilha\bd*, tayya n Raḥil, \add tuɣa aten\add*: Dan d Naftali.  
\v 26 \bd Tarwa n Zilpa\bd*, tayya n Liya, \add tuɣa aten\add*: Jad d Acir. Ina \add tuɣa aten d\add* iḥenjiren n Yaɛqub inni d as dd-ittwaxeřqen di Fadan-Aram.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řmewt n Isḥaq  
\m
\v 27 Uca yusa-dd Yaɛqub ɣar babas Isḥaq di Mamri, di tendint n Arbaɛ, tenni iǧan d \add tandint n\add* Ḥabrun, mani tuɣa Ibrahim izeddeɣ am ubarrani, uca Isḥaq amenni \add awarni as\add*. \f ◼ \fr 35:27 \ft \+fk tandint n Arbaɛ\ft  - niɣ ‘Qaryat-Arbaɛ’.\f*  
\v 28 Iddar Isḥaq mya u-tmanyin n iseggʷusa. \f ◼ \fr 35:28 \ft \+fk Iddar Isḥaq ...\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Uca tuɣa wussan n Isḥaq ...’\f*  
\v 29 Iḍřeq Isḥaq i buḥbeř, immut uca immarni ɣar řgens nnes, iwsar, ijjiwen zi tudart, uca Ɛisu d Yaɛqub, iḥenjiren nnes, neḍřen t. \x ◘ \xo 35:29 \xt Amz. 25:8. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 36
\s1 Tarwa n Ɛisu  
\m
\v 1 \bd Ina d imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen \+bdit zi\+bdit* Ɛisu, wenni iǧan d Idum.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 36:1 \xt [1 Im. 1:28-54] — 1 Im. 1:35. \x*  
\v 2 Ɛisu iksi timɣarin nnes zeg yessis n Kenɛan: Ɛada, yeǧis n Ilun, Aḥitti, d Ahulibama, yeǧis n Ɛana, yeǧis n Ṣabɛun, Aḥiwi,  
\v 3 d Basmat, yeǧis n Ismaɛil, učmas n Nabayut.  
\v 4 Ɛada turuw-dd Ilifaz i Ɛisu uca Basmat turuw \add as-dd\add* Raɛuwil.  
\v 5 Ahulibama turuw-dd Yaɛus d Yaɛlam d Quraḥ. Ina \add tuɣa aten d\add* iḥenjiren n Ɛisu, inni d as dd-yurwen di temmurt n Kenɛan.   
\m
\v 6 Uca iksi Ɛisu timɣarin nnes d iḥenjiren nnes d yessis d marra aytbab n taddart nnes uřa d řebhayem nnes d marra řmař nnes d marra agřa nnes nni tuɣa dd-ikseb zi temmurt n Kenɛan uca iruḥ ɣar temmurt \add nneɣni\add* i iggʷejen x uɣembub n umas Yaɛqub,  
\v 7 minzi agřa nsen tuɣa imɣar ařami war zemmaren ad zedɣen jmiɛ, uca tammurt mani tuɣa zeddɣen am řbarrani, war tqedd i řebhayem nsen. \x ◘ \xo 36:7 \xt Amz. 13:6. \x*  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* izdeɣ Ɛisu deg idurar n Saɛir. Ɛisu, netta d Idum. \x ◘ \xo 36:8 \xt Yac. 24:4. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 \bd Ina d imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen \+bdit zi\+bdit* Ɛisu\bd*, babas n Idum, deg idurar n Saɛir.   
\m
\v 10 \bd Ina tuɣa aten d ismawen n iḥenjiren n Ɛisu\bd*: Ilifaz, mmis n Ɛada tenni d tamɣart n Ɛisu, Raɛuwil, mmis n Basmat, tenni d tamɣart n Ɛisu.   
\m
\v 11 Iḥenjiren n Ilifaz tuɣa aten d Tayman, Umar, Ṣafu, Jaɛtam d Qanaz. \f ◼ \fr 36:11 \ft \+fk Tayman\ft  - nᵉttaf isem wanita i twařa tamezwarut danita deg Wedlis Iqeddsen. Isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘afusi’ niɣ ‘ɣar ufus afusi’ niɣ ‘ljanub’ niɣ ‘ɣar ljanub’. Aqa wa d isem n mmis Ilifaz u awarni as idweř isem-a d isem n temmurt nnes di Idum.\f*   
\m
\v 12 Timnaɛ tedweř d tayya n Ilifaz, mmis n Ɛisu, u nettat turuw-dd Ɛamaliq i Ilifaz. Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Ɛada, tamɣart n Ɛisu.   
\m
\v 13 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Raɛuwil: Naḥat, Zaraḥ, Camma d Mizza. Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Basmat, tenni d tamɣart n Ɛisu.   
\m
\v 14 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Ahulibama, tenni d tamɣart n Ɛisu, yeǧis n Ɛana, tenni d yeǧis n Zibyun. Nettat turuw-dd Yaɛuc, Jaɛlam d Quraḥ i Ɛisu.   
\m
\v 15 \bd Ina tuɣa aten d imɣaren \+bdit n tqebbař\+bdit* n ayt n Ɛisu.\bd*  
\m Iḥenjiren n Ilifaz, amenzu n Ɛisu: amɣar Timan d umɣar Umar d umɣar Ṣafu d umɣar Qinaz,  
\v 16 d umɣar Quraḥ, d umɣar Gatam, d umɣar Ɛamaliq. Ina tuɣa aten d imɣaren n Ilifaz di temmurt n Idum, ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Ɛada.   
\m
\v 17 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Raɛuwil, mmis n Ɛisu: amɣar Naḥat d umɣar Zaraḥ d umɣar Samma d umɣar Mizza. Ina tuɣa aten d imɣaren n Raɛuwil di temmurt n Idum, d ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Basmat, tamɣart n Ɛisu.   
\m
\v 18 Ina tuɣa aten d ayt n Ahulibama, tamɣart n Ɛisu: amɣar Yaɛuc d umɣar Yaɛlam d umɣar Quraḥ. Ina tuɣa aten d imɣaren n Ahulibama, tamɣart n Ɛisu, yeǧis n Ɛana.  
\v 19 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Ɛisu d ina tuɣa aten d imɣaren \add n tqebbař nsen\add*, nitni d Idum.   
\b  
\m
\v 20 \bd Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Saɛir, Axuri, inni d imezdaɣ n temmurt nni\bd*: Luṭan, Cubal, Ṣabɛun, Ɛana, \x ◘ \xo 36:20 \xt 1 Im. 1:38. \x*  
\v 21 Dicun, Iṣar d Dican.  
\m \bd Ina tuɣa aten d imɣaren \+bdit n tqebbař\+bdit* n Ixuriyyen\bd*, ayt n Saɛir di temmurt n Idum.   
\m
\v 22 Iḥenjiren n Luṭan tuɣa aten d Axuri d Haymam uca tuɣa Timnaɛ d učmas n Luṭan.   
\m
\v 23 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Cubal: Ɛalwan, Manaḥat, Ɛibal, Cafu d Unam.   
\m
\v 24 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Ṣabɛun: Aya d Ɛana. D Ɛana wanita d wenni d yufin řɛunṣarat s waman iḥman di řexřa, umi yarwes iɣyař n Zibiyun babas. \x ◘ \xo 36:24 \xt 1 Im. 1:40 \x*   
\m
\v 25 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Ɛana: \add mɣir\add* Dicun, d Ahulibama, yeǧis n Ɛana.   
\m
\v 26 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Dican: Ḥamdan d Ahban d Yitran d Karan.   
\m
\v 27 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Iṣar: Bilhan, Zaɛwan d Ɛaqan.   
\m
\v 28 Ina tuɣa aten d iḥenjiren n Dican: Ɛuṣ d Aran.   
\m
\v 29 Ina tuɣa aten d imɣaren n tqebbař n Ixuriyyen: amɣar Luṭan d umɣar Cubal d umɣar Ṣabɛun d umɣar Ɛana  
\v 30 d umɣar Dicun d umɣar Iṣar d umɣar Dican. Ina tuɣa aten d imɣaren n Ixuriyyen ɛlaḥsab imɣaren nsen di temmurt n Saɛir.   
\b  
\m
\v 31 \bd Ina tuɣa aten d ijeǧiden nni iḥekmen di temmurt n Idum qbeř ma ad iḥkem ujeǧid x ayt n Israil\bd*: \x ◘ \xo 36:31 \xt 1 Im. 1:43. \x*   
\m
\v 32 Bilaɛ, mmis n Baɛur, iḥkem di Idum uca isem n tendint nnes tuɣa-t d Dinhaba.   
\m
\v 33 Immut Bilaɛ uca Yubab, mmis n Zaraḥ zi Buṣra idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\m
\v 34 Yubab immut uca Ḥucam, zi temmurt n Itaymaniyyen, idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\m
\v 35 Immut Ḥucam uca Hadad, mmis n Badad, wenni iɣeřben x Midyan deg iyyar n Mu’ab, idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. Isem n tendint nnes qqaren as Ɛawit.   
\m
\v 36 Immut Hadad uca Samla zi Masriqa idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\m
\v 37 Immut Samla uca Cawul, zi Raḥubut ɣar yeɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\m
\v 38 Immut Cawul uca Baɛl-Ḥanan, mmis n Ɛakbur, idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\m
\v 39 Immut Baɛl-Ḥanan, mmis n Ɛakbur, uca Hadar idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. Tandint nnes qqaren as Faɛu u tamɣart nnes qqaren as Mahiṭab’il, yeǧis n Maṭrid, yeǧis n Ma-Dahab. \f ◼ \fr 36:39 \ft \+fk Ma-Dahab\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘aman n wureɣ’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 40 Ina tuɣa aten d \bd ismawen n imɣaren \+bdit n tqebbař\+bdit* n Ɛisu ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen d imucan nsen d ismawen nsen\bd*: amɣar Timnaɛ d umɣar Ɛalwa d umɣar Yatit \x ◘ \xo 36:40 \xt 1 Im. 1:51-54\x*  
\v 41 d umɣar Ahulibama d umɣar Ila d umɣar Finun  
\v 42 d umɣar Qanaz d umɣar Tayman d umɣar Mibṣar  
\v 43 d umɣar Majdiyil d umɣar Ɛiram. Ina tuɣa aten d imɣaren n Idum ɛlaḥsab imucan nsen, di temmurt n řmelk nsen. Wanita d Idum, wenni d babas n Idumiyyen.   
\b  
\m
\v 44 Uca izdeɣ Yaɛqub di temmurt n Kenɛan mani tuɣa izeddeɣ babas am ubarrani.  
\m \bd Ina d imezruyen n yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen \+bdit zi\+bdit* Yaɛqub.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 36:44 \xt Amz. 36:7; Ɛbr. 11:9. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 37
\s1 Yusuf, zzenzen t aytmas  
\m
\v 1 Řami tuɣa ɣar Yusuf sbeɛṭac n iseggʷusa, yarwes uǧi n babas ak-d aytmas. Tuɣa Yusuf d amsexxar ɣar iḥenjiren n Bilha d iḥenjiren n Zilpa, timɣarin n babas uca issiweḍ Yusuf awařen nsen iɛeffanen i babatsen.  
\v 2 Uca ixs Israil Yusuf qaɛ x marra iḥenjiren nnes, minzi tuɣa-t ɣares d mmis x tewsar nnes uca igga as arruḍ \add s ifassen d iziraren\add*.  
\v 3 \add Řami\add* ẓrin aytmas belli babas ittexs i-t qaɛ xasen, carhen t uca war zemmaren akides ssiwřen \add ɛad\add* s řehna.   
\m
\v 4 Uca yurja Yusuf ict n tarjit, iɛawd i-tt i yaytmas. S uya nitni dewřen carhen t ɛad ktar.  
\v 5 Inna asen: “Sřem řexxu tarjit-a nni urjiɣ.  
\v 6 Xzar, tuɣa nettcedda tiqebbiḍin \add n imendi\add* di řwesṭ n yeyyar. U xzar, taqebbiḍt inu tbedd, teqqim tbedd u tiqebbiḍin nwem nni tuɣa d as dd-innḍent, bendqen i tqebbiḍt inu.”  
\v 7 Arrin-dd xas aytmas: “Ma ad tḥekmed \add zeɛma\add* nican xaneɣ \add am ujeǧid\add* niɣ ad xaneɣ tseǧḍed d aseǧeḍ?” Uca carhen t ɛad ktar di ssibbet n tirja nnes d wawařen nnes.  
\v 8 Uca yurja ɛad tarjit nneɣni, iɛawd i-tt i yaytmas, inna: “Xzar, arjiɣ ɛad tarjit nneɣni. Xzar tafuct d uyur d ḥiṭac n itran bendqen ayi.”  
\v 9 Iɛawed \add i-tt\add* i babas d aytmas uca iwebbex i-t babas, inna as: “Mana tarjit-a i tarjid? Ma ad dd-nas \add jmiɛ\add*, necc d yemmac d aytmac, ad ac nbendeq ɣar temmurt?”  
\v 10 Aytmas usmen zzayes. Maca babas iɛqeř x wawařen\add -a\add*. \x ◘ \xo 37:10 \xt Řex. 7:9. \x*   
\m
\v 11 Uca ruḥen aytmas, ḥima ad arewsen uǧi n babatsen ɣar Cakim.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna Israil i Yusuf: “Ma war arewsen aytmac \add uǧi\add* ɣar Cakim? Zid, ad cek ɣarsen ssekkeɣ.” Uca yarra-dd xas: “Aqa ayi da!”  
\v 13 Uca inna as: “Ruḥ cek, xzar muxas ǧan aytmac d muxas ǧan wuǧi uca awi ayi-dd řexbar ɛawed.” \add Ammu\add* i-t issekk zi řewḍa n teɣzurt n Ḥabrun uca netta yiweḍ-dd ɣar Cakim.  
\v 14 Yufa i-t ijj n weryaz umi iweddar deg iyyar. Isseqsa t weryaz, inna: “Min tarezzud?”  
\v 15 Inna: “Arezzuɣ x aytma. Ttzawgeɣ cek, ini ayi mani arewsen.”  
\v 16 Aryaz yarra-dd: “Aqa muṭṭiyen iqiḍan nsen ssa, necc sřiɣ asen qqaren: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad nraḥ ɣar Dutan.’” \add Řexdenni\add* iruḥ Yusuf awarni aytmas uca yufa i-ten di Dutan. \f ◼ \fr 37:16 \ft \+fk Dutan\ft  - isem-a wanita iffeɣ-dd zi tutlayt n Ikaldaniyyen u ixs ad yini ‘tnayen n wanuten’.\f*   
\m
\v 17 Umi t ẓrin zi řaggʷaj, qbeř ma ad ɣarsen dd-iqarreb, mɛahaden ḍidd nnes ḥima ad t nɣen,  
\v 18 nnan ijj i wenneɣni: “Xzar, yusa-dd bu-tirja nni!  
\v 19 Zid řexxu, ejj aneɣ ad t nᵉnneɣ uca ad t nenḍar deg wanu, ad nini: ‘Ca n řweḥc yewɛar icca i-t!’, uca \add xenni\add* ad nẓar min ɣa iřint tirja nnes.”  
\v 20 Isřa Rubin man aya uca ifekk i-t zeg ifassen nsen, inna: “War t nneqq ca!” \x ◘ \xo 37:20 \xt Amz. 42:22. \x*  
\v 21 Inna asen \add ɛawed\add* Rubin: “War sizziřem idammen! Nḍarem t deg wanu-ya \add da\add* di řexřa. War xas tteggem afus!”. Inna ammu ḥima ad t ifekk zeg ifassen nsen uca ad t yarr ɣar babas.   
\m
\v 22 Uca imsar, umi dd-yiweḍ Yusuf ɣar aytmas, kksen nitni arruḍ x Yusuf, arruḍ \add s ifassen d iziraren\add* nni xas tuɣa,  
\v 23 uca ṭṭfen t, nḍaren t deg wanu. \add Maca\add* anu tuɣa ixwa, war dayes tuɣi ca aman.  
\v 24 Awarni man aya qqimen maḥend ad ccen aɣrum, uca řami ssgeɛɛden nitni tiṭṭawin nsen, zřin ijj n ukaravan n Ismaɛiliyyen i dd-yusin zi Jilɛad. Iřeɣman nsen arbun řeɛṭur d řefwah n balsam d mirru, gguren ad t awyen ɣar Miṣra.  
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* inna Yahuda i yaytmas: “Man řefḍeř mařa nenɣa umatneɣ uca ad neffar idammen nnes?  
\v 26 Ɣawrem, ad t nezzenz i Ismaɛiliyyen, war ittiři ufus nneɣ xas, aqa d umatneɣ d aysum nneɣ.” Uca sřin aytmas ɣares.  
\v 27 Am dd-ɛdun tujjar n Midyan, ssgeɛɛden-dd Yusuf zeg wanu uca zzenzen t s ɛicrin n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart i Ismaɛiliyyen, inni dd-yiwyen Yusuf ɣar Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 37:27 \xt Řqḍ. 8:24; Izhd. 105:17; Řex. 7:9. \x*   
\m
\v 28 \add Řami\add* dd-idweř Rubin ɣar wanu, war din yufi Yusuf ɛad deg wanu. \add Xenni\add* icarreg arruḍ nnes.  
\v 29 Idweř ɣar aytmas uca inna: “Aḥenjir war din iǧi \add ɛad\add*. I necc, mani ɣa raḥeɣ?”  
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* ksin arruḍ n Yusuf uca ɣarṣen i yijj n umyan zeg iɣayḍen uca marɣen arruḍ s idammen.  
\v 31 Ssekken \add ijjen\add* s arruḍ d lemliḥ \add s ifassen d iziraren\add*, jjin t ad t yawi ɣar babatsen, nnan: “D wa i nufa. Xzar řexxu, ma wah niɣ lla arruḍ n mmic?”  
\v 32 Uca netta iɛeqř i-t, inna: “Arruḍ n mmi i yeǧa! Ca n řweḥc yewɛar icca i-t. Yusuf s tidett bettqen t!”  
\v 33 Icarreg Yaɛqub arruḍ nnes uca yarḍ ict n txancet \add n wecḍan\add* x tejɛinna nnes, icḍen x mmis aṭṭas n wussan.  
\v 34 Kkaren marra iḥenjiren nnes d marra tiḥenjirin nnes maḥend ad t ɛezzan, ɛad netta war ixs ad ittwaɛezza, inna: “Lla, ad dd-hwiɣ nnuryeɣ ɣar řaxart.” Uca isɣuy xas babas. \x ◘ \xo 37:34 \xt Amz. 42:38; 44:29,31. \x*   
\m
\v 35 Imidiyaniyyen zzenzen t di Miṣra i Putifar, amsexxar amcenneɛ n firɛun, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet. \x ◘ \xo 37:35 \xt Amz. 39:1; Izhd. 105:17. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 38
\s1 Yahuda d Tamar  
\m
\v 1 Di řweqt d ict ihwa Yahuda, \add iffeɣ\add* x aytmas, uca iwta \add iqiḍan nnes\add* ɣar yijj n weryaz d Adullamiti wenni umi qqaren Ḥira.  
\v 2 Uca iẓra din Yahuda yeǧis n yijj n weryaz d Akenɛani wenni umi qqaren Cuɛa. Uca \add Yahuda\add* yiwi \add yeǧis n Cuɛa\add* \add d tamɣart\add*, uca yudef xas. \x ◘ \xo 38:2 \xt 1 Im. 2:3. \x*  
\v 3 Nettat teksi s ddeyset uca turuw-dd aḥenjir uca \add Yahuda\add* iřaɣa as Ɛir.  
\v 4 Uca teksi ɛawed s ddeyset, turuw-dd aḥenjir uca třaɣa as Unan.  
\v 5 Uca turuw-dd ɛawed aḥenjir uca třaɣa as Cayla. Netta tuɣa-t di Kazib umi d as t-i-dd-turuw. \x ◘ \xo 38:5 \xt Řxř. 26:20. \x*  
\v 6 Yahuda iksi tamɣart i Ɛir, amenzu nnes. Tamɣart-a qqarent as Tamar.  
\v 7 Ɛir, amenzu n Yahuda, tuɣa-t d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI uca inɣa i-t SIDI.  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* inna Yahuda i Unan: “Adef x temɣart n umac, mřec akides deg wemcan n umac, tejjed-dd zzariɛet i umac.”  
\v 9 \add Maca\add* Unan issen belli zzariɛet war tᵉttiři nnes. Uca ammu imsar, umi yudef x temɣart n umas, inɣeř \add zzariɛet nnes\add* di temmurt, ḥima war ittic zzariɛet i umas.  
\v 10 Min igga tuɣa d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI uca inɣa i-t uřa d netta.   
\m
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna Yahuda i Tamar, tasřit nnes: “Qqim \add am\add* tajjač di taddart n babam, ař ɣa imɣar mmi Cayla!”, minzi inna: “Aqa war ittmetti uřa d wa am yaytmas.” Uca truḥ Tamar, tezdeɣ di taddart n babas.   
\m
\v 12 Ɛdun wussan aṭṭas, xenni temmut yeǧis n Cuɛa, tamɣart n Yahuda. Yahuda yarezzu ad ittwaɛezza uca igeɛɛed ɣar tḥimart n wuǧi nnes ɣar Timnata, netta d Ḥira, ameddukkeř nnes zi Adullam.  
\v 13 Ɛeřmen t i Tamar, nnan: “Xzar, aḍeggʷař nnem igeɛɛed ɣar Timnata, ad iřs uǧi nnes.”  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* tekkes xas arruḍ n tajjač, třeḥḥef s tkenbuct, tesřeḥhef ixef nnes zzayes, uca truḥ ad teqqim ɣar wadaf n Ɛaynayim, wenni iǧan deg webrid ɣar Timnata, minzi teẓra Cayla imɣar, u nettat tuɣa war d as temmewc d tamɣart.  
\v 15 Uca iẓra i-tt Yahuda, iḥesb i-tt d lfasda, minzi tuɣa-tt třeḥḥef i uɣembub nnes.  
\v 16 Uca imeyyeř ɣares ɣar webrid, inna as: “Ejj ayi ad xam adfeɣ!”, minzi netta tuɣa war issin, belli nettat d tasřit nnes. Nettat tenna: “Min d ayi ɣa tewced, ḥima ad xafi tadfed?”  
\v 17 Yarra-dd: “Necc ad \add am\add*-dd ssekkeɣ ijj n iɣayḍ d ameẓyan zeg iɣayḍen, zeg wuǧi.” Tenna as: “Mɣir ewc ayi ijj n warhan ař d ayi t-i-dd tᵉssekked.”  
\v 18 Inna: “Man aḍman i d am i ɣa wceɣ?” Nettat tenna: “Taxadent nnec n ucemmiɛ d ttesbiḥ nnec d taɣɣarct i ɣarek deg ufus.” Uca iwca as ten, yudef xas uca teksi zzayes ddeyset.  
\v 19 Uca tekkar, truḥ, tekkes xas takenbuct nnes uca tyarḍ arruḍ nnes n tajjač.   
\m
\v 20 Uca issekk Yahuda iɣayḍ d ameẓyan zeg iɣayḍen x ufus n umeddukkeř nnes Adullami, ḥima ad iṭṭef \add ɛawed\add* aḍman zeg ufus n temɣart, \add maca\add* war tt yufi.  
\v 21 Isseqsa iryazen x wemcan nnes, inna: “ Mani teǧa temɣart n farq-ccɣeř nni tuɣa iqqimen x webrid ɣar Ɛanayim?” Nitni arrin-dd xas: “War da tuɣi qaɛ ca n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř ɣar zzawect.”  
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb-dd ɣar Yahuda, inna: “War tt ufiɣ ca, uřa d iryazen n wemcan \add nni\add* nnan: ‘War da tuɣi qaɛ ca n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř \add ɣar zzawect\add*.’”  
\v 23 Uca inna Yahuda: “Ejj i-tt ad tᵉṭṭef \add aḍman\add* ɣares, ḥima war nettiři d řɛar. Xzar, necc aqa ssekkeɣ iɣayḍ-a d ameẓyan, \add maca\add* cek war tt tufid.”   
\m
\v 24 Ɛřaḥař awarni třata n iyuren temsar, aqa xebbaren Yahuda, nnan: “Tamar, tasřit nnec, aqa tessefsed ixef nnes uca řexxu nettat aqa-tt s ddeyset s farq-ccɣeř \add nnes\add*.” \add Xenni\add* inna Yahuda: “Suffɣem tt-i-dd, ad tecmeḍ!”  
\v 25 Umi tt-i-dd-yiwyen ɣar barra, tessekk-dd \add ijjen\add* ɣar uḍeggʷař nnes, maḥend ad yini: “Zeg weryaz n řeḥwayej-a, aqa ksiɣ s ddeyset.” Tenna ɛad: “Arzu xenni wi iřan taxadent-a n ucemmiɛ d ttesbiḥin-a d taɣɣarct-a.”  
\v 26 Yahuda iɛeqř \add i-tent\add*, inna: “Aqa-tt d nican xafi, minzi war tt wciɣ \add d tamɣart\add* i Cayla mmi.” War iqqim issen i-tt \add ɛad\add*.   
\m
\v 27 Di řweqt umi dd-tiweḍ ad dd-taruw, aqa da acniwen deg uɛeddis nnes. \x ◘ \xo 38:27 \xt 1 Im. 2:4. \x*  
\v 28 Imsar umi dd-turuw, issuffeɣ-dd ijjen afus uca teksi t řqabřa uca tcedd i-t ɣar ufus nnes s ufiřu d azeggʷaɣ, tenna: “Wa i dd-iffɣen d amezwar.”  
\v 29 Řami dd yarra afus nnes, iban-dd umas, uca tenna: “Mammec teggid tazzit. \add Ad tiřid\add* d bu-ittareẓẓan!” Uca semman t Fariṣ. \f ◼ \fr 38:29 \ft \+fk Fariṣ\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘anufseř’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 38:29 \xt Mixa 2:13; Mt. 1:3\x*  
\v 30 Awarni man aya iffeɣ-dd umas, wenni ɣar iǧa ufiřu azeggʷaɣ deg ufus nnes uca isemma t Zaraḥ. \f ◼ \fr 38:30 \ft \+fk Zaraḥ\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘azeggʷaɣ’ niɣ ‘wenni yareqqen’.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 39
\s1 Yusuf ameḥḍay x taddart n Putifar  
\m
\v 1 Nedhen \add xenni\add* Yusuf ɣar Miṣra. Putifar, amsexxar amcenneɛ n firɛun, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, ijj n Umiṣri, isɣa i-t zeg ufus n Ismaɛiliyyen, inni din t yiwyen. \x ◘ \xo 39:1 \xt Amz. 37:27; Izhd. 105:17. \x*  
\v 2 Tuɣa SIDI ak-d Yusuf. Tuɣa netta d aryaz ifřeḥ uca tuɣa-t di taddart n sidis, Amiṣri. \x ◘ \xo 39:2 \xt Řex. 7:9. \x*  
\v 3 Iẓra sidis belli SIDI tuɣa-t akides u belli SIDI issekkwaḍ s ufus nnes marra min tuɣa ittegg.   
\m
\v 4 \add Ammu i\add* yufa Yusuf arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnes, isexxar as. Uca igga i-t \add Putifar\add* d ameḥḍay x taddart nnes uca igga as deg ufus nnes marra min ɣares.  
\v 5 Zeg wass min di t igga x taddart nnes u x marra min ɣares, ibark SIDI taddart n Umiṣri di ṭṭweɛ n Yusuf. Tuɣa lbaraka n SIDI x marra min ɣares, \add am\add* daxeř n taddart, \add am barra\add* deg iyyar.  
\v 6 Marra min ɣares, ijja i-t deg ifassen n Yusuf, ař war issin netta ca ktar mɣir aɣrum i ittett.  
\m Tuɣa Yusuf icna deg waddud u udem nnes dayes aẓri.  
\v 7 Imsar awarni man aya, aqa tamɣart n sidis tenḍar tiṭṭawin nnes di Yusuf, tenna: “Zid, ṭṭeṣ akidi.” \x ◘ \xo 39:7 \xt Awřn. 7:13. \x*  
\v 8 \add Maca\add* netta yugi, inna i temɣart n sides: “Xzar, sidi inu war issin min iǧan di taddart řami da akides ǧiɣ. Marra min ɣares, igga i-t deg ufus inu.  
\v 9 Netta war iǧi sennej inu di taddart-a, war d ayi iṭṭif s walu mɣir cem, umi teǧid d tamɣart nnes. Mammec i ɣa ggeɣ ljarima-ya tameqqrant am tanita uca ad ggeɣ ddenb ak-d AREBBI!”  
\v 10 Tuɣa tessawař ak-d Yusuf kuř ass, war ɣares ittesři, ḥima ad iṭṭeṣ ṭṭarf nnes u ḥima ad akides yiři.   
\m
\v 11 Deg \add ijj n\add* wass temsar, umi dd-yudef ɣar taddart, ḥima ad igg řxedmet nnes, war tuɣi \add din\add* uřa d ijj zeg yeryazen n taddart.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* tᵉṭṭeff i-t zeg warruḍ nnes, tenna: “Araḥ-dd zzeř akidi!” \add Řexdenni\add* ijja as netta arruḍ nnes deg ufus, yarweř, iffeɣ barra.  
\v 13 Umi teẓra belli ijja as arruḍ nnes deg ufus nnes, yarweř ɣar barra,  
\v 14 třaɣa i aytbab n taddart, tenna asen: “Xzarem, aqa netta yiwy aneɣ-dd aryaz Aɛibrani, ḥima ad xaneɣ iḍḥec. Yusa-dd ɣari, ḥima akidi iṭṭeṣ uca necc sɣuyeɣ s jjehd.  
\v 15 Umi isřa belli ssgeɛɛdeɣ tmijja inu uca sɣuyeɣ, ijja ɣari arruḍ nnes, yarweř, iffeɣ barra.”  
\v 16 Uca nettat tegga arruḍ nnes zzates, ař dd ɣa yas sidis ɣar taddart.  
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* tessiweř akides s wawařen nni d ijjen, tenna: “Amsexxar Aɛibrani wenni dd-tiwyed ɣarneɣ, yusa-dd ɣari ḥima ad ayi issɛurra.  
\v 18 \add Umi\add* ssgeɛɛdeɣ tmijja inu, sɣuyeɣ, ijja arruḍ nnes ɣari uca yarweř barra.”  
\v 19 Sides isřa i wawařen inni d as tenna temɣart nnes, tenna: “Ammu i d ayi igga umsexxar nnec!”, uca ixeyyeq aṭṭas.  
\v 20 Iṭṭef i-t sidi n Yusuf, igga i-t di řeḥbes, mani tuɣa imeḥbas n ujeǧid. Ammu i iqqim di řeḥbes. \x ◘ \xo 39:20 \xt Izhd. 105:18. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 21 Maca SIDI tuɣa-t ak-d Yusuf uca isswiẓẓeḍ ɣares s tmexsiwt nnes icewwaren uca iwca as arḍa nnes di tiṭṭawin n umeqqran n řeḥbes.  
\v 22 Uca ameqqran n řeḥbes yarra marra imeḥbas nni tuɣa di řeḥbes sadu ufus n Yusuf. Marra min tuɣa tteggen din tuɣa ittekk x ufus nnes.  
\v 23 Ameqqran n řeḥbes war d as iqqim min xef ɣa innehweř zi min tuɣa sadu ufus nnes, minzi SIDI tuɣa ak-d Yusuf. Min ma tuɣa ittegg netta, SIDI issekkwaḍ i-t.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 40
\s1 Yusuf ifessar tnayen n tirja  
\m
\v 1 Imsar awarni man aya belli awarrad n ujeǧid n Miṣra d uxebbaz dennben ḍidd i siditsen, ajeǧid n Miṣra. \f ◼ \fr 40:1 \ft \+fk awarrad\ft  - wenni iqeddmen řkas i ujeǧid awarni iqeǧeb i-t d amezwaru.\f*  
\v 2 Iffugem firɛun x tnayen n imsexxaren icennɛen nnes, x umeqqran n iwarraden u x umeqqran n ixebbazen.  
\v 3 Igga i-ten deg uḥeṭṭu di taddart n řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, di taddart n tɛessast, mani iḥebbes Yusuf.  
\v 4 Řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet igga Yusuf d ameḥḍay nsen, uca netta tuɣa ittsexxar xasen. \add Ammu\add* tuɣa aten ussan \add d iziraren\add* di řeḥbes.  
\v 5 Urjin tarjit s tnayen idsen nsen, kuř ijjen zzaysen yurja di ǧiřet nni tarjit nnes s řmeɛna nnes, am uwarrad am uxebbaz n ujeǧid n Miṣra, inni tuɣa ittwaḥebbsen di taddart n tɛessast.   
\m
\v 6 Uca yusa-dd ɣarsen Yusuf x ṣṣbeḥ, ixzar daysen uca iẓra i-ten ttqellqen.  
\v 7 \add Řexdenni\add* isseqsa netta imsexxaren icennɛen n firɛun, inni tuɣa akides di řeḥbes di taddart n sidis, inna: “Maɣar barecnen udmawen nwem ass-a qaɛ ammu?”  
\v 8 Nitni nnan: “Aqa nurja tarjit, war da wi tt ɣa ifekken.” Inna asen Yusuf: “Ma war ǧin ca ifessaren zi AREBBI? Iwa, ɛawdem ayi tent řexxu!”   
\m
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* iɛawed umeqqran n iwarraden tarjit nnes i Yusuf, inna as: “Necc di tarjit inu ẓriɣ tazayart zzati tbedd.  
\v 10 Tazayart \add nni\add* ɣares třata n tseḍwin. \add Xmi\add* tessendiy, ittgeɛɛad nnuwwar nnes u ɣar izekkunen nnes iban-dd řḥebb n uḍiř yiweḍ.  
\v 11 Uca řkas n firɛun tuɣa-t ɣari deg ufus inu uca ksiɣ aḍiř nni uca ɛessareɣ t di řkas n firɛun uca sseɛduɣ řkas ɣar ufus n firɛun.”  
\v 12 Inna as Yusuf: “D wa d afessar nnes: třata n tiseḍwin, aqa d třata n wussan.  
\v 13 Ɛad třata n wussan \add xenni\add* ad ac issgeɛɛed firɛun azeǧif nnec uca ad cek yarr ɣar tsexxart nnec, ad tesseɛdud řkas i firɛun deg ufus nnes, am mammec tuɣa tasɣart nnec zic řami cek tuɣa d awarrad nnes.  
\v 14 Maca ɛqeř xafi xmi d ac dd ɣa yas řxar, ttzawageɣ cek ad kidi tegged s tmexsiwt icewwaren uca ejj firɛun ad xafi iɛqeř uca fekk ayi-dd zi taddart-a.  
\v 15 Minzi ucaren ayi zi temmurt n Iɛibraniyyen u da war ggiɣ x min xef dayi i ɣa ggen deg weḥfur \add n imeḥbas\add*.”   
\m
\v 16 \add Řami\add* iẓra umeqqran n ixebbazen belli ifessar as mliḥ, inna i Yusuf: “Uřa d necc ẓriɣ di tarjit inu třata n tsuǧatin s weɣrum d acemřař x uzeǧif inu.  
\v 17 Di tsuǧet n sennej tuɣa dayes aṭṭas n macca i firɛun i igga uxebbaz u ijḍaḍ ttᵉtten zi tsuǧet i iǧan x uzeǧif inu.”  
\v 18 Yarra-dd \add xas\add* Yusuf, inna: “D wa d afessar nnes. Třata n tsuǧatin d třata n wussan.  
\v 19 Ɛad třata n wussan \add xenni\add* ad xak issgeɛɛed firɛun azeǧif nnec \add jmiɛ akik\add* uca ad cek yayeř x ict n tcejjart u ijḍaḍ ad ccen aysum nnec.” \f ◼ \fr 40:19 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*   
\m
\v 20 Deg wass wiss třata, ass n wexřaq n firɛun, imsar belli issewjed ict n zzardet i marra imsexxaren nnes uca issgeɛɛed azeǧif n umeqqran n iwarraden u azeǧif n umeqqran n ixebbazen tuɣa-t jar imsexxaren nnes.  
\v 21 Uca netta yarra ameqqran n iwarraden ɣar řxedmet nnes n uwarrad, ařami wanita iwca \add ɛawed\add* řkas deg ufus n firɛun.  
\v 22 \add Maca\add* ameqqran n ixebbazen yuyeř i-t, am mammec d as ifessar Yusuf.  
\v 23 Maca ameqqran n iwarraden war ifekkar ca \add ɛad\add* di Yusuf, ittu t.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 41
\s1 Tarjit n firɛun  
\m
\v 1 Awarni řami ɛdun tnayen n iseggʷusa yurja firɛun aqa netta zeɛma ibedd x yeɣzar \add n Nil\add*.  
\v 2 Xzar, geɛɛdent-i-dd sebɛa n tfunasin zeg iɣzar, ṣebḥent i řxezrat u ɛemmarent s weysum, heddant jar weḥtic n uɣanim.  
\v 3 U xzar, sebɛa n tfunasin nneɣni geɛɛdent-i-dd awarni asent zeg iɣzar. Nitenti war ḥřint i řxezrat, aqa kkuccḍent uca beddent zzat i tfunasin nneɣni ɣar tma n iɣzar.  
\v 4 Tifunasin i war iḥřin i řxeẓrat, tinni ikuccḍen, ṣarḍent sebɛa n tfunasin iṣebḥen i řxezrat, tinni iṣeḥḥen. Uca ifaq-dd firɛun.   
\m
\v 5 Iṭṭeṣ \add ɛawed\add* uca yurja twařa nneɣni, u xzar, zeg ict n tseṭṭa geɛɛdent sebɛa n tidrin ccurent, cnant.  
\v 6 U xzar, ɣemyent-i-dd sebɛa n tidrin qqusbaren awarni asent, isscemḍ i-tent usemmiḍ acarqi.  
\v 7 Sebɛa n tidrin qqusbarent ṣarḍent sebɛa n tidrin iyman d iccuren. Uca ifaq-dd firɛun, u xzar, aqa d ict n terjit.   
\m
\v 8 Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ iban-dd belli buḥbeř nnes innehweř uca issekk maḥend ad dd-řaɣan i marra tarwa n tseḥḥart n Miṣra u i marra imiɣisen. Iɛawd asen firɛun tarjit nnes, maca war din tuɣi ḥed izemmar ad \add tt\add* ifessar i firɛun.  
\v 9 Issiweř umeqqran n iwarraden ak-d firɛun, inna: “Deg wass-a ad ttwasɛeqřeɣ x ddnub inu.  
\v 10 \add Umi\add* iffugem firɛun x imsexxaren nnes, igga ayi di řeḥbes di taddart n řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, \add am\add* necc \add am\add* umeqqran n ixebbazen.  
\v 11 Necc d netta nurja ict n tarjit di ǧiret d ict. Kuř ijj zzayneɣ yurja tarjit nnes s řmeɛna nnes. \x ◘ \xo 41:11 \xt Dan. 2:2. \x*  
\v 12 Tuɣa din akidneɣ ijj n ubřiɣ d Aɛibrani. Tuɣa-t d amsexxar n řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet. Nḥaja as tirja nneɣ uca ifessar aneɣ tent. I kuř ijj \add zzayneɣ\add* ifessar as tarjit nnes.  
\v 13 Am mammec tent ifessar, amenni i imsar. Aqa \add Firɛun\add* yarra ayi necc ɣar řxedmet inu u wenneɣni yuyeř i-t.”   
\b  
\m
\v 14 Issekk firɛun ḥima ad dd-řaɣan x Yusuf uca ssuffɣen t-i-dd deɣya zeg weḥfur \add n imeḥbas\add*. Iḥeff acuwwaf, ibeddeř arruḍ uca ammu i yudef ɣar firɛun. \x ◘ \xo 41:14 \xt Izhd. 105:20; Dan. 2:25. \x*  
\v 15 Inna firɛun i Yusuf: “Necc urjiɣ ict n tarjit, war iǧi wi tt ɣa ifessaren. \add Maca\add* aqa sřiɣ xak belli cek, \add xmi i ɣa\add* tesřid i tarjit, tzemmared ad tt tfessared.”  
\v 16 Yarra-dd Yusuf x firɛun, inna: “War iǧi ca zzayi, \add maca\add* AREBBI ad dd-yarr x mammec ɣa idweř umeddur n firɛun.”  
\v 17 Inna firɛun i Yusuf: “Di tarjit inu ẓriɣ ixef inu beddeɣ x tma n iɣzar.  
\v 18 Aqa geɛɛdent-i-dd sebɛa n tfunasin zeg iɣzar, ṣeḥḥent u ṣebḥent i řxezrat, heddant jar weḥtic n uɣanim.  
\v 19 Awarni asent sebɛa n tfunasin nneɣni geɛɛdent-i-dd. Tuɣa kkuccḍent u war ḥřint deg wudem, uẓɣent. Ammu war ḥřint, ɛemmarṣ war tent ẓriɣ di temmurt n Miṣra am tekmeř.  
\v 20 Tifunasin yuẓɣen, war iḥřin, sarḍent sebɛa n tyenduzin timezwura iṣeḥḥen.  
\v 21 \add Umi\add* udfent tina deg uɛeddis nsent, ɛad war issin ḥed, belli aqa udfent deg uɛeddis nsent, aqa qqiment war ḥřint i řxezrat am qbeř. \add Xenni\add* faqeɣ.  
\v 22 \add Ɛawed\add* ẓriɣ di tarjit inu, xzar, zeg ict n tseṭṭa ffɣent-i-dd sebɛa n tidrin ccurent u cnant.  
\v 23 Xzar, ẓriɣ, geɛɛdent-i-dd sebɛa n tidrin qqusbarent, uẓɣent, isscemḍ i-tent usemmiḍ acarqi.  
\v 24 U sebɛa n tidrin yuẓɣen, ṣarḍent sebɛa n tidrin nni icnan. Nniɣ \add tarjit\add* i tarwa n tseḥḥart, maca war din tuɣi ḥed i izemmaren ad ifessar \add tarjit-a\add*.”   
\m
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* inna Yusuf i firɛun: “Tarjit n firɛun d ict. AREBBI ibeyyen i firɛun min i ɣa yegg Netta.  
\v 26 Sebɛa n tfunasin cnant aqa atent d sebɛa n iseggʷusa. Uca tidrin cnant aqa d sebɛa n iseggʷusa. D tarjit d ict.  
\v 27 Sebɛa n tfunasin uẓɣent war iḥřin tinni dd-yuřyen awarni asent, aqa d sebɛa n iseggʷusa, u sebɛa n tidrin qqusbarent, tinni isscemḍ usemmiḍ acarqi, aqa atent d sebɛa n iseggʷusa i di ɣa yiři řaẓ.  
\v 28 D wa d awař i nniɣ i firɛun. Min ɣa yegg AREBBI, aqa isscen i-t i firɛun.  
\v 29 Xzar, di sebɛa n iseggʷusa i dd-igguren ad tiři tyawant tameqqrant x marra tammurt n Miṣra.  
\v 30 Awarni asen ad dd-asen sebɛa n iseggʷusa n řaẓ. Di marra tammurt n Miṣra ad ttun marra tyawant uca řaẓ ad iteḥḥa tammurt.  
\v 31 Uca tyawant war tᵉttiři tᵉttwassen \add ɛad\add* zi ssibbet n řaẓ i tt-i-dd-iḍfaren, maɣar řḥař ad yiři iqseḥ aṭṭas.  
\v 32 Ɛlaḥsab ṭṭbiɛet n tnayen n wudmawen n tarjit n firɛun, aqa tnayen n tseqqar, aqa man aya s minzi yura tt AREBBI nican u AREBBI aqa ad tt yegg deɣya.  
\v 33 Ejj firɛun řexxu ad yarzu x ijj n weryaz s řefhamet d tiɣit, maḥend ad t igg x temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 34 Ejj firɛun ad igg \add ammu\add*: ejj i-t ad igg iweqqafen x temmurt, maḥend ad ksin řexmus \add n řɣiǧet\add* n temmurt n Miṣra di sebɛa n iseggʷusa n tyawant.  
\v 35 Ejj i-ten ad ssmunen marra řeɛweč deg iseggʷusa iṣebḥen i dd ɣa yasen uca ad xemmřen řḥebb n yirden sadu ufus n firɛun, maḥend ad t xemmřen d macca di tneddam.  
\v 36 Ad yiři d řexzen n macca i temmurt i sebɛa n iseggʷusa n řaẓ nni dd ɣa iwḍan x temmurt n Miṣra, ḥima tammurt war tᵉttmetti ca s řaẓ.”   
\m
\v 37 Awařen-a banen-dd d lemliḥ i firɛun d marra imsexxaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 41:37 \xt Řex. 7:10. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yusuf idweř d řḥakem x temmurt n Miṣra  
\m
\v 38 \add Xenni\add* inna firɛun i imsexxaren nnes: “Ma izemmar ad ittwaf ca n weryaz am wa i di izeddeɣ Arruḥ n AREBBI?” \x ◘ \xo 41:38 \xt Izhd. 105:22. \x*  
\v 39 Uca inna firɛun i Yusuf: “Umi AREBBI immeř ac-dd marra aya, x uya war din yeǧi wenni ɣar teǧa řefhamet d tiɣit am cek.  
\v 40 Cek ad tiřid x taddart inu u i wawař nnec ad iṭaɛ řgens inu marra. Mɣir x řɛarc waha ad iřiɣ necc d ameqqran xak.” \x ◘ \xo 41:40 \xt Izhd. 105:21. \x*  
\v 41 \add Yarni\add* inna firɛun i Yusuf: “Xzar, ggiɣ cek x marra tammurt n Miṣra.”  
\v 42 Uca ikkes firɛun taxadent nnes zeg ufus nnes, igga i-tt deg ufus n Yusuf uca issyarḍ as arruḍ n řeqṭen azdad uca igga as taseddect n wureɣ deg yiri nnes.  
\v 43 Issenya i-t di tkarrut wiss tnayen i tuɣa ɣares uca řaɣan \add am gguren\add* zzates: “Qews!” Ammu i t igga x marra tammurt n Miṣra.  
\v 44 Inna firɛun i Yusuf: “Necc d firɛun, břa cek uřa d ijj ad igeɛɛed afus nnes niɣ aḍar nnes di marra tammurt n Miṣra.”  
\v 45 Iřaɣa firɛun i Yusuf s yisem n Ṣafnat-Faɛniḥ uca iwca as Asnat d tamɣart, tenni d yeǧis n Futi-Faraɛ, akehhan n Un. Uca ijuř Yusuf di temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 46 Tuɣa Yusuf d mmis n třatin n iseggʷusa řami ibedd netta zzat i firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, uca iffeɣ Yusuf zzat i firɛun uca ijuř x marra tammurt n Miṣra.   
\b  
\m
\v 47 Uca tesseɣmi-dd temmurt di sebɛa n iseggʷusa s tyawant. \f ◼ \fr 41:47 \ft \+fk s tyawant\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘s ifassen iccuren’.\f*  
\v 48 Issmun marra macca n sebɛa n iseggʷusa \add n tyawant\add*, inni tuɣa di temmurt n Miṣra, uca ixemmeř macca di tneddam. Macca n iyyaren i d as dd-innḍen i kuř tandint, ixemmeř i-tt dayes daxeř \add di tendint\add*.  
\v 49 Yusuf ixemmeř řḥebb n irden aṭṭas, anect n ijdi n řebḥar, ařami war izemmar ad ittwaḥseb, minzi tuɣa-t břa řeḥsab.   
\b  
\m
\v 50 Qbeř i dd-yusa useggʷas \add amezwaru\add* n řaẓ, mmarenyen-dd ɣar Yusuf \bd tnayen n iḥenjiren\bd*, inni d as dd-turuw Asnat, yeǧis n Futi-Faraɛ, akehhan n Un. \x ◘ \xo 41:50 \xt Amz. 46:20; 48:5. \x*  
\v 51 Isemma Yusuf \bd amenzu Manassa\bd*, minzi \add inna:\add* “AREBBI aqa issettu ayi marra tamara inu d marra taddart n baba.” \f ◼ \fr 41:51 \ft \+fk Manassa\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni ittejjan ad ttuɣ’.\f*  
\v 52 Wiss tnayen isemma i-t \bd Ifrayim\bd*, minzi inna: “AREBBI igga ayi s řɣiǧet di temmurt n řeḥṣaret inu.” \f ◼ \fr 41:52 \ft \+fk Ifrayim\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni itticcen řɣiǧet’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 53 \add Xenni\add* kemmřen sebɛa n iseggʷusa n ufeyyeḍ \add n řɣiǧet\add* nni ikkin x temmurt n Miṣra,  
\v 54 uca bdan ad dd-asen \bd sebɛa n iseggʷusa n řaẓ\bd*, am mammec xas issiweř Yusuf. Tuɣa řaẓ di marra timmura, \add maca\add* di marra tammurt n Miṣra tuɣa dayes \add ɛad\add* aɣrum. \x ◘ \xo 41:54 \xt Amz. 45:6; Izhd. 105:16. \x*  
\v 55 \add Ařami\add* tuɣa řaẓ di marra tammurt n Miṣra, isɣuy řgens ɣar firɛun x weɣrum. Uca inna firɛun i marra Imiṣriyyen: “Ruḥem ɣar Yusuf, ggem min d awem ɣa yini!”  
\v 56 Tuɣa řaẓ izeǧeɛ x marra tammurt uca yarzem Yusuf x marra min tuɣa ixemmeř, uca izzenz i-t i Imiṣriyyen, minzi tuɣa řaẓ idweř imɣar aṭṭas di temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 57 Zi marra timmura usin-dd \add iwdan\add* ɣar Miṣra ɣar Yusuf ḥima ad sɣen, minzi di marra timmura tuɣa řaẓ imɣar aṭṭas.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 42
\s1 Aytmas n Yusuf usin-dd ɣar Miṣra i twařa tamezwarut  
\m
\v 1 \add Řami\add* iẓra Yaɛqub belli aqa din řḥebb \add n yirden\add* di Miṣra, \add xenni\add* inna i iḥenjiren nnes “Maɣar teqqimem txezzarem ijjen deg wenneɣni?”  
\v 2 Inna: “Aqa necc sřiɣ belli din imendi di Miṣra. Ruḥem dinni uca sɣem aneɣ-dd ssenni \add řḥebb\add*, ḥima ad neqqim neddar uca war nettmetti ca.” \x ◘ \xo 42:2 \xt Řex. 7:12. \x*  
\v 3 Hwan ɛecra n wawmaten n Yusuf, maḥend ad raḥen ad sɣen imendi zi Miṣra.  
\v 4 \add Maca\add* Yaɛqub war issekk Binyamin, umas n Yusuf, ak-d aytmas, minzi inna: “Ḥima war d as ittemsar ca n řḥajjet d taɛeffant.”   
\m
\v 5 Jar inni dd-yusin \add dinni\add*, usin-dd \add ɛawed\add* ayt n Israil, maḥend ad sɣen \add macca\add*, minzi tuɣa din řaẓ di temmurt n Kenɛan.  
\v 6 Tuɣa Yusuf d řḥakem x temmurt uca izzenz \add imendi\add* i marra řgens n temmurt. Umi dd-iwḍen aytmas n Yusuf, bendqen as s uɣembub nsen ɣar temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 42:6 \xt Amz. 37:6. \x*  
\v 7 \add Umi\add* iẓra Yusuf aytmas, iɛqeř i-ten, maca igga ixef nnes axmi war ten issin uca issiweř akidsen s řeqsaḥet, inna asen: “Manis dd-tusim?” Nnan: “Zi temmurt n Kenɛan, maḥend ad nseɣ macca.”  
\v 8 Yusuf iɛeqř aytmas, maca nitni war t ɛqiřen ca.  
\v 9 Ifekkar Yusuf di tirja nni tuɣa xasen yurja, inna asen: “Kenniw d ibergagen i teǧam, tusim-dd, ḥima ad tẓarem mani war tᵉttwaḥḍi temmurt.” \x ◘ \xo 42:9 \xt Amz. 37:4. \x*  
\v 10 Arrin-dd xas: “Lla, a sidi inu, ɛad imsexxaren nnec usin-dd, maḥend ad sɣen macca.  
\v 11 Marra neccin aqa aneɣ d tarwa n ijj n weryaz. Aqa aneɣ d \add iryazen\add* d imtiqqan, imsexxaren nnec war ǧin ca d ibergagen.”  
\v 12 Netta yarra-dd xasen: “Lla, kenniw tusim-dd maḥend ad tẓarem tuɛɛaryent n temmurt.”  
\v 13 Nnan nitni: “Neccin d imsexxaren nnec, aqa aneɣ di tenɛac n wawmaten, tarwa n ijj n weryaz di temmurt n Kenɛan. Aqa amaẓuẓ aqa-t ak-d babatneɣ u wenneɣni war iǧi \add ɛad\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 42:13 \xt Amz. 43:29. \x*  
\v 14 Inna asen Yusuf: “Ma war d awem t nniɣ umi nniɣ: ‘Aqa kenniw d ibergagen!’  
\v 15 S uya tᵉttwaqeǧbem. S tidett am iddar firɛun, kenniw war dd-tteffɣem ssa, mɣir xmi dd ɣa yas umatwem amaẓuẓ danita!  
\v 16 Sekkem ijj n zzaywem, maḥend ad dd-yawi umatwem. \add Xenni\add* kenniw ad tᵉttwaḥebbsem uca awařen nwem ad ttwaqeǧben, ma daywem řaman. Mařa lla, s tidett am iddar firɛun, aqa kenniw d ibergagen!”  
\v 17 Uca igga i-ten třata n wussan di řeḥbes.   
\m
\v 18 Deg wass wiss třata inna asen Yusuf: “Ggem aya, ḥima ad teqqimem teddarem, necc tteggʷdeɣ AREBBI.  
\v 19 Mařa kenniw d iryazen d imtiqqan, jjem \add xenni\add* ijj n umatwem ad iqqim icarf di taddart mani tᵉttwaḥebbsem kenniw, \add xenni\add* ruḥem, ksim imendi i řaẓ n aytbab n taddart nwem.  
\v 20 Awyem-dd \add xenni\add* umatwem, amaẓuẓ, maḥend ad ttwaqeǧben wawařen nwem, war tᵉttmettim ca.” Uca nitni ggin amenni. \x ◘ \xo 42:20 \xt Amz. 43:5; 44:23. \x*  
\v 21 Nnan i wayawya: “S tidett aqa ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ad dd-narr ddeyyet n umatneɣ, aqa neẓra řḥeṣran n řeɛmar nnes umi d aneɣ ittar aḥinni, maca war d as nesři ca! X uya dd-yusa řḥeṣran-a xaneɣ.”  
\v 22 Yarra-dd xasen Rubin, inna: “Ma war d awem t nniɣ, umi nniɣ: ‘War xeṭṭim ca ak-d uḥenjir!’, maca kenniw war tesřim ca. Xzar, idammen nnes ttwattaren \add řexxu\add*!” \x ◘ \xo 42:22 \xt Amz. 37:20, 21. \x*  
\v 23 Nitni war ssinen belli ifhem asen Yusuf, minzi tuɣa aturjman jar asen. \x ◘ \xo 42:23 \xt Ayub 33:23\x*  
\v 24 Inneqřeb xasen uca isɣuy. \add Awarni as\add* inneqřeb-dd ɛawed ɣarsen, issiweř akidsen, iksi zzaysen Cimɛun uca iḥebbes i-t zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen.  
\v 25 Yumur Yusuf maḥend ad ccuren tixuncay nsen s imendi u ad ggen \add tmenyat n\add* nnuqart di kuř ict n txancet nsen uca wcin asen macca i webrid. U ammu i kidsen ggin.  
\v 26 Ssarbun imendi nsen x yeɣyař nsen uca ffɣen ssenni.   
\m
\v 27 \add Umi\add* yarzem ijjen zzaysen taxancet nnes, ḥima ad issecc aɣyuř nnes ɣar mani ɣa ssensen, iẓra nnuqart nnes deg arzam n uqemmum n txancet nnes.  
\v 28 Inna i yaytmas: “Nnuqart inu tedweř ayi-dd. Xzar, aqa-tt da di txancet inu!” Řexdenni ibedd asen wuř, arjijen uca nnan i wayawya: “Manawya i d aneɣ ittegg AREBBI?”  
\v 29 Uca reḥḥgen ɣar babatsen Yaɛqub di temmurt n Kenɛan uca ɛawden as marra min xasen ikkin, nnan:  
\v 30 “Aryaz, bab n temmurt, issiweř akidneɣ s řeqsaḥet, iḥesb aneɣ d ibergagen n temmurt.  
\v 31 \add Maca\add* nenna as: ‘Neccin d iryazen d imtiqqan, \add ɛemmarṣ\add* war neǧi d ibergagen.  
\v 32 Aqa aneɣ di tenɛac n wawmaten, iḥenjiren n babatneɣ. Ijjen war iqqim, amaẓuẓ aqa-t ass-a ak-d babatneɣ di temmurt n Kenɛan.’  
\v 33 U aryaz nni, bab n temmurt, inna aneɣ: ‘S uya ad ssneɣ, ma aqa kenniw d imtiqqan. Ad kidi tejjem ijjen zeg aytmatwem uca ad teksim \add macca\add* i řaẓ nni din ɣar aytbab n taddart nwem, xenni ffɣem.  
\v 34 Awyem-dd \add da\add* umatwem, amaẓuẓ, \add xenni\add* ad ssneɣ belli war teǧim d ibergagen, maca d imtiqqan uca ad awem dd-arxuɣ i wamatwem nwem uca ad traḥem ad tjuřem di temmurt.’”  
\v 35 \add Umi\add* ssexwan tixuncay nsen, ḥekkaren belli di txancet n kuř ijjen, aqa dayes tacyart s nnuqart nnes. Ẓrin nitni d babatsen ticyar s nnuqart nsen uca tudef i-ten tiggʷudi. \x ◘ \xo 42:35 \xt Amz. 42:25; 44:1. \x*   
\m
\v 36 Inna asen babatsen Yaɛqub: “Aqa tḥarrmem ayi \add zeg iḥenjiren inu\add*! Yusuf war dd-iḍhar \add ɛad\add* uřa d Cimɛun, uca \add řexxu\add* tᵉttexsem ad tnedhem Binyamin. Marra man aya ittemsaren di řeɛkes inu!”  
\v 37 \add Xenni\add* issiweř Rubin ɣar babas, inna: “Ad tenɣed tnayen n iḥenjiren inu, mařa war d ac t-i-dd-arriɣ. Ewc ayi t deg ufus inu, necc aqa ad ac t-i-dd-arreɣ!”  
\v 38 \add Maca\add* netta inna as: “Mmi war ittriḥ ca akidwem, minzi umas immut u netta weḥḥdes i d ayi iqqimen. Mařa iřqef i-t ca n řɣar deg webrid nni i ɣa tekkem, ad tessehwam ccib inu s wecḍan ɣar řaxart.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 43
\s1 Aytmas n Yusuf usin-dd ɣar Miṣra i twařa wiss tnayen  
\m
\v 1 \add Maca\add* řaẓ tuɣa imɣar aṭṭas di temmurt.  
\v 2 \add Řami\add* kemmřen ccin řḥebb \add n yirden\add* nni kidsen dd-iwyen zi Miṣra, inna asen babatsen: “Dewřem-dd ɛawed uca sɣem aneɣ-dd cwayt n macca.”  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* issiweř Yahuda, inna: “Aqa aryaz nni inna aneɣ s urekkez: “War tẓarrem \add ɛad\add* udem inu, mɣir mařa tiwyem-dd umatwem akidwem.”  
\v 4 Mařa tessekked umatneɣ akidneɣ, ad nraḥ din uca ad ac dd-nseɣ macca,  
\v 5 maca mařa war t tᵉssekkid \add akidneɣ\add*, xenni war dinni nettraḥ, minzi aryaz nni inna aneɣ: ‘War tẓarrem \add ɛad\add* udem inu mɣir mařa yusa-dd umatwem akidwem.’” \x ◘ \xo 43:5 \xt Amz. 42:20; 44:23; \x*  
\v 6 Inna Israil: “Maɣar d ayi teggim řɣar uca tennam i weryaz nni belli aqa ɣarwem ɛad umatwem nneɣni?”  
\v 7 Nitni nnan: “Aryaz nni isseqsa xaneɣ nican, u x temmurt mani nexřeq, inna: ‘Ma iddar ɛad babatwem? Ma ɣarwem ca n umatwem nneɣni?’ \add Xenni\add* nɛawed as \add t\add*. Ma nzemmar zeg wawařen-a ad dd-nejbed illa ad nessen zeɛma ad yini: ‘Awyem-dd umatwem?’”  
\v 8 Uca inna Yahuda i babas Israil: “Sekk akidi aḥenjir uca ad nekkar ad nraḥ, ḥima ad neddar u war nᵉttmetti ca neccin d cek d tarwa nneɣ.  
\v 9 Necc ad as iřiɣ d aḍman u zeg ufus inu ad t tᵉttared ɛawed. Mařa war d ac t-i-dd-arriɣ, ad t ssbeddeɣ zzatek, ad yiři xḍiɣ akidek i řebda! \x ◘ \xo 43:9 \xt Amz. 44:32. \x*  
\v 10 Meɛlik war neqqim nettraja \add aṭṭas\add*, tiři řexxu nedweř-dd tnayen n twařawin.”   
\m
\v 11 \add Uca\add* yarra-dd xasen Israil, babatsen: “Mařa ammu i yeǧa s tidett, ggem ammu uca ksim min icnan aṭṭas n temmurt di txuncay nwem, hwam-dd maḥend ad t tiwyem d arriɣalu i weryaz nni: cwayt n balsam d cwayt n tamment, řeɛṭur d mirru d teɣyact n pistac d ǧuz.  
\v 12 Ksim tnayen n tseqqar n \add tenɛacin n\add* nnuqart akidwem uca arrem s ufus nwem nnuqart i dd-iɛeqben di txuncay nwem. Ad taɣ tuɣa d ca n lɣalaṭ.  
\v 13 Awyem-dd ɛawed umatwem akidwem, kkarem, ɛeqbem ɣar weryaz nni.  
\v 14 Uca aqa Arebbi, Amzemmar x kuřci, ad awem iwc arreḥmet zzat i wudem n weryaz nni uca ad yarxu i umatwem nneɣni d Binyamin. U min d ayi iqqimen necc, mařa ttwaḥarrmeɣ zeg iḥenjiren inu, aqa ad zzaysen ttwaḥarrmeɣ!”   
\m
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* iwyen iryazen arriɣalu uca ksin deg ufus nsen tnayen n tseqqar n \add tmenyat\add* n nnuqart uřa d Binyamin uca kkaren, hwan ɣar Miṣra uca bedden zzat i wudem n Yusuf.  
\v 16 \add Umi\add* iẓra Yusuf Binyamin akidsen, inna i wenni \add tuɣa\add* x taddart nnes: “Sidef iryazen-a ɣar taddart, tɣarṣed \add i ca\add* min iǧan i tɣarṣt, sewjed i-tt, minzi iryazen-a ad kidi ccen ɣar wezyen n wass.”  
\v 17 Igga weryaz am mammec d as inna Yusuf uca yiwi iryazen ɣar taddart n Yusuf.  
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* dewřen yeryazen nni ggʷeden aṭṭas, umi ten ssidfen di taddart n Yusuf uca nitni nnan: “X \add tmenyat n\add* nnuqart i d aneɣ dd-idewřen di txuncay nneɣ twařa tamezwarut iwyen aneɣ-dd da ḥima \add xenni ɛawed\add* ad xaneɣ ɛefsen uca ad xaneɣ ɛeddan, \add xenni\add* ad aneɣ ksin d isemɣan ak-d yeɣyař nneɣ.”  
\v 19 Qarrben-dd ɣar weryaz nni igga Yusuf x taddart uca ssiwřen akides ɣar wadaf n taddart,  
\v 20 nnan: “A sidi inu, neccin aqa nican nehwa-dd d amezwar, maḥend ad nseɣ macca. \x ◘ \xo 43:20 \xt Amz. 42:3. \x*  
\v 21 Imsar umi dd-niweḍ ɣar řemraḥ uca narzem tixuncay nneɣ, neẓra nnuqart n kuř ijj ɣar werzam n uqemmum n txancet nnes, nnuqart nneɣ s řmizan nnes nican. Aqa narra i-tt-i-dd s ifassen nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 43:21 \xt Amz. 42:27,35. \x*  
\v 22 Ɛawed niwi-dd deg ifassen nneɣ nnuqart nneɣni, ḥima ad nseɣ macca. Neccin war nessin wi iggin nnuqart di txuncay nneɣ.”  
\v 23 Yarra-dd \add xasen\add*: “Sřam xawem, war tteggʷedem ca! AREBBI nwem d AREBBI n babatwem iwca awem ict n txabect di txuncay nwem. Aqa nnuqart nwem ṭṭfeɣ tt.” Uca issuffeɣ-dd ɣarsen Cimɛun.  
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* issidef weryaz iryazen nni ɣar taddart n Yusuf, iwca \add asen\add* aman uca sirden iḍaren nsen. Iwca \add asen\add* ɛawed řeɛřef i yeɣyař nsen. \x ◘ \xo 43:24 \xt Amz. 18:4. \x*  
\v 25 U nitni sswejden arriɣalu i Yusuf, wenni igguren ad dd-yas ɣar wezyen n wass, minzi nitni sřin aqa ad ccen dinni.   
\m
\v 26 \add Řami dd-\add* yudef Yusuf ɣar taddart, wcin as-dd di taddart arriɣalu nni dd-iwyen akidsen, uca bendqen as ɣar temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 43:26 \xt Amz. 37:9; 42:6. \x*  
\v 27 Isseqsa ten x mammec ǧan uca inna: “Mammec iǧa babatwem awessar i xef tessiwřem? Ma aqa ɛad iddar?”  
\v 28 Nitni arrin: “Mlih i yeǧa umsexxar nnec, babatneɣ, netta ɛad iddar.” Uḍaren nitni uca netta ibendeq.  
\v 29 \add Řami\add* netta issgeɛɛed tiṭṭawin nnes uca iẓra Binyamin, umas, mmis n yemmas, inna: “Ma d wa d umatwem, amaẓuẓ, min xef d ayi tessiwřem?” \add Xenni\add* inna: “Ad xak iḥinn AREBBI, a mmi!” \x ◘ \xo 43:29 \xt Amz. 42:13. \x*  
\v 30 Yusuf iffeɣ xenni deɣya, minzi taḥnunect nnes x umas tuɣa temɣar. Yarzu x mani ɣa iru uca yudef ɣar ijj n wexxam uca iru din. \x ◘ \xo 43:30 \xt Amz. 45:2. \x*  
\v 31 Issird udem nnes uca iffeɣ-dd ɣar barra, iṭṭef deg ixef nnes, inna: “Qedmem-dd macca.”  
\v 32 Nitni sswejden as i netta weḥḥdes u i nitni weḥḥedsen uřa i Imiṣriyyen inni akides ccin weḥḥedsen, minzi Imiṣriyyen war zemmaren ad ccen aɣrum ak-d Iɛibraniyyen, minzi d man aya d jjɛifect ɣar Imiṣriyyen.  
\v 33 Uca nitni qqimen zzat i wudem nnes: amenzu \add deg wemcan nnes\add* ɛlaḥsab tasɣart n tmenzut nnes uca amaẓuẓ \add deg wemcan nnes\add* ɛlaḥsab temẓi nnes. Tuɣa iryazen ttbehaten, xezzaren ijjen deg wenneɣni.  
\v 34 Uca netta iqeddem asen-dd zi min \add tuɣa iǧan\add* zzates, maca tasɣart n Binyamin tuɣa-tt xemsa n tseqqar ktar zi tseqqar n marra idsen. Uca swin nitni, ssenni dewřen farḥen akides.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 44
\s1 Taxceft i igga Yusuf i aytmas  
\m
\v 1 Issekk Yusuf ɣar \add umsexxar\add* nni \add tuɣa\add* x taddart nnes, inna as: “Ɛemmar tixuncay n yeryazen nni s macca, marra min zemmaren ad ksin. Egg nnuqart n kuř ijj deg warzam n uqemmum n txancet nnes.  
\v 2 Sars řkas inu, řkas n nnuqart, deg warzam n uqemmum n txancet n umaẓuẓ ak-d \add tmenyat\add* n nnuqart n řḥebb nnes \add n yirden\add*.” Uca igga am mammec d as inna Yusuf.  
\v 3 Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ umi dd-yeffu řhař, jjin iryazen ad uyuren, nitni ak-d yeɣyař nsen.  
\v 4 Umi ffɣen nitni zi tendint, tuɣa \add ɛad\add* war ggʷijen ca, inna Yusuf i wenni \add tuɣa\add* x taddart nnes: “Kkar, ḍfar iryazen nni uca, xmi xasen ɣa teɛdud, ini asen: ‘Maɣar dd-tarram řxar s řɣar?  
\v 5 Ma war iǧi d wa \add d řkas\add* i zi isess sidi inu u \add ma war iǧi\add* s wa i zi ɣa ikacef min ɣa imsaren tiwecca? Aqa teggim řɣar umi teggim amya.’”   
\m
\v 6 \add Am\add* ten iɛdu, inna asen awařen-a simant nsen.  
\v 7 Nitni arrin-dd xas: “Mayemmi iqqar sidi inu awařen-a? Iggʷej x imsexxaren nnec ad ggen man aya.  
\v 8 Xzar, nnuqart i nufa deg warzam n uqemmum n txuncay nneɣ, aqa narr ac tt-i-dd zi temmurt n Kenɛan. Mammec \add ɛad\add* i ɣa negg ad nacar nnuqart niɣ ureɣ zi taddart n sidi nnec?  
\v 9 Wi zeg imsexxaren nnec i ɣar i ɣa ittwaf \add řkas\add*, ad immet, uca neccin ɛawed ad niři d isemɣan n sidi inu!”  
\v 10 Netta inna: “Xenni řexxu ad yiři am mammec tennam kenniw. Wenni ɣar t ɣa naf, d netta ad yiři d ismeɣ inu, maca kenniw ad tiřim d ifurra.”  
\v 11 Uca kuř ijj zzaysen iqeǧeq ad issars taxancet nnes di temmurt uca kuř ijj yarzem taxancet.  
\v 12 Uca netta ifettec i-tent, ibda zeg umeqqran, ikemmeř zeg umeẓyan, uca ufin řkas di txancet n Binyamin.   
\m
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* carrgen arruḍ nsen, uca kuř ijj issarbu \add ɛawed\add* x weɣyuř nnes uca ɛeqben nitni ɣar tendint.  
\v 14 Uca yiweḍ Yahuda ak-d aytmas ɣar taddart n Yusuf, wenni tuɣa din ɛad, uca wḍan zzates ɣar temmurt.  
\v 15 Inna asen Yusuf: “Mana cɣeř-a i teggim? Ma war tefhimem ca belli ijj n weryaz am necc, iggur ad xas ikacef nican?”  
\v 16 Inna Yahuda: “Min ɣa nini i sidi inu d mammec i ɣa nessiweř niɣ s min zi ɣa nsegged ixef nneɣ? AREBBI iqeǧeb ddenb n imsexxaren nnec, xzar, neccin d imsexxaren n sidi inu, neccin d wi ɣar ufin řkas.”  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* netta yarra: “Iggʷej xafi ad ggeɣ aya! Aryaz nni ɣar ufin řkas, netta ad yiři d ismeɣ inu, \add maca\add* kenniw ruḥem di řehna ɣar babatwem.”   
\m
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* yiweḍ-dd Yahuda ɣares, inna: “\add A\add* sidi inu, ejj ad issiweř umsexxar nnec ijj n wawař deg umezzuɣ n sidi inu, war yareqq uxeyyeq nnec x umsexxar nnec, minzi aqa cek am firɛun.  
\v 19 Sidi inu isseqsa imsexxaren nnes, inna: ‘Ma ɣarwem \add ɛad\add* babatwem niɣ tawmat?’  
\v 20 Uca neccin narra x sidi inu: ‘Aqa ɣarneɣ babatneɣ d awessar d yijj n uḥenjir, \add wenni d as dd-ittwaxeřqen\add* x tewsar nnes, d amaẓuẓ ɛad. Umas immut, netta waha i iqqimen \add zeg iḥenjiren\add* n yemmas, u babas ittexs i-t.’  
\v 21 \add Xas uca\add* tennid cek i imsexxaren nnec: ‘Awyem t-i-dd \add da\add* ɣari, ḥima ad t ẓareɣ s tiṭṭawin inu.’ \x ◘ \xo 44:21 \xt Amz. 42:15. \x*  
\v 22 Uca neccin nenna i sidi inu: ‘War izemmar uḥenjir ad yejj babas, minzi mařa ijja i-t, babas ad immet.’  
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* tennid i imsexxaren nnec: ‘Mařa umatwem amaẓuẓ war dd-yusi akidwem, war tẓarrem ɛad udem inu.’ \x ◘ \xo 44:23 \xt Amz. 43:3, 5 \x*  
\v 24 Řami ngeɛɛed ɣar baba, amsexxar nnec, nesseɛdu as awařen n sidi inu.  
\v 25 Uca babatneɣ inna: ‘Ɛeqbem ɛawed maḥend ad tesɣem cwayt n macca i neccin.’  
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* narra-dd: ‘War nzemmar ad nraḥ. \add Maca\add* mařa umatneɣ, amaẓuẓ, iruḥ akidneɣ, ad nraḥ, minzi war nzemmar ad nẓar udem n weryaz nni, mɣir mařa aqa akidneɣ umatneɣ amaẓuẓ.’  
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* inna aneɣ umsexxar nnec, babatneɣ: ‘Kenniw tessnem belli tnayen \add n iḥenjiren\add* i d ayi dd-turuw temɣart inu.  
\v 28 Iffeɣ ijjen zi ɣari uca nniɣ: Aqa s tidett ittwabetteq! U ař řexxu ɛad war t ẓriɣ. \x ◘ \xo 44:28 \xt Amz. 37:32. \x*  
\v 29 Mařa ɛawed tekksem ayi wa uca imsar ca n řɣar, ad tessehwam ccib inu s wecḍan ɣar řaxart!’ \x ◘ \xo 44:29 \xt Amz. 42:38. \x*  
\v 30 Řexxu \add xenni\add*, mařa ruḥeɣ necc ɣar umsexxar nnec, baba, uca aḥenjir war kidi iǧi - řeɛmar nnes iřṣeq ɣar řeɛmar n \add babas\add* -  
\v 31 aqa ad immet xmi ɣa iẓar aḥenjir war iǧi, uca imsexxaren nnec ad ssehwan ccib n umsexxar nnec, babatneɣ, s wecḍan ɣar řaxart.  
\v 32 Aqa zeɛma amsexxar nnec d aḍman i uḥenjir-a ɣar baba umi inna: ‘Mařa war d ac t-i-dd-arriɣ, řexdenni necc ad iřiɣ d amednub i baba i řebda!’ \x ◘ \xo 44:32 \xt Amz. 43:9. \x*  
\v 33 Iwa řexxu, ejj amsexxar nnec ad iqqim deg wemcan n uḥenjir-a am yismeɣ ɣar sidi inu, uca ejj aḥenjir ad iraḥ ak-d aytmas!  
\v 34 Maɣar mammec ɣa ggeɣ ad geɛɛdeɣ ɣar baba, břa aḥenjir\add -a\add* akidi? Mammec i ɣa ẓareɣ řemḥayen i dd ɣa iwḍan x baba?”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 45
\s1 Yusuf issargeb ixef nnes i aytmas  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* war izemmar \add ɛad\add* Yusuf ad iṭṭef ixef nnes zzat i yinni akides marra uca iřaɣa: “Suffɣem marra inni akidi \add da\add*!” War iqqim ḥed akides řami isscen Yusuf i yaytmas min iɛna.  
\v 2 \add Řexdenni\add* yarxu tmijja nnes s iɣuyyan, \add ařami d as\add* sřin Imiṣriyyen, uca uřa d taddart n firɛun tesřa \add aya\add*.  
\v 3 Inna Yusuf i yaytmas: “Necc d Yusuf! Ma iddar ɛad baba?” Aytmas war zemmaren ad xas dd-arren, minzi tuɣa ggʷeden zzayes.  
\v 4 Inna Yusuf i yaytmas: “Qarrbem-dd řexxu ɣari!” Uca nitni qarrben \add ɣares\add*. Inna xenni: “Necc d Yusuf umatwem, wenni tezzenzem i Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 45:4 \xt Amz. 37:27; Izhd. 105:17; Řex. 7:9, 13. \x*  
\v 5 Řexxu, war kessim s wemnus u war t ttejjim ad yiři d axeyyeq di tiṭṭawin nwem umi d ayi tezzenzem danita \add i Miṣra\add*, aqa AREBBI issekk ayi-dd, maḥend ad \add kenniw\add* jjeɣ teddarem. \x ◘ \xo 45:5 \xt Amz. 50:19, 20, 21. \x*  
\v 6 Aqa řexxu \add ɛad\add* tnayen n iseggʷusa n řaẓ di temmurt uca qqim ɛad xemsa n iseggʷusa war daysen ittiři tyarza niɣ tameyra.  
\v 7 \add Maca\add* AREBBI issekk ayi-dd zzatwem, ḥima ad awem ggeɣ min iqqimen x temmurt u ḥima ad ḥḍiɣ tudart nwem i yijj n usenjem imɣar. \x ◘ \xo 45:7 \xt Amz. 50:20\x*  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, kenniw war d ayi dd-tessekkem ca da, maca AREBBI d wenni d ayi iggin d babas i firɛun d sidi x marra taddart nnes d řḥakem x marra tammurt n Miṣra.  
\v 9 Qeǧqem deɣya, sgeɛɛdem ɣar baba, inim as: ‘Ammu i iqqar mmic Yusuf: AREBBI igga ayi d sidi n marra Miṣra. Araḥ-dd ɣari, war tteɛgiz.  
\v 10 Ad tzedɣed di temmurt n Jucan, ad tiřid zzati, cek d iḥenjiren nnec, d iḥenjiren n iḥenjiren nnec, d wuǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin uřa d marra min ɣarek.  
\v 11 Ad ac ggeɣ arzeq din, minzi \add ad dd-asen\add* ɛad xemsa n iseggʷusa n řaẓ, ḥima war tᵉtteḍɛifed, cek \add lla\add*, taddart nnec \add lla\add*, uřa d marra min ɣarek \add lla\add*!  
\v 12 Xzar, tiṭṭawin nwem ẓrint, uřa d tiṭṭawin n uma Binyamin, aqa d necc i kidwem issawařen.  
\v 13 Ɛeřmem i baba x marra aɛuǧi inu di Miṣra u x marra min teẓrim. Qeǧqem deɣya, tiwyem-dd baba da.” \x ◘ \xo 45:13 \xt Řex. 7:14. \x*  
\v 14 Uca ingez x yiri n Binyamin umas, iru, uca Binyamin iru x yiri nnes.  
\v 15 Issudem marra aytmas, iru xasen. Awarni man aya ssiwřen akides aytmas.   
\m
\v 16 \add Řami\add* tesřa taddart n firɛun řexbar\add -a\add*, nnan: “Aytmas n Yusuf usin-dd!”. Tuɣa-t d řexbar aṣebḥan di tiṭṭawin n firɛun d imsexxaren nnes.  
\v 17 Inna firɛun i Yusuf: “Ini i aytmac: ‘Ggem aya: sarbum zwayeř nwem uca geɛɛdem, ruḥem ɣar temmurt n Kenɛan.  
\v 18 Ksim-dd babatwem d raǧ nwem, tusim-dd ɣari. Aqa ad awem wceɣ lemliḥ n temmurt n Miṣra uca ad teccem zi min icnan n temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 45:18 \ft \+fk min icnan\ft  - s Tɛibranit temmars ammu ‘tadunt n temmurt’.\f*  
\v 19 Aqa ttwaggent tiweṣṣa di ṭṭweɛ nnek. Ggem aya: Ksim zi temmurt n Miṣra ikarruten i iḥenjiren nwem u i temɣarin nwem, awyem-dd \add zzayes\add* babatwem uca asem-dd \add da\add*.  
\v 20 War ttejjim tiṭṭawin nwem ad ssḥissfent i řqecc nwem, minzi lemliḥ n temmurt n Miṣra ad yiři nwem.’”   
\m
\v 21 Uca ammu i ggin ayt n Israil. Iwca asen Yusuf ikarruten x řumur n firɛun uca iwca asen \add ɛawed\add* macca i webrid.  
\v 22 Iwca i kuř ijj zzaysen weḥḥdes arruḍ n jdid, maca i Binyamin iwca as teřt-mya n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart d xemsa n warruḍ d jdid.  
\v 23 U ammu \add ɛawed\add* issekk i babas ɛecra n yeɣyař ccuren s min ifarzen n Miṣra u ɛecra n teɣyař ccurent s imendi d weɣrum d macca i babas \add umi ɣa yiři netta\add* deg webrid.  
\v 24 Iqebbeḍ aytmas uca ruḥen. Inna asen netta: “War ttmenɣim ca deg webrid.”  
\v 25 Geɛɛden zi Miṣra, iwḍen ɣar temmurt n Kenɛan ɣar Yaɛqub, babatsen.  
\v 26 Wcin as řexbar, nnan: “Yusuf aqa iddar ɛad, wah, aqa-t d řḥakem n marra tammurt n Miṣra!” \add Xenni\add* isxef wuř nnes, minzi war ten yumin ca.  
\v 27 Umi d as ɛawden marra awařen n Yusuf inni d asen inna u \add řami\add* iẓra ikarruten inni dd-issekk Yusuf ḥima ad t awyen, iɛqeb-dd buḥbeř n babatsen Yaɛqub.  
\v 28 Uca inna Israil: “Kfa! Yusuf mmi aqa iddar! Ad raḥeɣ uca ad t ẓarɣ qbeř i ɣa mmteɣ!”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 46
\s1 Aytmas n Yusuf usin-dd ɣar Miṣra ak-d Yaɛqub  
\m
\v 1 Ifsi Israil iqiḍan nnes \add ssenni\add*, \add yuyur\add* s marra min ɣares uca yiweḍ ɣar Bi’r-Sebɛa. Iqeddem \add din\add* tiɣarṣa i AREBBI n babas Isḥaq.  
\v 2 Uca issiweř AREBBI ak-d Israil di iweḥḥan di ǧiřet, inna: “Yaɛqub, Yaɛqub!” uca inna netta: “Aqa ayi da!”  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Necc d Arebbi, AREBBI n babac. War tteggʷed, maḥend ad tehwid ɣar Miṣra, minzi Necc ad cek ggeɣ din d ijj n řgens imɣar. \x ◘ \xo 46:3 \xt Amz. 13:16; 16:10; 17:2; 22:17; 26:24; 28:13; 32:9; 35:11; 48:4. \x*  
\v 4 Ad kidek hwiɣ ɣar Miṣra uca Necc ad cek ssgeɛɛdeɣ \add ɛawed\add* u Yusuf ad xak issars ifassen nnes x tiṭṭawin nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 46:4 \xt Řxř. 20:15; Aɛwd. 10:22; Yac. 24:4, 5, 6; Izhd. 105:23, 24; Ica. 52:4; Ḥuc. 11:1. \x*   
\m
\v 5 Ikkar Yaɛqub, iffeɣ zi Bi’r-Sebɛa. Ksin ayt n Israil babatsen Yaɛqub d iḥenjiren nsen d temɣarin nsen deg ikarruten nni dd-issekk firɛun maḥend ad t yawi. \x ◘ \xo 46:5 \xt Řex. 7:15. \x*  
\v 6 Ksin řebhayem nsen d wagřa i yarebḥen di temmurt n Kenɛan uca iwḍen ɣar Miṣra, Yaɛqub d marra iḥenjiren nnes akides:  
\v 7 iḥenjiren nnes d iḥenjiren n iḥenjiren nnes \add jmiɛ\add* akides, uřa d yessis d yessitsen n iḥenjiren nnes, aqa yiwi akides marra tarwa nnes ɣar Miṣra. \f ◼ \fr 46:7 \ft \+fk marra tarwa nnes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘marra zzariɛet nnes’.\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tarwa n Yaɛqub  
\m
\v 8 Ina d \bd ismawen n ayt n Israil, inni yudfen ɣar Miṣra\bd*:  
\m \bd Yaɛqub\bd* d iḥenjiren nnes.  
\m Amenzu n Yaɛqub: Rubin. \x ◘ \xo 46:8 \xt Uf. 1:2; 6:13; Řxř. 26:5; 1 Im. 4-8. \x*   
\m
\v 9 Tarwa n \bd Rubin\bd*: Ḥanuk d Fallu d Ḥaṣrun d Karmi. \f ◼ \fr 46:9 \ft \+fk Ḥanuk\ft  - xzar afesssar ɣar Amz. 4:17. \fk Fallu\ft  - ‘aryaz icenɛen’. \fk Ḥaṣrun\ft  - ‘wenni d iqewwaren s ijj n řḥiḍ’. \fk Karmi\ft  - ‘tazayart inu’ niɣ ‘bab n tzayart’.\f*   
\m
\v 10 Tarwa n \bd Cimɛun\bd*: Yamuyil d Yamin d Uhad d Yakin d Ṣuḥar d Cawul, mmis n \add temɣart\add* Takenɛanit. \x ◘ \xo 46:10 \xt Uf. 6:15; 1 Im. 4:24. \x*   
\m
\v 11 Tarwa n \bd Lawi\bd*: Jarcun d Qahat d Marari. \x ◘ \xo 46:11 \xt 1 Im. 5:27. \x*   
\m
\v 12 Tarwa n \bd Yahuda\bd*: Ɛir d Unan d Cayla d Fariṣ d Zaraḥ. Maca Ɛir d Unan mmuten di temmurt n Kenɛan. Tarwa n Fariṣ tuɣa aten Ḥaṣrun d Ḥamul. \x ◘ \xo 46:12 \xt Amz. 38:3, 4, 5; 1 Im. 2:5. \x*   
\m
\v 13 Tarwa n \bd Issakar\bd*: Tulaɛ d Fawwa d Yub d Cimrun.   
\m
\v 14 Tarwa n \bd Zabulun\bd*: Sarad d Ilun d Yaḥliyil.   
\m
\v 15 \bd Ina \+bdit tuɣa aten\+bdit* d iḥenjiren n Liya\bd* inni d as dd-turuw i Yaɛqub di Fadan-Aram, uca \add ɛawed\add* yeǧis Dina. Marra řeɛmur n iḥenjiren nnes d tḥenjirin tuɣa aten di třata u-třatin.   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Tarwa n \bd Jad\bd*: Ṣifyun d Ḥajji d Cuni d Aṣbun d Ɛiri d Arudi d Arwili. \x ◘ \xo 46:16 \xt 1 Im. 5:11. \x*   
\m
\v 17 Iḥenjiren n \bd Acir\bd*: Yimna d Yiswi d Bariɛa d učmatsen Caraḥ. D iḥenjiren n Bariɛa: Ḥabir d Malkiyil. \x ◘ \xo 46:17 \xt 1 Im. 7:30. \x*   
\m
\v 18 \bd Ina \+bdit tuɣa aten\+bdit* d iḥenjiren n Zilpa\bd* tenni iwca Laban i yeǧis Liya. Nettat turuw-dd ina i Yaɛqub, ina seṭṭac d arruḥ. \x ◘ \xo 46:18 \xt Amz. 29:24. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 Tarwa n \bd Raḥil, tamɣart n Yaɛqub:\bd* Yusuf d Binyamin.   
\m
\v 20 Ttwaxeřqen-dd i \bd Yusuf\bd* di temmurt n Miṣra Manassa d Ifrayim, inni d as dd-turuw Asnat, yeǧis n Fuṭi-Faraɛ, akehhan n Un. \x ◘ \xo 46:20 \xt Amz. 41:50; 48:5. \x*   
\m
\v 21 Tarwa n \bd Binyamin\bd*: Bilaɛ d Bakir d Acbil d Jira d Naɛman d Iḥi d Ruc d Muffim d Ḥuffim d Ard. \x ◘ \xo 46:21 \xt 1 Im. 7:6; 8:1. \x*   
\m
\v 22 \bd Ina \+bdit tuɣa aten\+bdit* d iḥenjiren n Raḥil\bd*, inni dd-ittwawarwen i Yaɛqub, marra arbeɛṭac d arruḥ.   
\b  
\m
\v 23 Tarwa n \bd Dan\bd*: \add mɣir\add* Ḥucim.   
\m
\v 24 Tarwa n \bd Naftali\bd*: Yaḥaṣwil d Juni d Yiṣru d Cillim. \x ◘ \xo 46:24 \xt 1 Im. 7:13. \x*   
\m
\v 25 \bd Ina \+bdit tuɣa aten\+bdit* d iḥenjiren n Bilha\bd*, tenni i d as iwca Laban i Raḥil yeǧis. Turuw as-dd ina i Yaɛqub, ina marra \add tuɣa aten\add* sebɛa d arruḥ. \x ◘ \xo 46:25 \xt Amz. 29:29. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 26 Marra řeɛmur nni dd-yusin ɣar Miṣra ak-d Yaɛqub, inni dd-iffɣen zeg uɣezdis nnes, břa timɣarin n iḥenjiren n Yaɛqub, ina marra tuɣa aten di setta u-settin řeɛmur.  
\v 27 Tarwa n Yusuf inni d as dd-ittwaxeřqen di Miṣra, aqa tnayen n řeɛmur. Marra řeɛmur n taddart n Yaɛqub nni dd-yusin ɣar Miṣra, \add tuɣa aten\add* di sebɛin. \x ◘ \xo 46:27 \xt Aɛwd. 10:22; Řex. 7:14. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 28 Uca netta issekk Yahuda zzates ɣar Yusuf, ḥima ad isscen abrid zzates ɣar Jucan uca iwḍen ɣar temmurt n Jucan.  
\v 29 Indeh Yusuf \add ɛawed\add* akarru nnes uca igeɛɛed ɣar Jucan, maḥend ad iřqa Israil, babas. Umi d as immeř ixef nnes, ingez as x yiri, iqqim ittru x yiri nnes aṭṭas.  
\v 30 Inna Israil i Yusuf: “Řexxu zemmareɣ necc ad mmteɣ, řexxu umi ẓriɣ aɣembub nnec, zeɛma aqa ɛad teddared!”  
\v 31 \add Xenni\add* inna Yusuf i yaytmas u i \add aytbab n\add* taddart n babas: “Ad geɛɛdeɣ ad xebbareɣ firɛun, ad iniɣ: ‘Aytma d taddart n baba, inni iǧan di temmurt n Kenɛan, aqa usin-dd ɣari.  
\v 32 Iryazen d imeksawen n wuǧi, tuɣa ceɣřen ixef nsen ak d řebhayem. Aqa iwyen-dd uǧi nsen d ifunasen d tfunasin nsen d marra min ɣarsen.’  
\v 33 Mařa imsar ad awem dd-iřaɣa firɛun uca ad awem yini: ‘Min teɛna řxedmet i tᵉtteggem?’,  
\v 34 ad tinim: ‘Imsexxaren nnec d iryazen inni iceɣřen ak-d řebhayem zi temẓi nsen ař i řexxu, neccin uřa d řejdud nneɣ!’, ḥima ad ɣarwem yiři ttesriḥ maḥend ad tzedɣem di temmurt n Jucan, minzi kuř ameksaw n wuǧi, aqa-t d jjɛifect i Imiṣriyyen.” \x ◘ \xo 46:34 \xt Amz. 43:32; Uf. 8:22. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 47
\s1 Israil ad izdeɣ di Jucan  
\m
\v 1 \add Řami\add* dd-yusa Yusuf, ixebbar firɛun, inna as: “Baba d aytma d wuǧi nsen d ifunasen d tfunasin nsen d marra min ɣarsen, aqa usin-dd zi temmurt n Kenɛan. Xzar, \add aqa aten\add* di temmurt n Jucan.” \x ◘ \xo 47:1 \xt Amz. 45:10. \x*  
\v 2 Uca zi jar marra aytmas yiwi xemsa n yeryazen, iqeddem as ten i firɛun.  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna firɛun i yaytmas: “Min teɛna řxedmet i tᵉtteggem?” Nitni arrin-dd x firɛun: “Imsexxaren nnec d imeksawen n wuǧi, am neccin am řejdud nneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 47:3 \xt Amz. 46:34. \x*  
\v 4 Nnan ɛawed i firɛun: “I tzeddiɣt di temmurt-a am ibarraniyyen i dd-nusa, minzi war yeǧi wefsu i wuǧi n imsexxaren nnec, minzi řaẓ iqseḥ di temmurt n Kenɛan. \add Xenni\add* řexxu, nettzaweg i cek, ejj imsexxaren nnec ad zedɣen di temmurt n Jucan!”  
\v 5 Uca issiweř firɛun ak-d Yusuf, inna: “Babac d aytmac usin-dd ɣarek.  
\v 6 Tammurt n Miṣra aqa-tt nnec marra. Ejj babac d aytmac ad zedɣen di temmurt iṣebḥen, ejj i-ten ad zedɣen di temmurt n Jucan uca mařa tḥekkared belli aqa jar asen iryazen iwengiten, ggem ten d imeḥḍayen x řebhayem inu.”  
\v 7 Uca indeh Yusuf babas, iqeddem i-t i firɛun uca Yaɛqub ibarek firɛun.  
\v 8 Inna firɛun i Yaɛqub: “Mechař ɣarek n iseggʷusa?” \f ◼ \fr 47:8 \ft \+fk Mechař ɣarek n issegʷusa?\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Mecḥař ussan n iseggʷusa n tudart nnec?’\f*  
\v 9 Yaɛqub yarra-dd x firɛun: “Mya u-třatin n iseggʷusa i ddareɣ d abarrani. Ussan n iseggʷusa n tudart inu yuqřiřen u \add ccuren s\add* řɣar. War iwiḍen ca wussan n iseggʷusa n tudart n řejdud inu deg wussan n lɣurba nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 47:9 \xt Izhd. 119:19; Ɛbr. 11:9, 13. \x*  
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* Yaɛqub ibark firɛun uca iffeɣ ssenni zzat i wudem n firɛun.   
\m
\v 11 Isscen Yusuf tazeddiɣt i babas d aytmas, iwca asen tasɣart di temmurt n Miṣra, zi lemliḥ n temmurt, di temmurt n Raɛamsis am mammec t iweṣṣa firɛun.  
\v 12 Iɛewweř Yusuf babas d aytmas d marra taddart n babas. \add Iɛewweř uřa d\add* macca i iḥenjiren imeẓyanen. \f ◼ \fr 47:12 \ft \+fk macca i iḥenjiren\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘macca i uqemmum n iḥenjiren’.\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aseyyar n Yusuf di řweqt n řaẓ  
\m
\v 13 Aɣrum tuɣa war iǧi di temmurt marra, minzi řaẓ tuɣa iqseḥ aṭṭas, ařami tiweḍ temmurt n Miṣra d temmurt n Kenɛan fennant s řaẓ.  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* iyru Yusuf marra nnuqart nni ittwafen di temmurt n Miṣra u di temmurt n Kenɛan deg ubeddeř n imendi i isɣin. Igga Yusuf nnuqart nni di taddart n firɛun.  
\v 15 \add Umi\add* teqḍa nnuqart zi temmurt n Miṣra d temmurt n Kenɛan, usin-dd marra Imiṣriyyen ɣar Yusuf nnan: “Ewc aneɣ aɣrum, maɣar mayemmi ɣa nemmet zzatek? War din \add ɛad\add* ca nnuqart.”  
\v 16 Yusuf inna: “Mařa war ɣarwem bu nnuqart ɛad, wcem \add xenni\add* řebhayem nwem u necc ad awem wceɣ \add macca\add* deg ubeddeř n řebhayem nwem.”  
\v 17 Nitni iwyen-dd řebhayem nsen ɣar Yusuf uca iwca asen Yusuf aɣrum deg \add wemcan n\add* iysan d wuǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin d yeɣyař \add nsen\add* uca issecc i-ten s weɣrum deg \add wemcan n\add* marra řebhayem nsen deg useggʷas nni.   
\m
\v 18 \add Umi\add* iɛdu useggʷas nni, usin-dd ɣares deg useggʷas wiss tnayen uca nnan as: “War nᵉtteffar ca x sidi inu belli aqa nnuqart nneɣ teqḍa uca řebhayem aqa atent \add deg ufus\add* n sidi inu. War iqqim walu zzat i wudem n sidi inu, mɣir arrimet nneɣ d iyyaren nneɣ.  
\v 19 Mayemmi ɣa nemmet zzat i tiṭṭawin nnec, uřa d neccin uřa d iyyaren nneɣ? Seɣ aneɣ, tesɣed tammurt nneɣ i weɣrum uca neccin d temmurt nneɣ ad niři d imsexxaren n firɛun. Ewc \add aneɣ\add* zzariɛet \add ḥima\add* ad neddar war nettmetti ca uca tammurt war tᵉddikkwiř d amessuci!”   
\m
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* isɣa Yusuf marra tammurt n Miṣra i firɛun, minzi Imiṣriyyen zzenzen marra iyyar nsen, minzi tuɣa řaẓ iqseḥ xasen. U \add ammu i\add* tedweř temmurt \add d agřa\add* n firɛun.  
\v 21 Uca issmuṭṭiy řgens zeg uneggaru n weymir ař aneggaru nneɣni n \add weymir\add* n Miṣra ɣar tneddam.  
\v 22 Mɣir tammurt n ikehhanen war tt isɣi ca. Aqa ikehhanen ɣarsen ict n řmunet zi firɛun, nitni ttᵉtten tasɣart nsen, tenni i d asen iwca firɛun. X uya war zzenzen ca tammurt nsen.  
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* inna Yusuf i řgens: “Xzar, ass-a necc sɣiɣ kenniw uřa d tammurt nwem i firɛun. Xzarem, aqa da zzariɛet nwem. Zarɛem zzayes tammurt!  
\v 24 Zi řɣiǧet ad tewcem tasɣart texmusect i firɛun u arebɛa n tseqqar \add i iqqimen\add* ad iřint \add i yixef\add* nwem d zzariɛet i yeyyar uca \add ad iřint\add*, maḥend ad zzaysent teccem kenniw ak-d aytbab n taddart nwem u \add ɛawed\add*, maḥend ad \add zzaysent\add* ccen iḥenjiren imeẓyanen nwem.”  
\v 25 Nitni nnan: “Cek teḥḍid tudart nneɣ. Ejj aneɣ ad naf arḍa di tiṭṭawin n sidi inu uca neccin ad niři d imsexxaren i firɛun.”  
\v 26 Igga Yusuf man aya d tawṣeyyet i din iǧan ař ass-a, belli ict n tesɣart n texmusect \add n řɣiǧet\add* n temmurt n Miṣra ad tiři i firɛun. Mɣir iyyaren n ikehhanen \add qqimen\add* d agřa nsen, war ddikkwiřen ca \add d agřa\add* n firɛun.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řmewt n Yaɛqub tudes-dd  
\m
\v 27 Ammu i izdeɣ Israil di temmurt n Miṣra, di temmurt n Jucan, mellken dayes uca wcin řɣiǧet uca ktaren s yijj n cckel imɣar.  
\v 28 Iddar Yaɛqub di temmurt n Miṣra sbeɛṭac n iseggʷusa uca tuɣa ussan n Yaɛqub, iseggʷusa n tudart nnes, mya u-sebɛa u-rebɛin n iseggʷusa.  
\v 29 \add Umi\add* dd-iwḍen wussan i Israil ad immet, iřaɣa-dd x Yusuf mmis, inna as: “Mařa ufiɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, ttzawageɣ cek, ad tegged afus nnec sadu tmeṣṣaḍt inu uca egg akidi s tmexsiwt icewwaren d řaman u war d ayi neṭṭeř ca di Miṣra, \x ◘ \xo 47:29 \xt Amz. 24:2. \x*  
\v 30 maca xmi ɣa ggeɣ ad areyyḥeɣ jar řejdud inu, \add xenni\add* awi ayi zi Miṣra uca nḍeř ayi deg wenḍeř nsen. Yarra-dd xas: “Necc ad ggeɣ min tennid!”  
\v 31 \add Xas uca\add* inna as: “Jaǧ ayi!”, uca ijjuǧ as. Řexdenni yuḍar Israil x uzeǧif n qama. \x ◘ \xo 47:31 \xt Ɛbr. 11:21. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 48
\s1 Yaɛqub ibarek tarwa n Yusuf  
\m
\v 1 Awarni man aya imsar, ittwanna i Yusuf: “Xzar, aqa babac iḥřec!” \add Xenni\add* iksi akides tnayen n iḥenjiren nnes Manassa d Ifrayim.  
\v 2 Xebbaren Yaɛqub, nnan: “Xzar, aqa mmic Yusuf ad ɣarek dd-yas!” \add Xenni\add* igga Israil uř deg ixef nnes uca ikkar iqqim x qama.  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna Yaɛqub i Yusuf: “Arebbi, Amzemmar x kuřci, aqa iban ayi-dd di Luz, di temmurt n Kenɛan, u aqa Netta ibark ayi. \x ◘ \xo 48:3 \xt Amz. 17:1. \x*  
\v 4 U aqa Netta inna ayi: “Xzar, ad cek arreɣ ad tegged řɣiǧet uca ad cek kettareɣ, ad cek ggeɣ d ijj n wegraw n řegnus, ad ac wceɣ tammurt-a d agřa i řebda u i zzariɛet nnec awarni ac. \x ◘ \xo 48:4 \xt Amz. 28:3; 35:11. \x*  
\v 5 Uca řexxu, aqa tnayen n iḥenjiren nnec, Ifrayim d Manassa, inni d ac dd-ittwaxeřqen di temmurt n Miṣra qbeř i ɣarek dd-usiɣ di temmurt n Miṣra, aqa aten inu, am Rubin d Cimɛun i iǧan inu. \x ◘ \xo 48:5 \xt Amz. 41:50; 46:20. \x*  
\v 6 \add Maca\add* inni d ac dd-ittwaxeřqen awarni asen, ad iřin nnec. Ad ttwasemman x yisem n aytmatsen di řwart nsen.  
\v 7 Umi dd-usiɣ zi Fadan-Aram, temmut Raḥil zzati di temmurt n Kenɛan deg webrid, řami tuɣa ɛad war tiggʷij x Ifrata. Neḍřeɣ tt din deg webrid ɣar Ifrata!”, aqa-tt d Bayt-Laḥm. \x ◘ \xo 48:7 \xt Amz. 35:19. \x*  
\v 8 Iẓra Israil iḥenjiren n Yusuf, inna: “Min ɛnan ina?”  
\v 9 Yarra-dd Yusuf x babas: “D iḥenjiren inu i d ayi iwca AREBBI danita.” Inna \add as\add*: “Sqarrbem ten-dd ɣari uca ad ten barkeɣ!”  
\v 10 Tuɣa tiṭṭawin n Israil uẓɣent s tewsar, war iqqim ittwařa. Issqarreb as ten-dd, xenni issudem i-ten, idarreɛ asen.  
\v 11 Inna Israil i Yusuf: “War d ayi ittɣiř ad ẓareɣ \add ɛad\add* udem nnec. Xzar, AREBBI igga ayi ad ẓareɣ ɛad tarwa nnec!” \f ◼ \fr 48:11 \ft \+fk tarwa nnec\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘zzariɛet nnec’.\f*  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* issḍar i-ten Yusuf x ifadden nnes uca ibendeq s wudem nnes ɣar temmurt.  
\v 13 Uca iksi i-ten Yusuf s tnayen idsen, Ifrayim s ufusi nnes arendad n uzeřmaḍ n Israil u Manassa s uzeřmaḍ nnes arendad n ufusi n Israil uca issqarreb as \add ten\add*-dd.  
\v 14 Isswiẓẓeḍ Israil yefus nnes, issars i-t x uzeǧif n Ifrayim, waxxa tuɣa-t d amaẓuẓ, d azeřmaḍ nnes x uzeǧif n Manassa. Issars ammu ifassen nnes mammec nneɣni neɛmada, waxxa Manassa tuɣa-t d amenzu.  
\v 15 Israil ibark Yusuf, inna: “D AREBBI, wenni umi řejdud inu, Ibrahim d Isḥaq, uyuren zzates, AREBBI, wenni iǧan d Ameksaw inu zeg wami ǧiɣ ař ass-a, \f ◼ \fr 48:15 \ft \+fk zzates\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘zzat i uɣembub nnes’, ixs ad yini ‘di řḥeḍra nnes’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 48:15 \xt Ɛbr. 11:21. \x*  
\v 16 lmalak nni d ayi ifdin zi marra tuɛeffna, iři netta ad ibark iḥenjiren-a u iři ad ittwařaɣa isem inu daysen uřa d isem n řejdud inu, Ibrahim d Isḥaq. Iři ad mmarenyen ař ɣa dewřen d ijj n ubarru \add am iseřman deg waman\add* di řwesṭ n temmurt!” \f ◼ \fr 48:16 \ft \+fk ifdin\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 48:16 \xt Amz. 31:42; 32:1. \x*   
\m
\v 17 \add Umi\add* iẓra Yusuf, belli babas igga afus afusi nnes x uzeǧif n Ifrayim, tuɣa-tt d ict n řeɛřamet war teḥḥři ɣares di tiṭṭawin nnes uca iṭṭef afus n babas, ḥima ad t ibeddeř zeg uzeǧif n Ifrayim ɣar uzeǧif n Manassa.  
\v 18 Inna Yusuf i babas: “War ttegg ca ammu, \add a\add* baba, minzi d wa d amenzu, egg afusi nnec x uzeǧif nnes.”  
\v 19 \add Maca\add* babas war ixs ca, inna: “Ssneɣ, \add a\add* mmi, ssneɣ. Ɛawed netta ad idweř d ijj n řgens, ad imɣar ɛawed, maca umas amaẓuẓ ad yiři ktar zzayes, zzariɛet nnes ad tedweř d tacurret n řegnus.” \x ◘ \xo 48:19 \xt Raɛ. 4:11, 12. \x*  
\v 20 Uca \add ammu\add* i ten ibarek deg wass nni, inna: “Dayek, \add deg yisem nnek\add*, \add a Yusuf\add* ad ibarek \add řgens\add* Israil, ad inin: ‘Ad kenniw yarr AREBBI am Ifrayim d Manassa!’” Uca yarra Ifrayim ad ibedd zzat i Manassa. \x ◘ \xo 48:20 \xt Irm. 31:20. \x*  
\v 21 \add Awarni as\add* inna Israil i Yusuf: “Xzar, ad mmteɣ, maca AREBBI ad yiři akidwem, ad kenniw issmuṭṭiy ɣar temmurt n řejdud nwem.  
\v 22 Aqa wciɣ ac ict n tesɣart n idurar x min wciɣ i yaytmac, tenni ksiɣ necc zeg ifassen n Imuriyyen s ssif d řqews inu.” \x ◘ \xo 48:22 \xt Yac. 13:7; 16:1; 17:1; 24:8. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 49
\s1 Yaɛqub ibarek tarwa nnes  
\m
\v 1 Iřaɣa Yaɛqub x iḥenjiren nnes, inna: “Smunem-dd ixef nwem, ad awem iniɣ min d awem ɣa imsaren deg uneggar n wussan.  
\v 2 Smunem-dd ixef nwem uca sřem, \add a\add* tarwa n Yaɛqub, sřem i Israil, babatwem.   
\m
\v 3 \bd Rubin\bd*, cek d amenzu inu, jjehd inu, d amezwar n teryast inu, aqa cek d amseḍfar inu di řuɛřa, d amseḍfar \add inu\add* di řɛezz. \x ◘ \xo 49:3 \xt Amz. 29:32; Deu. 21:17; Izhd. 78:51. \x*  
\v 4 Cek amecnaw aman ittneqřaben, war dd ayi tḍeffared, aqa cek tgeɛɛded ɣar řectu n řemřac n babac, řexdenni tessfeḍḥed \add t\add*, aqa ɣar řectu inu igeɛɛed. \x ◘ \xo 49:4 \xt Amz. 35:22; 1 Im. 5:1. \x*   
\m
\v 5 \bd Cimɛun\bd* d \bd Lawi\bd* d awmaten! Řemwas nsen d řesnaḥ n lɛunf.  
\v 6 Di tmeɛmuč nsen war ittidef řeɛmar inu deg wegraw nsen war icarrec wuř inu. Aqa deg uxeyyeq nsen nɣin ijj n weryaz uca iɛjeb asen ad qessen iẓewran n iḍaren n ufunas. \x ◘ \xo 49:6 \xt Amz. 34:25. \x*  
\v 7 D amenɛuř axeyyeq nsen, minzi wanita ijhed aṭṭas, uřa d aduqqez \add n ufugem\add* nsen, minzi iqseḥ. Necc ad ten bḍiɣ x Yaɛqub, ad ten ssuyuseɣ di Israil. \x ◘ \xo 49:7 \xt Yac. 19:1; 21:3-45. \x*   
\m
\v 8 \bd Yahuda\bd*, aytmac ad cek ssemɣaren. Afus nnec ad yiři x yiri n řɛedyan nnec u iḥenjiren n babac ad ac bendqen.  
\v 9 Yahuda d ijj n mmis n wayrad. Zi zzardet i tuřyed, \add a\add* mmi. Iqwes amecnaw ayrad u amecmaw tayradt. Wi izeɛɛemen ad t-dd-issfaq? \x ◘ \xo 49:9 \xt Řxř. 24:9; Mixa 5:7. \x*  
\v 10 Taɣɣarct \add n řḥakem\add* war ittwakkes x Yahuda uřa d azeǧaḍ \add n ṣṣulṭa\add* zi jar iḍaren nnes, ař dd ɣa yas wenni i ɣa iwcen arraḥet uca ad as ṭaɛen řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 49:10 \xt Mt. 2:6. \x*  
\v 11 Iqqen ɣar tzayart asnus nnes d mmis nnes n teɣyuč ɣar tzayart icennɛen aṭṭas, issird arruḍ nnes di binu u arruḍ nnes deg idammen n uḍiř.  
\v 12 Tiṭṭawin \add nnes\add* d tibarcanin s binu u tiɣmas \add nnes\add* d ticemřařin s uɣi.   
\m
\v 13 \bd Zabulun\bd* ad izdeɣ ɣar tma n řebḥar, ad yiři d řmuyyi i iɣarruba. Aɣezdis nnes ad yareyyeḥ x Ṣidun. \x ◘ \xo 49:13 \xt Yac. 19:10, 11. \x*   
\m
\v 14 \bd Issakar\bd* d ijj n weɣyuř iqseḥ, izzeř jar tnayen n řmedwat.  
\v 15 Umi iẓra arraḥet d lemliḥ u tammurt aqa tarecceq, iqwes, igga tiɣarḍin nnes maḥend ad yarbu \add arrmeḥ\add* uca \add ammu i\add* idweř sadu azayřu n ismeɣ.   
\m
\v 16 \bd Dan\bd* ad iḥkem řgens nnes am yict zi tqebbař n Israil.  
\v 17 Ad yiři Dan d afiɣar deg webrid, tařefsa deg umesruq, wenni izeɛɛfen deg inirzawen n uyis, ař ɣa iwḍa wenni \add xas\add* inyin ɣar ḍeffar.  
\v 18 Asenjem nnec i ttrajiɣ, \add a\add* SIDI!   
\m
\v 19 \bd Jad\bd*, ad xas ḥejment bandiyyat, \add maca\add* ad xasen idarrec.   
\m
\v 20 \bd Acir\bd*, aɣrum nnes ad yiři d aɣrum ismen, netta ad iqeddem macca yiziden igellden.   
\m
\v 21 \bd Naftali\bd* d ict n tudadt ittwaḍeřqen, issuffuɣ awařen cnan.   
\m
\v 22 \bd Yusuf\bd* d mmis n tcejjart itticen řɣiǧet, mmis n tcejjart itticen řɣiǧet ɣar tařa. Yessis ggurent x weɣbar. \x ◘ \xo 49:22 \xt 1 Im. 5:1. \x*  
\v 23 Nitni ssarezgen xas \add tudart\add*, neyycen xas, \add wah\add* imjebbaden n řqews ḍfaren t, \x ◘ \xo 49:23 \xt Amz. 50:20. \x*  
\v 24 maca řqews nnes iqqim imḥeḍ u iɣaǧen n ifassen nnes qqimen arxun s ifassen n Umzemmar n Yaɛqub - x uya Netta d Ameksaw d taṣḍart n Israil -  
\v 25 s Arebbi n babac wenni cek i ɣa iɛawnen, Amzemmar x kuřci, wenni cek i ɣa ibarken s lbarakat n ujenna sennej, s lbarakat n \add waman\add* ihewřen i din iǧan swadday, s lbarakat n tubbect d řemřawet.  
\v 26 Lbarakat n babac d timeqqranin uɛřant x lbarakat n yinni d ayi dd-yejjin \add uca ttakkwaḍent\add* ɣar tqiccatin n tewririn n řebda. Ad iřint x uzeǧif n Yusuf, x tuccent n ucuwwaf n wenni yarebbu ttaj \add n weɛzar\add* jar aytmas . \x ◘ \xo 49:26 \xt Aɛwd. 33:16\x*   
\m
\v 27 \bd Binyamin\bd* d ijj n wuccen ittmezzaq. Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ ad isarḍ zzardet u s ǧiřet ibeṭṭa takeccaḍt.”   
\m
\v 28 Marra ina d tenɛac n tqebbař n Israil. D man aya min d asen inna babatsen uca ibark i-ten, \add wah,\add* ibark i-ten, kuř ijj s lbaraka nnes.  
\v 29 Yumur i-ten, inna asen: “Ad mmarenyeɣ ɣar řgens inu. Neḍřem ayi ak-d řejdud inu deg ifri wenni iǧan deg iyyar n Ifrun, Aḥitti,  
\v 30 deg ifri wenni iǧan deg iyyar n Makfila i iǧan zzat i Mamri di temmurt n Kenɛan, tenni isɣa Ibrahim ak-d yeyyar zi Ifrun, Aḥitti, ḥima ad yiři d anḍeř nnes. \x ◘ \xo 49:30 \xt Amz. 23:9, 16. \x*  
\v 31 Dinni i neḍřen Ibrahim d Sara tamɣart nnes. Dinni i neḍřen Isḥaq d temɣart nnes Rifqa. U necc neḍřeɣ din Liya. \x ◘ \xo 49:31 \xt Amz. 25:9; 35:29; Řex. 7:16. \x*  
\v 32 Iyyar s ifri i tuɣa dayes iǧan immseɣ x tarwa n Ḥit.”   
\m
\v 33 \add Umi\add* ikemmeř Yaɛqub ad iweṣṣa iḥenjiren nnes, ikemmec iḍaren nnes di qama, iffeɣ i-t buḥbeř uca immarni ɣar řgens nnes. \x ◘ \xo 49:33 \xt Řex. 7:15. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 50
\s1 Anḍeř n Yaɛqub  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* ingez Yusuf x uɣembub n babas, iru xas uca issudem i-t.  
\v 2 Yumur Yusuf i imsexxaren nnes, iḍbiben, ad ḥennḍen babas uca iḍbiben ḥennḍen Israil.  
\v 3 Arebɛin n wussan i dayes kkin, minzi ḥdajen ussan nni maḥend ad kemmřen aḥenneṭ uca run marra Imiṣriyyen sebɛin n wussan di ssibbet nnes.  
\v 4 \add Umi\add* ɛdun wussan n řeɛzat xas, issiweř Yusuf ak-d \add yenni n\add* taddart n firɛun, inna: “Mařa ufiɣ řexxu arḍa di tiṭṭawin nwem, ttzawageɣ kenniw, ad tessiwřem deg imejjan n firɛun, inim:  
\v 5 “Baba inu ijja ayi ad jjaǧeɣ uca inna: ‘Aqa ttmettiɣ. Ittxeṣṣa ad ayi tneḍřed deg wenḍeř nni neqceɣ i yixef inu di temmurt n Kenɛan!’ Xenni, ttzawageɣ, ejj ayi ad raḥeɣ řexxu ad neḍřeɣ baba uca \add awarni man aya\add* ad dd-ɛeqbeɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 50:5 \xt Amz. 47:29. \x*  
\v 6 Uca inna firɛun: “Ruḥ, nḍeř babac, am mammec yarra cek ad as tejjuǧed.”   
\m
\v 7 Uca igeɛɛed Yusuf ḥima ad inḍeř babas uca geɛɛden marra imsexxaren n firɛun akides, imɣaren n taddart nnes d marra imɣaren n temmurt n Miṣra,  
\v 8 uřa d marra taddart n Yusuf d aytmas nnes d taddart n babas. Mɣir iḥenjiren imeẓyanen nsen d wuǧi nsen d ifunasen d tfunasin nsen jjin ten di temmurt n Jucan.  
\v 9 Geɛɛden akides ikarruten d yinni inyin x yeysan uca ggin ijj n uqarru n řɛeskar imɣar.  
\v 10 \add Umi\add* iwḍen ɣar unedrar n Atad, wenni iǧan x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, ssgeɛɛden din ict n tɣuyyit temɣar, tejhed aṭṭas uca igga Yusuf \add din\add* ijj n wecḍan x babas i yijj n řmijař n sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 11 Ẓrin imezdaɣ n temmurt, ayt n Kenɛan, acḍan deg unedrar n Atad, nnan: “Wa d acḍan imɣar n Imiṣriyyen.” X uya řaɣan isem nnes Abal-Miṣrayim, wenni iǧan x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun. \f ◼ \fr 50:11 \ft \+fk Abal-Miṣrayim\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘acḍan n Imiṣriyyen’.\f*  
\v 12 Ggin as iḥenjiren nnes am mammec ten iweṣṣa.  
\v 13 Arbun t iḥenjiren nnes ɣar temmurt n Kenɛan, neḍřen t deg ifri deg iyyar n Makfila nni isɣa Ibrahim ak-d yeyyar zi Ifrun, Aḥitti, arendad n Mamri, maḥend ad yiři d anḍeř nnes. \x ◘ \xo 50:13 \xt Amz. 23:16; Řex. 7:15, 16. \x*  
\v 14 Awarni řami inḍeř babas, iɛqeb Yusuf ɣar Miṣra, netta d yaytmas d marra inni akides dd-igeɛɛden, maḥend ad neḍřen babas.   
\m
\v 15 \add Umi\add* ẓrin aytmas n Yusuf babatsen immut, nnan: “Mařa icarh aneɣ Yusuf, ad aneɣ ixeǧeṣ nican marra řɣar nni dayes negga.”  
\v 16 \add S uyenni\add* ssekken ad xebbaren Yusuf \add s man aya\add*, nnan: “Babac iweṣṣa qbeř řmewt nnes, inna:  
\v 17 ‘Ammu i ɣa tinim i Yusuf: Ttzawgeɣ cek, ɣfar řexxu axeṭṭu n aytmac d ddenb nsen d řɣar i d ac ggin. Ɣfar řexxu axeṭṭu n imsexxaren n AREBBI n babac!’” Uca isɣuy Yusuf am kis ssiwřen \add ammu\add*.  
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* usin-dd ɛawed aytmas \add s yixef nsen\add*, wḍan as zzat i uɣembub nnes, nnan: “Aqa-neɣ da d imsexxaren nnec!”  
\v 19 Yarra-dd xasen Yusuf: “War tteggʷdem ca! Ma aqa ayi necc deg wemcan n AREBBI? \x ◘ \xo 50:19 \xt Amz. 45:5. \x*  
\v 20 Waxxa kenniw txarrṣem dayi s řɣar, aqa AREBBI inwa zzayes řxar, ḥima ad yegg am mammec \add i teǧa\add* ass-a, ad yejj di tudart ijj n řgens d ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 50:20 \xt Amz. 45:7\x*  
\v 21 Řexxu, war tteggʷdem ca! Necc ad kenniw ɛewwřeɣ, kenniw d iḥenjiren imeẓyanen nwem.” Ammu ten issfewwej uca issiweř akidsen ɣar wuřawen nsen.   
\m
\v 22 Tuɣa Yusuf izeddeɣ di Miṣra, netta d taddart n babas, uca iddar Yusuf mya u-ɛecra n iseggʷusa.  
\v 23 Iẓra Yusuf iḥenjiren n Ifrayim ař jjiř wiss třata. Aqa ttwarwen-dd iḥenjiren n Makir, mmis n Manassa, ɛawed x ifadden n Yusuf. \x ◘ \xo 50:23 \xt Řxř. 32:39. \x*   
\m
\v 24 Uca inna Yusuf i yaytmas: “Necc ad mmteɣ, maca AREBBI ad kenniw yarzef s tidett uca ad kenniw issgeɛɛed zi temmurt-a ɣar temmurt i iwaɛd s tjaǧit i Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub.” \x ◘ \xo 50:24 \xt Ɛbr. 11:22. \x*  
\v 25 \add Xas uca\add* issjjuǧ Yusuf ayt n Israil, inna: “AREBBI ad kenniw yarzef s tidett uca \add xenni\add* ad teksim ssa iɣsan inu!” \x ◘ \xo 50:25 \xt Uf. 13:19; Yac. 24:32. \x*  
\v 26 Immut Yusuf umi tuɣa ɣares mya u-ɛecra n iseggʷusa. Ḥennḍen t uca ssarsen t di řmeḥmeř n umettin di Miṣra.   